\id ISA
\h Icaɛya
\toc1 Icaɛya
\toc2 Icaɛya
\toc3 Ica.
\mt1 Icaɛya
\c 1
\s1 Tameẓriwt n Icaɛya
\m 
\v 1 Řewḥiy n Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ, nni iẓra x Yahuda d Urcalim, deg wussan n Ɛuzziya, Yutam, Aḥaz d Ḥizqiya, ijeǧiden n Yahuda.
\b
\m 
\v 2 “Sřem, \add a\add* ijenwan, uca sseɣd, \add a\add* tammurt, minzi SIDI issawař: ‘Necc sseymeɣ iḥenjiren u ssemɣareɣ ten, \add maca\add* nitni ɣewwɣen xafi. \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Aɛwd. 32:1\x*
\v 3 Afunas issen bab nnes d usnus řmedwed n sidi nnes, \add maca\add* Israil war ɣares bu tussna, řgens inu war dayes teǧi řefhamet.
\v 4 \bd Uct\bd* x řgens i ixḍan, řgens \add i x iǧa\add* ddqeř n řmuɛṣiyyet, zzariɛet n iɛeffanen, tarwa n usnexřiɛ. Nitni jjin SIDI, sseḥqaren Amqeddas n Israil, arrin \add as-dd\add* s weɛrur. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Izhd. 78:8; Ica. 57:3\x*
\v 5 Mani tᵉttexsem ad tᵉttwawtem ɛad, \add umi\add* kenniw teqqimem tᵉttɣewwaɣem. Azeǧif marra ihřec, uř marra yuheř aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt 2 Im. 28:22; Irm. 2:30\x*
\v 6 Zi třeqqa n uḍar ař azeǧif war dayes tᵉttifed min iṣebḥen! Mɣir iyezzimen, ṭṭeɛbayar d iyezzimen yarezmen, war ten hennḍen, war ten ssyarḍen, war ten ssareḍben s zzect.
\v 7 Tammurt nwem texřa, tineddam nwem sscemḍen tent s tmessi, tammurt nwem ṣṣarden tt ibarraniyyen zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem, aqa-tt d řxirbet axmi ssenqeřben tt ibarraniyyen. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Aɛwd. 28:51, 52; Ica. 5:5\x*
\v 8 Yeǧis n Ṣihyun teqqim ɣar ḍeffar am yict n tɛiccut deg umarjeɛ n uḍiř, am texxant \add n uɛessas\add* deg iyyar n řexyar, am tendint ittwaḥṣaren.
\v 9 Mři SIDI n řɛeskarat war d aneɣ ijji drus min yarewřen, iři nedweř am Sadum, iři negga am Ɛamurra.’” \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Amz. 19:24; Ica. 17:6; 24:6; 30:17; Rum. 9:29\x*
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Sřem i wawař n SIDI, \add a\add* řḥukkam n Sadum! Wcem amezzuɣ i Ccariɛa n AREBBI, \add a\add* řgens n Ɛamurra!
\v 11 Min ɣa ggeɣ s tɣarṣi nwem, iqqar SIDI. Necc jjiwneɣ zi tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ n icarriyyen u zi tadunt n řmař iṣeḥḥen. Idammen n ifunasen imeẓyanen d yezmaren d iɣayḍen war d ayi tteɛjiben. \x ◘ \xo 1:11 \xt Izhd. 50:8, 9; Awřn. 15:8; 21:27; Ica. 66:3; Irm. 6:20; Ɛam. 5:22\x*
\v 12 Xmi dd-tᵉttasem ḥima ad tbanem zzat i wudem inu, wi kenniw iɛarḍen i uya, maḥend ad tɛefsem x řemraḥat inu?
\v 13 War d ayi dd-tawyem ɛad tawhibt ibeḍřen. Řebxur ɣari d nnɛi. Ussan n iyuren n jdid d wussan n ssebt d uřaɣi i tmesmunin iqeddsen war zemmareɣ ad ḥemřeɣ \add marra\add* aya, aqa-t d řmuɛṣiyyet, \add ɛad uřa\add* d amuni ifarzen.
\v 14 Řeɛmar inu icarreh ussan n uyur n jdid nwem d řeɛyudat nwem ittwaggen. Aqa aten dewřen ɣari d řeḥmeř, Necc uḥřeɣ ad ten arbuɣ.
\v 15 Xmi tᵉttsarraḥem ifassen nwem, ttřeḥḥfeɣ i tiṭṭawin inu zzaywem. Ɛad mařa kenniw tarnim di tẓaǧit, Necc war tt ttesřiɣ, maɣar ifassen nwem ɛemmaren s idammen.\x ◘ \xo 1:15 \xt Awřn. 1:28\x*
\v 16 Sirdem, sizdegem ixef nwem, ssiggʷejem tuɛeffna n tmegga nwem zi zzat n tiṭṭawin inu. Sbeddem zi řɣar i tᵉtteggem. \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt Izhd. 34:15; 37:27; Ɛam. 5:15; Rum. 12:9\x*
\v 17 Řemdem ad teggem min iṣebḥen, arzum x řḥeqq, wcem afus i wenni iḥsaren, ggem tasɣart i uyujiř, wtem x tajjač.”
\b
\m 
\v 18 “Asettiw-dd u ejj aneɣ ad nᵉttemḥakem ak-d wayawya!, iqqar SIDI. Waxxa ddnub nnec d izeggʷaɣen am uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen, ad dewřen d icemřaren am wedfeř, waxxa d izeggʷaɣen am uzeggʷaɣ yuǧɣen, ad dewřen d icemřařen am tḍuft. \x ◘ \xo 1:18 \xt Izhd. 51:9\x*
\v 19 Mařa kenniw tɛewwřem, u ad tesřem, \add xenni\add* ad teccem min iṣebḥen n temmurt,
\v 20 maca mařa kenniw tugim uca ad tɣewwɣem, ad kenniw yecc ssif, maɣar aqemmum n SIDI aqa issiweř!”
\b
\m 
\v 21 \qt “Mammec tedweř tendint\qt*
\m \qt nni dayes řaman\qt*
\m \qt d tamɣart n farq-ccɣeř!\qt*
\m \qt Nettat tuɣa teccur s řḥeqq,\qt*
\m \qt tasegda tuɣa tᵉttnusa dayes,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* řexxu iqettařen.\qt*
\m 
\v 22 \qt Nnuqart nnem tedweř d kuffu,\qt*
\m \qt binu nnem ṣṣuren t ak-d waman.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:22 \xt Ḥiz. 22:18, 19; Ḥuc. 4:18\x*
\m 
\v 23 \qt Řḥukkam nnem ttɣewwɣen,\qt*
\m \qt aqa ggin ixewwanen d imeddukkař \tl nsen\tl*,\qt*
\m \qt marra ttexsen tirzifin\qt*
\m \qt uca arezzun x arrecwet.\qt*
\m \qt Nitni war ttiɣen i uyujiř tasɣart nnes,\qt*
\m \qt ddeɛwet n tijjař war ten tᵉttikkwiḍ.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:23 \xt Irm. 5:28; Zak. 7:10\x*
\b
\m 
\v 24 “S uya iqqar Sidi, SIDI n řɛeskarat, Amzemmar n Israil: ‘\bd Uct\bd* \add xawem\add*! Necc ad ssfewwjeɣ ixef inu s iɣrimen inu, Necc ad xeřfeɣ ixef inu zi řɛedyan inu.
\v 25 Necc ad wteɣ afus inu xawem, ad kenniw ṣeffiɣ ak-d llixiyya uca marra řexfif nnem ad t weddareɣ. \x ◘ \xo 1:25 \xt Irm. 6:29; Mal. 3:3\x*
\v 26 Necc ad \add am\add* wceɣ ɛawed řquḍat nnem am ɣar umezwaru, d ayt n ccwar nnem am ɣar umezwaru. Awarni aya ad am řaɣan: ‘Tandint n tsegda!’ d ‘Tendint dayes řaman!’
\v 27 Ṣihyun ad tᵉttwassenjem s řḥeqq d yinni zzayes ittuben \add ad ttwassenjmen\add* s tsegda,
\v 28 \add maca\add* imɣewwɣen d imednab ad ttwarẓen jmiɛ, uca inni i ɣa iḥeyyden x SIDI, ad ttwaqḍan. \x ◘ \xo 1:28 \xt Ayub 31:3; Izhd. 1:6; 5:6; 73:27; 92:10; 104:35\x*
\v 29 Nitni ad seḍḥan zi ssibbet n tcejjura n l’aṣnam nni di temmeẓrem uca kenniw ad tseḍḥam zi ssibbet n iḥwicen nni tixḍarem kenniw.
\v 30 Maɣar kenniw ad tiřim am tcejjart n yigg i zi afar nnes isřaw, u am weḥwic i war ɣar ǧin waman.
\v 31 Ad idweř wenni ijehden d ijj n ufiřu n tiffest u řxedmet nnes d ict n tfeṭṭut, ad arɣen s tnayen idsen munen uca war din iǧi uřa d ijj wi ɣa issxesyen.’”
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Adrar n Taddart n SIDI
\m 
\v 1 Awař nni iẓra Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ, x Yahuda d Urcalim.
\b
\m 
\v 2 “Deg uneggar n wussan ad yiři wedrar n Taddart n SIDI ibedd imten x \add wedrar\add* ameqqran qaɛ n idurar. Netta ad iɛdu marra tiwririn uca ad ɣares dd-azzřen marra řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Mixa 4:1\x*
\v 3 Aṭṭas n řegnus ad ṭṭfen abrid \add dinni\add*, ad inin: ‘Asem-dd, ejj aneɣ ad ngeɛɛed ɣar wedrar n SIDI, ɣar Taddart n AREBBI n Yaɛqub, ḥima Netta ad aneɣ isseřmed ibriden nnes u neccin ad nuyur di tebridin nnes!’, maɣar zi Ṣihyun ad dd-teffeɣ Ccariɛa u awař n SIDI zi Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Izhd. 110:2\x*
\v 4 Netta ad iḥkem jar ccuɛub u ad iḥakem x waṭṭas n řegnus. Nitni ad ggen řesyuf nsen d dduzan u fřitcat nsen d řemwas i wezbar. War issgeɛɛad \add ijj n\add* řgens \add ɛad\add* ssif x \add ijj n\add* řgens \add nneɣni\add* u war darriben ɛad i umenɣi. \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt Yuw. 4:10; Mixa 4:3\x*
\v 5 \add A\add* taddart n Yaɛqub, araḥ-dd ejj aneɣ ad nuyur di tfawt n SIDI.”
\b
\s1 Ass n SIDI
\m 
\v 6 “Maɣar Cek tenḍared řgens nnec, taddart n Yaɛqub, minzi nitni ccuren s uqarri zi \add temmura n\add* ccarq uca ceɣřen ixef nsen s tbezgiwt am \add řgens n\add* Ifilisṭiniyyen, uca wtin ifassen ak-d tarwa n ibarraniyyen.
\v 7 Tammurt nsen teccur s nnuqart d wureɣ u war din aneggar ɣar txubay nsen. Tammurt nsen teccur s yeysan u war din aneggar ɣar \add ubarru n\add* ikarruten nsen.
\v 8 Tammurt nsen teccur s l’aṣnam, nitni bendqen zzat i řxedmet n ifassen nsen, i min ggin iḍewḍan nsen.
\v 9 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa iɣnes bnadem uca ad issehwa \add kuř\add* ijj n weryaz ixef nnes. War d asen ttsamaḥ!”
\m 
\v 10 “Adef ɣar řejruf, nuffar deg ucař zi ssibbet n usnexřiɛ n SIDI u zi ssibbet n řɛezz n lɛaḍama nnes!
\v 11 Tiṭṭawin inefxen n iwdan ad dd-ttwassehwant u acenneɛ n yeryazen ad ihwa. Ad ittwassɛuǧa SIDI waha \bd deg wass nni\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt Ica. 5:15\x*
\m 
\v 12 Maɣar ass i SIDI ad dd-yas x kuř bu-nnfaxet d umɛeffar u x kuř ijj wenni issɛuǧan ixef nnes, ḥima ad dd-ittwassehwa. \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Yuw. 2:10, 31; 3:15; Ica. 13:6-13; 24:23; Am. 8:9; Mt. 24:29; Řex. 2:20; Asa. 6:12-13\x*
\v 13 X marra ticejjura n tengelt yuɛřan d ittwassgeɛɛden \add n wedrar\add* n Lubnan, x marra ticejjura n řbeǧuḍ n Bacan,
\v 14 x marra idurar iɛeffaren, x marra tiwririn yuɛřan,
\v 15 x kuř lburj yuɛřan, x kuř řḥiḍ n lqelɛa,
\v 16 x marra iɣarruba n Tarcic u x marra řeqcuɛ iɣřan.
\b
\m 
\v 17 Nnfaxet n bnadem ad tessehwa u iryazen iɛeffaren ad ttwassehwan. Ad ittwassɛuǧa SIDI waha \bd deg wass nni\bd*.
\v 18 L’aṣnam ad ttwabeḍřen marra.
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* ad dd-adfen deg ifran n řejruf d iḥfrawen n temmurt zi ssibbet n usnexřiɛ n SIDI u zi ssibbet n uɛuǧi n lɛaḍama nnes, xmi Netta ad dd-ikkar ḥima ad issnexřeɛ tammurt. \x ◘ \xo 2:19 \xt Asa. 6:15-17\x*
\m 
\v 20 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad inḍar bnadem l’aṣnam nnes n nnuqart d l’aṣnam nnes n wureɣ, inni ggin i yixef nsen ḥima ad asen bendqen, \add ařami i ɣa yiřin\add* i ijarbuɛen d řweḍwaḍat,
\v 21 maḥend ad dd-adfen di tezziyin n řejruf u deg ifran deg weẓru zi tiggʷudi n SIDI u zi ssibbet n řɛezz n lɛaḍama nnes, xmi dd ɣa ikkar ḥima ad issnexřeɛ tammurt.”
\b
\m 
\v 22 “Ḥeyydem x bnadem, wenni deg wenzaren nnes iǧa mɣir nnefs, minzi min iɛna netta qaɛ ad xas neḥseb?”
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Imseyyaren iɛeffanen n Urcalim
\m 
\v 1 “Maɣar xzar, Sidi, SIDI n řɛeskarat, ad ikkes x Urcalim d Yahuda qaɛ aɛekkaz d qaɛ taɣɣarct, qaɛ tamewciwt s ufus n weɣrum d qaɛ tamewciwt s ufus n waman,
\v 2 bu-teɣruḍt d uɛeskari, řqaḍi d unabi, agezzan d umɣar,
\v 3 ameqqran x xemsin d bu-ccan, amcawar, bu-ṣṣenɛet d wenni ɣar iǧa řefhamet n tḥessect n uɛezzem.
\v 4 Necc ad xasen ggeɣ iḥuḍriyyen d řḥukkam nsen u nitni ad xasen sellṭen am mammec ttexsen nitni.
\v 5 Xenni di řgens ad ḥsaren ijj i wenneɣni, aryaz i weryaz \add nneɣni\add*, kuř ijj i jjar nnes. Nitni ad hekkweřen ijj i wenneɣni, aḥudri i uwessar, wenni ittwasseḥqaren i wenni ittwacennɛen.
\v 6 Xmi ɣa icebbar ca n yijjen umas di taddart n babas, \add ad yini\add*: ‘Cek ɣarek \add ɛad\add* ijj n upartessu, ittxeṣṣa ad tiřid d amgewwed xaneɣ. Arr řxarbet-a sadu afus nnec!’, \f ◼ \fr 3:6 \fk Arr řxarbet-a ...\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Ḥḍa x řxarbet-a sadu ifassen nnec’\f*
\v 7 \add xenni\add* ad yagi netta \bd deg wass nni\bd*, ad yini: ‘Necc war zemmareɣ ad iřiɣ d amesgenfu. War din bu weɣrum u war din bu warruḍ di taddart inu. War d ayi teggem d amgewwed n řgens!’
\v 8 Maɣar tennedref \add tendint n\add* Urcalim u tewḍa Yahuda, minzi iřes nsen d tmegga nsen aqa aten ḍidd i SIDI maḥend ad sɛaren tiṭṭawin n uɛuǧi nnes.
\v 9 Tifras n iɣembab nsen cehhdent xasen. Am Sadum ssawařen nitni s bṭayṭay x ddnub nsen, war ten ssnuffaren. Uct x řeɛmar nsen, maɣar nitni tteggen řɣar deg yixef nsen.”
\m 
\v 10 “Inim i umsegged aqa ad yiři mliḥ, aqa ad ccen \add s yixef nsen\add* řɣiǧet n tmegga nsen.
\v 11 Uct x uɛeffan. Uct xas, maɣar ad t xeǧṣen ɛlaḥsab \add min ggin\add* ifassen nnes.
\v 12 Inni ideǧen řgens inu aqa aten d iḥenjiren, uca timɣarin ttṣellṭent xas. \add A\add* řgens inu, inni cek ineddhen, aqa ttɣarran cek, uca řatar n tbridin nnec messḥen t.”
\m 
\v 13 “SIDI iwjed ḥima ad icarreɛ, Netta ibedd ḥima ad icarreɛ řegnus.
\v 14 SIDI ad dd-yarfeɛ ddeɛwet ak-d imɣaren n řgens u ak-d řḥukkam nnes, maɣar kenniw tesscemḍem amarjeɛ n uḍiř u min tucarem i imezřaḍ aqa-t di tudrin nwem.
\v 15 Min kenniw yuɣin, aqa třebbzem řgens inu u tᵉtteffẓem iɣembab n imezřaḍ?, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat.”
\b
\s1 Timɣarin timɛeffarin n Urcalim
\m 
\v 16 \add Ammu\add* i iqqar SIDI: “Minzi yessis n Ṣihyun daysent nnfaxet, ggurent s irawen geɛɛden, s řexzrat ttɣarrant, am ttraḥent u ttqezqizent s iṣuraf maḥend ad ssṭenṭunent ixeřxařen n iḍaren nsent,
\v 17 ad yarr Sidi inu jdam x taceqquft n uzeǧif n yessis n Ṣihyun uca ad iɛarra SIDI řɛar nsent.”
\m 
\v 18 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad asent ikkes Sidi inu \add marra\add* řehzuṭ \add nsent\add*: ixeřxařen x iḍaren nsent d řizarat \add ttwaceddent\add* x tenyart d tezriwin timeẓyanin
\v 19 d texrazin di ṣṣifet n tuddimin d timeqyasin d lltamat
\v 20 d iḥewwaqen izewwqen i uzeǧif d ixerxařen d tḥezzamin d tziyyatin ittfuḥen d řeḥruz
\v 21 d txadin n ufus d texrazin n tenzarin
\v 22 d warruḍ n weydud d řizarat d tsebnay d iqurab
\v 23 d tisitin d werruḍ n řeqṭen azdad d tcuccay d funarat n uzeǧif.
\v 24 Deg wemcan \add n řefwaḥet\add* n balsam ad tiři arriḥet, deg wemcam n tḥezzamt \add ad yiři\add* wesɣun, deg wemcan n tcenkukin icuwwaren \add ad yiři\add* uzeǧif aqeccar, deg wemcan n werruḍ iwseɛ \add ad tiři\add* txancet \add n wecḍan\add* u deg wemcan n weẓri d uɛeǧem n wecmaḍ \add x teřmect\add*.
\v 25 Iryazen nnem ad wḍan s ssif u ayt n bu-teɣruḍt nnem deg umenɣi.
\v 26 Tiwwura nnes ad cetcant u ad ceḍnent uca nettat ad teqqim x temmurt s ifassen xwan.” \f ◼ \fr 3:26 \fk Tiwwura nnes\ft - ixs ad yini ‘tiwwura n Urcalim’ niɣ ‘tiwwura n Ṣihyun’.\f*
\b
\b
\c 4
\m 
\v 1 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad cebbarent sebɛa n temɣarin deg ijj n weryaz, ad qqarent: ‘Neccin ad necc aɣrum nneɣ u ad nessyarḍ ixef nneɣ, ejj aneɣ ad neksi isem nnec waha, ksi řefḍiḥet xaneɣ.’”
\b
\m 
\v 2 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad idweř UƔEDDU n SIDI d telwizt icewwaren, u řɣiǧet n temmurt d řɛezz d ucewwar i min innejmen n Israil.
\v 3 Min iqqimen n Ṣihyun d wenni iqqimen di Urcalim ɛad, ad asen inin: ‘D amqeddas!’, kuř ijj di Urcalim wenni ittwazemmemen i tudart.
\v 4 Xmi ɣa issird Sidi řexmej n yessis n Ṣihyun u ad isrir zi řwest n Urcalim idammen s Arruḥ n řeḥkam u s Arruḥ icemmḍen,
\v 5 xenni ad igg SIDI deg uziř ijj n useynu x marra Tazeddiɣt x wedrar n Ṣihyun u x tmesmunin nnes u s ǧiřet ddexxan d tissiqt n tmessi ittceɛciɛen, maɣar tiwa marra min iɛuǧen \add ad tiři\add* tqidunt i udurri n tesřit.
\v 6 Ad yiři uɛiccu i tiři s uziř zi řeḥmu u i wemcan n tarewřa d udurri zi řḥemřet d wenẓar.”
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Taddart n Israil: amarjuɛ n uḍiř n SIDI
\m 
\v 1 “Ttexseɣ ad ɣennjeɣ \add izři\add* i llif inu, izři n llif inu x \add umarjeɛ\add* nnes n uḍiř:
\b
\m \qt ‘Llif inu ɣares ijj n umarjeɛ n uḍiř\qt*
\m \qt x ijj n wedrar i dd-ittwassgeɛɛden\qt*
\m \qt am ijj n yicc n ijj n mmis \tl dehnen t\tl* s zzect.\qt* \f ◼ \fr 5:1 \fk s zzect\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘n zzect’.\f*
\m 
\v 2 \qt Netta inqec i-t u iṣeffa i-t zeg iẓra,\qt*
\m \qt iẓẓu t s tzayarin icennɛen.\qt*
\m \qt Netta issbedd ijj n lburj di řwesṭ nnes.\qt*
\m \qt Inqec dayes tasirt \tl n uḍiř\tl*.\qt*
\m \qt Xenni tuɣa issitim,\qt*
\m \qt aḥwic n tzayart ad dd-yawi aḍiř,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* netta yiwi-dd aḍiř asemmam.’”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 3 “\add Xenni\add* řexxu, \add a\add* imezdaɣ n Urcalim d \add kenniw\add* iryazen n Yahuda, ḥekmem jar ayi d umarjeɛ inu n uḍiř!
\v 4 Min zemmareɣ Necc ɛad ad ggeɣ i umarjeɛ inu n uḍiř nni war d as ggiɣ ɛad? Mayemmi ssitimeɣ aqa ad dd-yawi aḍiř mliḥ, \add umi\add* dd yiwi mɣir aḍiř asemmam? \x ◘ \xo 5:4 \xt Irm. 2:5; Mixa 6:3, 8\x*
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, Necc xseɣ ad awem ssecneɣ min ɣa ggeɣ ak-d umarjeɛ inu n uḍiř: Necc ad kkseɣ afray nnes i t iḥḍan, ḥima ad t řeqḍen qaɛ, ad ggeɣ ict n tazzit di řḥiḍ ař xas i ɣa ɛefsen. \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt Izhd. 80:13\x*
\v 6 Ad t ggeɣ d řexřa, war t zebbaren niɣ ad t carzen, \add maca\add* tazeggʷart d isennanen ad dinni ɣemyen u Necc ad umureɣ iseynuten maḥend war d as tticen anẓar.
\v 7 Maɣar amarjeɛ n uḍiř n SIDI n řɛeskarat d taddart n Israil u iryazen n Yahuda d taɣeddut min xef yarḍa. Iraja řḥeqq, \add maca\add* xzar, tuɛeffna, \add iraja\add* tasegda, \add maca\add* xzar, tɣuyyit.” \x ◘ \xo 5:7 \xt Izhd. 80:9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 8 “\bd Uct\bd* x yinni ittseddan taddart ɣar taddart u arennyen iyyar ɣar yeyyar, ař tafed war da iǧi wemcan ɛad u kenniw waha i izeddɣen di řwesṭ n temmurt! \x ◘ \xo 5:8 \xt Mixa 2:2\x*
\v 9 Inna ayi SIDI n řɛeskarat deg imezzuɣen inu: ‘S tidett, aṭṭas n tudrin ad dewřent d řxirbet issaggʷaden, \add tudrin\add* timeqqranin d tinni icnan war daysent izeddeɣ ɛad uřa d ijj.’
\v 10 Minzi ɛecra n ifeddanen n umarjeɛ n uḍiř ad awyen mɣir ijj n ubatu, u ijj n uḥumir n zzarriɛet ad yawi mɣir ijj n ifa \add n řḥebb n irden\add*.” \f ◼ \fr 5:10 \fk abatu\ft - ijj n ‘ubatu’ ɛraḥař 20 niɣ 40 litru.\f*
\m 
\v 11 “\bd Uct\bd* x yinni ikkaren zic, arezzun x ccrab u ttɣiman \add wsewsen\add* ař tbambast, \add ař\add* ten isseḥma binu! \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt Awřn. 23:29,30\x*
\v 12 Řgambri d lharpa d ubendir d temja d binu aqa aten ɣar zzradi nsen, \add maca\add* min ittegg SIDI war ɣares xezzaren, tameggit n ifassen nnes, war tt ttwiřin.
\v 13 S uya ad ittwandeh řgens inu di lmenfa, minzi war ɣares teǧi tussna. Tarwa n taṣiřet n řgens ad heyyfen, ad yaẓeɣ ubarru nsen s ufadi. \x ◘ \xo 5:13 \xt Ɛam. 6:7\x*
\v 14 S uya i ɣa tarzem řaxart aṭṭas tmijja nnes, ad yarzem aqemmum nnes nhřa řeqyas, maḥend ad dayes ihwa řɛezz nnes d ubarru nnes d ddriz nnes d \add marra\add* inni dayes ineggzen \add ammu\add* s řefraḥet.
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* ad ixnes bnadem uca \add kuř\add* aryaz ad ittwassehwa, uca tiṭṭawin n ayt n bu-nnfaxet ad dewřent xezzarent ɣar swadday.
\v 16 \add Maca\add* SIDI n řɛeskarat ad ittwassɛuǧa s řḥeqq u Arebbi d amqeddas ad uttwaqeddes s tsegda.
\v 17 Ad hedden dinni izmaren am \add ttheddan\add* x tkessawt nsen, uca ibarraniyyen ad ccen řexrabi n ayt n bu-wagřa.” \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt Ica. 14:30\x*
\m 
\v 18 “\bd Uct\bd* x yinni \add ɣarsen\add* dd-ijebbden řmuɛṣiyyet s tesɣunin n řɣecc uřa d ddenb s iseɣwan \add iqebbuzen\add* n ukarru n iɛejmiyyen,
\v 19 inni iqqaren: ‘Ejj i-t ad yazzeř, ejj i-t ad t igg deɣya ḥima ad t nẓar, uca ccwar n Umqeddes n Israil ejj i-t ad ixecc, ad dd-yas, ḥima ad t nessen!’”
\m 
\v 20 “\bd Uct\bd* x yenni, min war iḥřin qqaren as iṣbeḥ u min iṣebḥen war iḥři, inni itteggen taǧest d tfawt u tafawt d taǧest, inni itteggen min yarzigen d miẓid u min iziḍen d amarzag.”
\m 
\v 21 “\bd Uct\bd* x yinni umi ittɣiř asen aqa aten d imiɣisen i yixef nsen, u \add uct x yinni iḥessben\add* ixef nsen d ifehhamen!” \x ◘ \xo 5:21 \xt Awřn. 3:7; Rum. 12:16\x*
\m 
\v 22 “\bd Uct\bd* x yinni iǧan d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt ɣar tsessit n binu u \add x\add* yeryazen imeḥḍen ɣar weḥray n ccrab,
\v 23 inni ittsarraḥen i uɛeffan s terzeft \add iɣeccen\add*, \add maca\add* kksen tasɣart i imseggaden.” \x ◘ \xo 5:23 \xt Awřn. 17:15; 24:24\x*
\b
\m 
\v 24 “S uya i ɣa ixsar weẓwar nsen u tanewwact nsen ad tᵉḍuw am tɛejjajt, am mammec ittett iřes n tmessi iɣeǧ u am mammec ihekkwa wurum s uceɛɛař, maɣar nitni nḍaren Ccariɛa n SIDI n řɛeskarat u sseḥqaran zeg wawařen n Umqeddas n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 5:24 \xt Uf. 15:7; Ica. 9:18\x*
\v 25 X uya yarɣa weɣḍab n SIDI x řgens nnes uca iksi xas afus nnes. Aqa iwta i-t ařami arjijen idurar u řxecbat nsen meddent x imesraq am wefraḍ. \bd S marra aya war yarexxu weɣḍab nnes, \bdit maca\bdit* afus nnes iqqim isarreḥ.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 5:25 \xt Ica. 9:11, 16, 20; 10:4, 6\x*
\v 26 Maɣar ad issgeɛɛed taɛeǧant i řegnus nni iǧan di řaggʷaj, u zeg uneggaru n temmurt ad t iṣeffar ɣares. Xzar, ittas-dd deɣya s tezřa.
\v 27 War ɣares yuḥiř uřa d ijj, uřa d ijjen inqarḍ, uřa d ijjen innudem niɣ iṭṭeṣ, uřa ɣar ijjen war ifsi abyas x tejɛinna nnes niɣ iqeṭṭes as ijj n ufiřu n sandaliyat nnes.
\v 28 Fřitcat nnes qeḍɛent u marra řeqwas nnes ttwameḥḥḍen. Ticeḍyin n yeysan nnes banent qesḥent am uqayas, tijarrarin nnes am tḥaryaḍt.
\v 29 Zzhir nnes am \add zzhir n\add* teyradt u \add netta\add* ittzehhar am yiyraden imeẓyanen. Ad yarruǧed, ad iṭṭef taymart nnes uca ad \add tt\add* ijarr u war ittiři wi t ɣa ifekken.
\v 30 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad izehhar ḍidd \add řgens\add* am zzhir n řebḥar. Ad xezzaren ɣar temmurt, aqa-tt \add mɣir d\add* taǧest d řeḥṣaret, uca tafawt ad tebbarcen s iseynuten ibbarecnen.” \x ◘ \xo 5:30 \xt Ica. 8:22\x*
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Tařaɣit n Arebbi x Icaɛya
\m 
\v 1 Deg useggʷas n řmewt n ujeǧid Ɛuzziya ẓriɣ SIDI iqqim x řɛarc yuɛřan ittwassgeɛɛden uca afray n warruḍ nnes ittcur Zzawect Tameqqrant. \x ◘ \xo 6:1 \xt 2 Ij. 15:7\x*
\v 2 Tiwa nnes bedden isarafiyyen, \add lmalakat nni ittbanen am daysen timessi\add*, ɣarsen setta n wafriwen. Qaɛ ijj ɣares setta n wafriwen. S tnayen \add n wafriwen\add* iřeḥḥef aɣembub nnes, s tnayen iřeḥḥef iḍaren nnes u s tnayen tuɣa iṭṭaw. \f ◼ \fr 6:2 \fk Isarafiyyen\ft - ijj n marka n lmalakat inni ittbanen amecnaw daysen tmessi.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 6:2 \xt Asa. 4:8\x*
\v 3 Iřaɣa ijj x wenneɣni, inna: “Amqeddas, Amqeddas, Amqeddas d SIDI n řɛeskarat. Marra tammurt teccur s uɛuǧi nnes!”, \x ◘ \xo 6:3 \xt Asa. 4:8\x*
\v 4 ařami nhezzen dsusa n tnebdatin n tewwart s tmijja n wenni iřaɣan uca Taddart teccur s ddexxan.
\m 
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ necc: “\bd Uct\bd* xafi, maɣar ad hellkeɣ, maɣar necc d aryaz bu-iyencicen xemjen u zeddɣeɣ jar řgens n ayt n bu-iyencicen xemjen, \add waxxa amenni\add* tiṭṭawin inu ẓrint Ajeǧid, SIDI n řɛeskarat.”
\v 6 Iḍwa-dd ijj zeg isarafiyyen ɣari. Yarbu řefḥem itteḥduduqen deg ufus nnes nni tuɣa iksi s tjeqqaḍt zeg uɛalṭar.
\v 7 Netta iḥada zzayes aqemmum inu, inna: “Xzar, iḥada \add řefhem itteḥduduqen\add* wanita iyencicen nnec. Temmeksi řmuɛṣiyyet nnec u ittwasseṣřeḥ i ddenb nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 6:7 \xt Irm. 1:9; Dan. 10:16\x*
\m 
\v 8 Awarni uya sřiɣ i tmijja n Sidi inu, teqqar: “Man wen i ɣa ssekkeɣ u wi ɣa yuyuren maḥend ad izwar i Neccin?” \add Xas uca\add* nniɣ: “Xzar, aqa ayi da, sekk ayi!”
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Uyur uca tinid i řgens-a: ‘Waxxa ad tesřem s teynit, war \add t\add* tfehhmem!’, uca: ‘Waxxa teẓrim mliḥ, war \add t\add* tessinem!’\x ◘ \xo 6:9 \xt Mt. 13:14; Mk. 4:12; Lk. 8:10; Yḥ. 12:40 Řex. 28:26; Rum. 11:8\x*
\v 10 Seqseḥ uř n řgens-a, uca belleɛ as imezzuɣen nnes, seřseq as tiṭṭawin maḥend s tiṭṭawin nnes war ittwiři u s imezzuɣen nnes war ittesři u s wuř nnes war ittessen, ařami war iddikkwiř uca ad ittwassgenfa.” \x ◘ \xo 6:10 \xt Irm. 5:21\x*
\m 
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ: “Ař meřmi, \add a\add* Sidi inu?” Netta yarra-dd: “Ař i ɣa ttwaxarrbent tneddam, war \add daysent\add* ittɣimi ɛad umezduɣ, uřa d tudrin, war \add daysent\add* ittɣimi ɛad bnadem, uca ad tiři temmurt tareddeǧ.
\v 12 Maɣar SIDI ad issbeɛɛed iwdan ɣar řaggʷaj, uca ad tiři temmurt texwa aṭṭas.
\v 13 \add Maca\add* ad dayes teqqim ɛad ict n teɛcart, \add maca\add* uřa d man aya ad tᵉttwacc, \add maca\add* am mammec ɣar tcejjart n yigg u ɣar tcejjart n řbeǧuḍ awarni řami tent i ɣa zedmen, ad iqqim ɛad jjdeɛ, \add ammu\add* i ɣa yiři jjdeɛ nnes d zzariɛet tamqeddest.”
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Řeɛřamet n Ɛimmanu-Il
\m 
\v 1 Deg wussan n Aḥaz, mmis n Yutam, mmis n Ɛuzziya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, igeɛɛed Raṣin, ajeǧid n Aram, ak-d Faqaḥ, mmis n Ramalyahu, ajeǧid n Israil, ɣar Urcalim maḥend ad immneɣ akides. \add Maca\add* netta war izemmar ad xas iɣelleb. \x ◘ \xo 7:1 \xt 2 Ij. 16:5; 2 Im. 28:5\x*
\v 2 \add Umi\add* ḥajan i taddart n Dawud, nnan: “Aqa ihwa Aram x Ifrayim!”, yarjij wuř n ujeǧid d wuř n řgens nnes, am mammec ttarjijint tcejjura n wezɣar s usemmiḍ. \f ◼ \fr 7:2 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\m 
\v 3 Inna SIDI i Icaɛya: “Ffeɣ i umsagar ak-d Aḥaz, cek d mmic Ca’ar-Yacub, ɣar uneggar n uqadus n waman n uyeřman n sennej, wenni \add iǧan\add* ɣar webrid yuɛran ɣar Weḥwic n Uṣebban.
\v 4 Ini as: ‘Ḥḍa, ars, war tteggʷed ca u war ttejji uř nnec ad yarxu x tnayen n isefḍawen n ukeccuḍ idduxxunen, x uxeyyeq yarɣin n Raṣin d Aram, u n mmis n Ramalyahu,
\v 5 umi ixarreṣ Aram di řɣar xak, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d Ifrayim u ak-d mmis n Ramalyahu, inna:
\v 6 ‘Ejj aneɣ ad ngeɛɛed x \add temmurt n\add* Yahuda uca ad as nessiggʷed uca ad tt nebḍa jar aneɣ u \add xenni\add* ad negg dinni mmis n Ṭabyil d ajeǧid.’
\v 7 Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Aya war ittiři, aya war ittemmsar ca!’
\v 8 Maɣar azeǧif n Aram d Dimacq u azeǧif n Dimacq d Raṣin - waxxa ammenni iqqim ɛad mɣir xemsa u-settin n iseggʷusa xenni ad yarẓ Ifrayim ař war ittiři \add ɛad\add* d řgens -
\v 9 uca azeǧif n Ifrayim d Samarya u azeǧif n Samarya d mmis n Ramalyahu. Mařa war tuminem, war tᵉttɣimam ad tbeddem.”
\m 
\v 10 Yarni SIDI \add ɛad\add* deg wawař ak-d Aḥaz, inna:
\v 11 “Ttar ict n řeɛřamet i yixef nnec zi SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ttar i-tt swadday di raǧaɣ niɣ ttar i-tt dinni sennej di řuɛřa.”
\v 12 \add Maca\add* Aḥaz inna: “Necc war tt ttᵉttareɣ ca u war ttqeǧabeɣ SIDI.”
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* inna netta: “Sřem, \add kenniw\add* \add a\add* taddart n Dawud, ma war kenniw iqedd ad tessiḥřem iwdan, aqa kenniw tessiḥřem \add ɛawed\add* uřa AREBBI inu?
\v 14 S uya ad awem iwc Sidi inu simant nnes řeɛřamet. Xzar, taɛzarect ad teysi ddeyset, ad taru Mmis, ad as tegg ‘Ɛimmanu-Il’, \add ixs ad yini ‘SIDI aqa-t akidneɣ’\add*. \x ◘ \xo 7:14 \xt Mt. 1:23; Lk. 1:31\x*
\v 15 Netta ad icc trussi d tamment ař ɣa iften ad inḍar min war iḥřin u ad ixḍar min iṣebḥen.
\v 16 Maɣar qbeř i ɣa issen uḥenjir ad inḍar min war iḥřin u ad ixḍar min iṣebḥen, ad texřa temmurt nni n tnayen n ijeǧiden i zi cek tᵉṭṭfed tiggʷudi.
\v 17 Ad issiweḍ SIDI xak u x řgens nnec u x taddart n babac s ufus n ujeǧid n Accur ussan am mammec war dd-usin zeg wass nni di immsebḍa Ifrayim x Yahuda.”
\m 
\v 18 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad imsar, aqa SIDI ad iṣeffar iẓan \add i iǧan\add* ɣar ineggura n iɣezran n Miṣra uřa d tzizwa \add i iǧan\add* di temmurt n Accur.
\v 19 Ad dd-asen uca ad arsen marra di teɣzurin u di tezziyin n řejruf u x marra řḥarrac u x marra iyeřmamen n řwarud.”
\m 
\v 20 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad awem iřs Sidi inu s ijj n řmuss i d icra x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, s \add ufus n\add* ujeǧid n Accur, \add acuwwaf n\add* uzeǧif d ucuwwaf x iḍaren uřa d tmart.”
\m 
\v 21 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* aryaz ad yarebba ict n tɛejmit n ifunasen d tnayen n wuǧi.
\v 22 S tyawant n uɣi i ɣa wcent, ad yecc trussi. Trussi d tamment ad yecc marra wi ɣa iqqimen di temmurt.”
\m 
\v 23 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad yiři kuř amcam i xef bedden ařef n tzayarin i isekkwan ařef n řewzan n nnuqart, i isennanen d tzeggʷart. \x ◘ \xo 7:23 \xt Lawi 26:22; Hgd. 8:11, 12\x*
\v 24 Ad uyuren ɣar din s fřitca d řqews, maɣar marra tammurt ad tiři teccur s isennanen d tzeggʷart.
\v 25 Uřa x marra tisawnin nni carrzen s uřizim, war din dd-ttasen \add ɛad\add* zi ssibbet n tiggʷudi zeg isennanen d tzeggʷart. \add Tammurt nni\add* ad tiři ḥima ad arren ɣar dinni ifunasen u ḥima ad \add xas\add* ɛefsen wuǧi.”
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Zzardet s tazřa, takeccaḍt deɣya
\m 
\v 1 Inna ayi SIDI: “Ksi tařwiḥt tameqqrant, tarid xas s řeqřem n bnadem \add ařami zemmaren ad t ɣaren\add*: ‘Zzardet s tazřa, takeccaḍt deɣya!’”
\v 2 Řechud imtiqqan iwyeɣ-ten d acehhad i yixef inu: akehhan Uriya d Zakariyya, mmis n Yabraxya.
\v 3 Tuɣa udfeɣ x tnabit u teksi s ddeyset, turuw-dd ijj n uḥenjir. Uca inna ayi SIDI: “Egg as: ‘Mahar-Calal, Xac-Baz!’, \add ixs ad yini: ‘Zzardet s tazřa, takeccaḍt deɣya!’\add*
\v 4 Maɣar qbeř ma ad iřmed uḥenjir ad yini: ‘Baba!’, niɣ: ‘Yemma!’, ad kksen agřa n Dimacq d zzardet n Samarya zzat i wudem n ujeǧid n Accur.”
\b
\m 
\v 5 Yarni SIDI deg wawař akidi, inna:
\v 6 “Minzi řgens-a isseḥqar aman yarsan ittazzřen n Ciluha, s uya ifarḥ Raṣin d mmis n Ramalyahu.
\v 7 S uya, xzar, Sidi inu ad yarr aman yewɛaren d imeqqranen n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* ad xasen ḥemřen, \add ixs ad yini\add* ajeǧid n Accur d marra aɛuǧi nnes. Ad igeɛɛed zi marra taryiwin nnes u ad dd-issfiy tiwa n marra timuwwa nnes.
\v 8 Ad yadef ɣar Yahuda, ad tt issɣarq uca ad yarni ad ɣares dd-yazzeř ař dd-as i ɣa yaweḍ ař yiři. Xmi ɣa isswiẓẓeḍ afriwen nnes ad dřen tiru n temmurt nnec! \add A Ɛimmanu-Il\add*, Arebbi aqa-t akideneɣ.”
\m 
\v 9 “Hajam, \add a kenniw\add* řegnus, \add maca ɛad\add* ad tᵉttwařebzem! Ejj marra jjwayeh iggʷejen n ddunect ad wcen imezzuɣen nsen: waxxa tḥezzmem ixef nwem, ad tᵉttwařebzem, waxxa tḥezzmem ixef nwem, ad tᵉttwařebzem!
\v 10 Mcawarem, \add maca\add* amcawar nwem ad ifceř! Inim ijj n wawař, war ittiři, maɣar Arebbi aqa-t akidneɣ, \add ‘Ɛimmanu-Il’\add*.”
\b
\s1 Řumur n SIDI i Icaɛya
\m 
\v 11 Maɣar ammu i d ayi inna SIDI, umi xafi ijhed ufus nnes u iɛřem ayi ḥima war ggureɣ x webrid n řgens-a, inna:
\v 12 “War qqarem ‘Tameɛmuč!’ i marra umi iqqar řgens-a ‘Tameɛmuč!’ War tteggʷedem u war ttnexřiɛem!
\v 13 SIDI n řɛeskarat ad t tessqeddsem, ad zzayes teggʷedem u ad zzayes tennxeřɛem.
\v 14 Netta ad yiři d Zzawect Iqeddsen, d aẓru n unedraf uřa d taṣḍart n uneqraḍ i tnayen n tudrin n Israil, d řfex d tracca i imezdaɣ n Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 8:14 \xt Ica. 28:16; Lk. 2:34; Rum. 9:33; 1 Bṭ. 2:7\x*
\v 15 Aṭṭas jar asen ad nnqarḍen, ad wḍan, ad ttwarẓen, ad dewřen ɣar řfex uca ad nnaɣen.” \x ◘ \xo 8:15 \xt Mt. 21:44; Lk. 20:18\x*
\b
\m 
\v 16 “Cfen Cchadet, cemmeɛ Ccariɛa jar imeḥḍaren inu!”
\b
\m 
\v 17 “Necc ad rajiɣ SIDI, wenni iřeḥḥfen i uɣembub nnes zzat i taddart n Yaɛqub, xas i ɣa tecřeɣ.
\v 18 Xzar, necc d iḥenjiren nni d ayi iwca SIDI, aqa aneɣ neǧa i řeɛřamat d lmuɛjizat di Israil zi ssibbet n SIDI n řɛeskarat nni izeddɣen x wedrar n Ṣihyun.”\x ◘ \xo 8:18 \xt Ɛbr. 2:13\x*
\m 
\v 19 “Mařa nnan awem: ‘Seqsam inni issawařan ak-d imettan d igezzanen, inni ittweswisen u ittwecwicen!’, \add xenni ini:\add* ‘Ma war dd-yusi i yijj n řgens ad isseqsa Arebbi nnes? Ma \add iɛeddeř ad sseqsan\add* imettan di ṭṭweɛ n yinni iddaren?’”\x ◘ \xo 8:19 \xt Aɛwd. 18:11\x*
\b
\m 
\v 20 “\add Dewřem\add* ɣar Ccariɛa u ɣar Cchadet! Mařa war uyuren ɛlaḥsab awař-a, war ɣarsen tᵉttiři tfawt n řefjar.”
\b
\m 
\v 21 “Ad inneḍ \add řgens\add* da d diha \add di temmurt\add*, icḍen u iǧuz, uca mařa iǧuz uca ixeyyeq, ad inɛeř \add řgens\add* ajeǧid nnes d AREBBI nnes. Ma ad xzaren ɣar ujenna,
\v 22 niɣ ɣar temmurt, \add aqa da mɣir\add* řeḥṣaret d ṭṭřam, ṭṭřam issaggʷad. Ittwassuffeɣ \add řgens\add* ɣar tubbarcent.” \x ◘ \xo 8:22 \xt Ica. 5:30\x*
\m 
\v 23 “Maca war ittɣimi ṭṭřam issaggʷad mani teǧa řeḥṣaret \add řexxu\add*. Zic yiwi-dd Netta aseḥqar ɣar temmurt n Zabulun u ɣar temmurt n Naftali, ammu i ɣa yawi di řweqt i dd ɣa yasen ccan x webrid n řebḥar, x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, ɣar Ljalil n řegnus.” \x ◘ \xo 8:23 \xt Mt. 4:15\x*
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Axřaq n Lmasiḥ
\m 
\v 1 “Řgens i iddaren di taǧest, ad iẓar tafawt tameqqrant. Tiwa nni izeddɣen di temmurt n tiři n řmewt ad tareɣ tfawt. \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt Mt. 4:15, 16; Afa. 5:14\x*
\v 2 Cek ad temmarnid di řgens u ad tessemɣared řefraḥet. Nitni ad farḥen zzat i wudem nnec am mammec farḥen ɣar tmeyra, am mammec arecgen xmi beṭṭan takeccaḍt ...
\b
\m 
\v 3 \bd maɣar\bd* \add a\add*zayřu n ddqeř nnes d weɛmud x teɣruḍt nnes d uzeǧaḍ n uweqqaf nnes, aqa tarẓid ten am deg wass n Midyan, \x ◘ \xo 9:3 \xt Řqḍ. 7:22; Ica. 10:26\x*
\m 
\v 4 \bd maɣar\bd* kuř řbuṭa nni yudfen deg uzehhar n umenɣi u kuř apartessu nni marɣen deg idammen, ad ittwassarɣ, ad yiři d macca i tmessi,
\m 
\v 5 \bd maɣar\bd* ittwaru aneɣ-dd Uḥenjir, immewc aneɣ Mmis uca řeḥkamet tᵉttwassars x teɣruḍt nnes u ttřaɣan as Isem nnes: Řeɛjeb, Amcawar, Arebbi Ijehden, Babas n Řebda, Řḥakem n Řehna. \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt Ica. 11:2; 22:22; Lk. 2:10, 11; Yḥ. 4:10\x*
\v 6 I řemɣaret n řeḥkamet \add nnes\add* u i řehna \add nnes\add* war ittiři qeṭṭu x řɛarc n Dawud u x tgeldit nnes, ḥima ad tᵉttwaḍmen u ad tᵉttwassejhed s řḥeqq d tsegda, zi řexxu ař i řebda. Acḍar n SIDI n řɛeskarat ad igg aya.” \x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt 2 Ij. 19:31; Ica. 37:32\x*
\b
\s1 Afus n SIDI ḍidd i Ifrayim
\m 
\v 7 “Sidi inu issekk awař ḍidd i Yaɛqub uca iwḍa di Israil.
\v 8 Marra řgens ad \add t\add* issen, Ifrayim d imezdaɣ n Samarya nni iqqaren s nnfaxet u s wuř \add iccuren\add* s ukebbar:
\v 9 ‘\add Reḥyuḍ n\add* llajur wḍan, \add maca\add* ad \add ten\add* nebna \add ɛawed\add* s tṣuḍar ittwassuydan. Urtan n řexřa ttwazedmen, \add maca\add* ad neẓẓu ticejjura n tengelt deg wemcan nsen!’
\v 10 Ad xas issekkar SIDI iɣrimen n Raṣin u Netta ad issehweř řɛedyan nnes \add xas\add*.
\v 11 Aram zi ccarq u Ifilisṭiniyyen zi ḍeffar, ařami nitni ad ṣarḍen Israil qaɛ. \bd S marra aya war yarexxu weɣḍab nnes, \bdit maca\bdit* afus nnes iqqim isarreḥ,\bd* \f ◼ \fr 9:11 \fk ad ṣarden ... qaɛ\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ad ccen ... s marra aqemmum’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 9:11 \xt Ica. 5:25; 10:4\x*
\v 12 \add maɣar\add* řgens war dd-idikkwiř ɣar wenni t iwtin u nitni war arezzun SIDI n řɛeskarat.”
\m 
\v 13 “Ad iqess SIDI zi Israil azeǧif d ukennas, taseṭṭa n tini d uɣanim, deg ijj n wass.
\v 14 Awessar d wenni umi ɣa yiři ccan, aqa aten d azeǧif, uca anabi nni isseřmaden ixarriqen, netta d akennas.
\v 15 \add Maɣar\add* imgewwaden n řgens-a d imɣekkʷayen u inni zzaysen ittwanedhen ad ttwaṣarḍen.
\v 16 X uya war ifarreḥ Sidi inu x iḥudriyyen nsen, u war yareḥḥem x iyujiřen d tejjař nsen, maɣar marra nitni d imnafqen d iɛeffanen u kuř aqemmum issawař tubbuheřya. \bd S marra aya war yarexxu weɣḍab nnes, \bdit maca\bdit* afus nnes iqqim isarreḥ.\bd*”\x ◘ \xo 9:16 \xt Ica. 10:6\x*
\m 
\v 17 “Maɣar tuɛeffna tareqq am tmessi, tᵉttett isennanen d tzeggʷart, tessreqqa ixeccaben n wezɣar, \add ařami\add* ttgeɛɛaden di ddexxan. \f ◼ \fr 9:17 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 9:17 \xt Ica. 5:24; 24:6\x*
\v 18 S uduqqez \add n ufugem\add* n SIDI n řɛeskarat ad issqusbar tammurt uca řgens ad yiři d macca n tmessi. Uřa d ijjen war ittḥiwiř x wenneɣni.
\v 19 \add Waxxa\add* bnadem inehhec ɣar yefus, ad iqqim iǧuz. \add Waxxa\add* ittett ɣar uzeřmaḍ, war ttyiwinen nitni. Kuř ijj ad isarḍ aysum n uɣiř nnes.
\v 20 Manassa \add ad isarḍ\add* Ifrayim u Ifrayim \add ad isarḍ\add* Manassa uca tnayen idsen munen ad iřin ḍidd i Yahuda. \bd S marra aya war yarexxu weɣḍab nnes, \bdit maca\bdit* afus nnes iqqim isarreḥ.\bd*”
\b
\b
\c 10
\m 
\v 1 “\bd Uct\bd* x yinni issuffuɣen řumurat iɣeccen, inni ittarin tiweṣṣa ittḍeǧen
\v 2 ḥima ad ssḥeyyden imezřaḍ x tesɣart \add nsen\add* u ḥima ad acaren tasɣart n yinni ittwaḥṣaren n řgens inu, ařami ɣa dewřent tijjař d takeccaḍt nsen u iyujiřen d taymart.
\v 3 \add Maca\add* min texsem ad teggem deg wass n uxeǧeṣ u ɣar ureddeǧ nni dd ɣa yasen zi řaggʷaj? Wi ɣar i ɣa tarewřem ḥima ad tafem twiza u mani ɣa tejjem aɛuǧi nwem?
\v 4 War \add din\add* min ɣa ggen mɣir ad uḍaren \add x ifadden\add* waha jar imeḥbas u ad wḍan jar inni ittwanɣen. \bd S marra aya war yarexxu weɣḍab nnes, \bdit maca\bdit* afus nnes iqqim isarreḥ.\bd*”
\b
\m 
\v 5 “\bd Uct\bd* x Accur, azeǧaḍ n weɣḍab inu, aqa asxeḍ inu d aɛmud deg ifassen nsen!\x ◘ \xo 10:5 \xt Ica. 36:1; Irm. 25:9; Ḥiz. 21:14\x*
\v 6 Ad t ssekkeɣ ɣar řgens \add iccuren\add* s nnifaq u Necc ad t umureɣ x řgens i x idduqqez ufugem inu, maḥend ad acaren tukkarḍa u maḥend ad t keccḍen qaɛ u ad t ɛarran i uneɛfas am tɛejjajt x imesraq.
\v 7 Maca netta s yixef nnes war d as ittɣiř ammu u uř nnes ittxarreṣ mammec nneɣni, maɣar netta ɣares deg wuř mɣir řekḥeḍ u maḥend ad iqḍa x řegnus, war iǧi drus.
\v 8 Maɣar iqqar: ‘Ma war ǧin řḥukkam inu d ijeǧiden marra?
\v 9 Ma war \add imsar\add* i Kalnu amecnaw \add min imsaren\add* i Karkamic? Ma war \add imsar\add* i Ḥamat amecnaw \add min imsaren\add* i Arfad? Ma war \add imsar\add* i Samarya am \add min imsaren\add* i Dimacq?
\v 10 Am mammec afus inu iṭṭef tigeldawin n l’aṣnam nni zi ɛdunt řexyařat nsen ineqcen řexyařat n Urcalim d Samarya,
\v 11 ma war tteggeɣ ammu \add ɛawed\add*, am mammec i t ggiɣ ak-d Samarya d l’aṣnam nnes, uřa ak-d Urcalim d řexyařat nnes n l’aṣnam?’”
\m 
\v 12 “\add Maca\add* xmi ɣa ikemmeř Sidi marra řxedmet nnes x wedrar n Ṣihyun u di Urcalim, \add xenni\add* ad xeǧṣeɣ Necc řɣiǧet n ukebbar deg wuř n ujeǧid n Accur uřa d aɛeffar yuffen di tiṭṭawin nnes,
\v 13 maɣar netta inna: ‘Aya ggiɣ t s ufus inu ijehden u s tiɣit inu, maɣar necc ɣari řeɛqeř. Iymiren n řegnus kkseɣ ten, u řeɛwayeḍ nsen keccḍeɣ ten, u am jjiheř ɣeḍřeɣ řḥukkam \add nsen\add*.
\v 14 Am řɛucc, \add ammu\add* yufa ufus inu agřa n řegnus, jarweɣ marra tammurt am mammec jarwen timeǧařin immenḍaren. Uřa d ijj war issenhezzi afriwen, war din wenni yarezmen ajeqmim niɣ ijaw.’
\v 15 Ma ittfeyyec ccaqur qibač i wenni zzayes ittceqqaren? Niɣ ittneffex řmencar zzat i wenni zzayes ittqessen? \add Aya iři\add* axmi aɛmud ittḥenneḍ \add aryaz\add* nni t issgeɛɛden, niɣ axmi aɛmud issgeɛɛed \add bab nnes\add* nni war iǧin d akeccuḍ.”
\m 
\v 16 S uya ad issekk Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat, bu-deǧis jar iryazen nsen iqebbuzen u Netta ad issireɣ timessi sadu aɛuǧi n Accur am yijj n řḥaduq n tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt Ica. 24:6\x*
\v 17 Tafawt n Israil ad tedweř d timessi u Amqeddes nnes d aceɛɛař nni i ɣa icemḍen u ad tecc isennanen d tzeggʷart nnes deg ijj n wass waha.
\v 18 Netta ad yecc aɛuǧi n wezɣar nnes u n řɛirst iṣebḥen nnes s \add marra\add* řeɛmar d weysum \add i daysen\add*, uca ad yiři \add uɛuǧi nnes\add* am yijj n umeḥřuc ittraḥen iɣeǧi.
\v 19 Min iqqimen n tcejjura n wezɣar nnes ad yiři drus waha, ijj n uḥudri izemmar ad ten iḥseb.”
\m 
\v 20 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad yiři min iqqimen n Israil d inni inejmen zi taddart n Yaɛqub war ttɛemmiden ɛad x wenni ten iccaten, maca ad iɛemmed \add Israil\add* x SIDI, Amqeddas n Israil, s řaman iccur.
\v 21 Min iqqimen ad dd-idweř, min iqqimen n Yaɛqub \add ad dd-idweř\add* ɣar Arebbi ijehden.
\v 22 \add A\add* Israil, waxxa řgens nnec ammu iwseɛ am yiǧi n řebḥar, ad \add zzaysen\add* dd-idweř mɣir min iceṭṭen. Akeḥḥeḍ bayen, tasegda tewseɛ. \x ◘ \xo 10:22 \xt Rum. 9:27, 28\x*
\v 23 Maɣar Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat, ad iqḍa \add x man aya\add* uca ad igg min yuran di marra tammurt.” \x ◘ \xo 10:23 \xt Ica. 28:22\x*
\m 
\v 24 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘\add A\add* řgens inu nni izeddɣen di Ṣihyun, war tteggʷed ca zi Accur xmi cek iccat s uzeǧaḍ uca issgeɛɛed xak aɛmud, am mammec imsar di Miṣra.
\v 25 Maɣar ɛad mɣir cwayt, \add xenni\add* ad ikemmeř \add mkuř\add* wesxeḍ nni uca ad yiři weɣḍab inu x ureddeǧ nsen.
\v 26 Maɣar SIDI n řɛeskarat ad iḥenneḍ tiwa nnes arekkuḍ, am mammec iwta Midyan ɣar teṣḍart n Ɣurab. Taɣɣarct nnes ad tiři \add tesswiẓẓaḍ\add* tiwa i řebḥar u Netta ad tt issgeɛɛed am mammec t igga di Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 10:26 \xt Uf. 14\x*
\v 27 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad iwḍa řeḥmeř n Accur x teɣruḍt nnec u taɣnact nnes x yiri nnec. Azayřu ad ittwabeṭṭeř s ijiman nni iṣeḥḥen.”
\m 
\v 28 “Ad dd-yas ɣar Ɛayyat, iɛdu x Mijrun, issars dduzan nnes di Mixmac.
\v 29 Nitni ɛeddun x webrid n uẓekkwu x idurar, ad ssensen di Jabaɛ. Rama tᵉttarjiji, tarweř Jibɛa n Cawul.
\v 30 Sɣuyy s tmijja ijehden, \add a\add* yeǧis n Jallim! Arr řbař, Layca, \add a cem\add* Ɛanatut, meskina!
\v 31 \add Tandint n\add* Madmina tarweř, imezdaɣ n Jibim ffɣen maḥend ad afen řaman.
\v 32 Ass-a ɛad ad ibedd di Nub. Netta ad iksi afus nnes \add issaggʷad\add* ɣar wedrar n yeǧis n Ṣihyun, ɣar tewrirt n Urcalim.”
\m 
\v 33 “Xzar, Sidi, SIDI n řɛeskarat, ad iqess řefruɛ s uɣiř. Inni s tiddi yuɛřan ad ttwazedmen, uca inni issgeɛɛden ixef nsen ad ttwassehwan.
\v 34 Cbarq n wezɣar ad ittwaqřeɛ s wuzzař uca Lubnan ad iwḍa s ufus n Umzemmar.” \f ◼ \fr 10:34 \fk Lubnan\ft - ixs ad yini řɛeskar n Accur wenni dd-yusin zi jjihet n idurar n Lubnan inni yuɛřan x wedrar n Ṣihyun. Maca Lmalak n SIDI, Arebbi n Israil, iwta řɛeskar n Accur (xzar Ica. 37:36).\f*
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Řeḥkamet n řehna i dd ɣa yasen
\m 
\v 1 “Ad dd-teffeɣ Tseṭṭa zi jjdeɛ n Yassa u Taɣeddut zeg iẓewran nnes ad dd-tawi řɣiǧet. \x ◘ \xo 11:1 \xt Ica. 4:2; Řex. 13:22, 23\x*
\v 2 Ad xas yarsa Arruḥ n SIDI, Arruḥ n tiɣit d řeɛqeř, Arruḥ n ccwar d jjehd, Arruḥ n tussna d tiggʷudi zi SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 11:2 \xt Uf. 31:3; 35;13; 1 Kur. 12:8; Kul. 1:9\x*
\v 3 Arḍa nnes ad yiři di tiggʷudi n SIDI. War icarreɛ ɛlaḥsab min ttwařant tiṭṭawin nnes, war iḥekkem ɛlaḥsab min ttesřan imezzuɣen nnes.
\v 4 Ad icarreɛ imuqřiřen s tsegda u ad iḥkem imwaḍɛen n temmurt s řḥeqq, \add maca\add* tammurt ad tt iwwet s uzeǧaḍ n uqemmum nnes u s usuḍi n uqemmum nnes ad ineɣ aɛeffan.
\v 5 Tasegda ad tiři d abyas n tejɛinnatin nnes u tidett d abyas x tmeṣṣaḍin nnes.
\m 
\v 6 Ad izdeɣ wuccen ɣar izmar, aɣiras ad ijen ɣar iɣayḍ ameẓyan. Aɛejmi d wayrad ameẓyan d řmař iṣeḥḥen \add ad iřin\add* munen uca aḥenjir ameẓyan ad ten indeh. \f ◼ \fr 11:6 \fk aɛejmi\ft - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:6 \xt Ica. 65:25; Ḥuc. 2:20\x*
\v 7 Tafunast d ddub ad hdan \add jmiɛ\add*, uca imeẓyanen nsen ad jnen ɣar wayawya uca ayrad ad yecc řum am ufunas.
\v 8 Aḥḍiḍ ad yarr mezři zzat i wexbuc n třefsa u anibu i kksen zeg uṭṭuḍ, ad isswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes ɣar warzam n tfawt \add n weḥfur\add* n ufiɣar.
\m 
\v 9 War tteggen řɣar u war tteggen areddeǧ x wedrar inu iqeddsen marra, maɣar tammurt teccur s tussna n SIDI am mammec dřen waman tisi n řebḥar.
\v 10 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ibedd Weẓwar n Yassa am tɛeǧant i weyduden. Ɣares ad sseqsan řegnus uca amcan n arraḥet nnes ad yiři icewwar.” \x ◘ \xo 11:10 \xt Rum. 15:12\x*
\b
\m 
\v 11 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad issgeɛɛed Sidi inu afus nnes ict n twařa nneɣnit, ḥima ad isellek min iqqimen n řgens nnes zi Accur, Miṣra, Fatrus, Kuc, Ɛilam, Cinɛar d Ḥamat u zi tegzirin n řebḥar. \f ◼ \fr 11:11 \fk řebḥar\ft - niɣ ‘il’.\f*
\v 12 Netta ad issbedd taɛeǧant i řegnus u ad ijarw ɛawed imenneɛraq n Israil, ḥima ad issmun inni ittwazeǧɛen zi Yahuda zi arebɛa n tɣemmura n temmurt.
\m 
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* ad iggʷej wasam n Ifrayim u inni iḥeṣṣaren Yahuda ad ttwaqeḍɛen. Ifrayim war ittisem ɛad zi Yahuda u Yahuda war iḥeṣṣar ɛad Ifrayim.
\v 14 Ad ffɣen ɣar řɣarb axmi ṭṭawen x tɣarḍin n Ifilisṭiniyyen uca munen ad keccḍen ayt n ccarq. Ad sswiẓẓḍen ifassen nsen ɣar Idum d Mu’ab uca ayt n Ɛammun ad asen ṭṭaɛen.
\v 15 Ad iḥarrem SIDI iřes n řebḥar n Miṣra uca Netta ad issgeɛɛed afus nnes x yeɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* s uḥaduq n Arruḥ nnes u ad t iwwet ař ɣa idweř sebɛa n tɣezratin, uca ad yarr aqa zemmaren ad kken x webrid s sandaliyat. \x ◘ \xo 11:15 \xt Asa. 16:12-14. \x*
\v 16 Ad \add din\add* yiři webrid iseggmen i min iqqimen n řgens nnes nni i ɣa iceṭṭen zi Accur, am mammec tuɣa iǧa \add webrid\add* i Israil umi dd-igeɛɛed zi Miṣra.” \x ◘ \xo 11:16 \xt Uf. 14:29\x*
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Izři n uṣebbeḥ zi Ṣihyun
\m 
\v 1 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad tinid: ‘Necc ttqadiɣ Cek, \add a\add* SIDI, aqa tuɣa Cek txeyyqed xafi, \add maca\add* aɣḍab nnec inneqřeb u Cek tessfewwajed xafi.
\v 2 Xzar, Arebbi d asenjem inu, necc ad \add xas\add* ttecřeɣ, ɛemmarṣ ad ggʷedeɣ, maɣar SIDi inu, SIDI, aqa-t d jjehd d uzehhid inu, Netta idweř ayi d asenjem.’
\v 3 Kenniw ad taymem aman s řefraḥet zi tařawin n usenjem.” \x ◘ \xo 12:3 \xt Yḥ. 7:37,38\x*
\m 
\v 4 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad tinim: ‘Qadam i SIDI, řaɣam Isem nnes, secnem timegga nnes jar řegnus, barrḥem aqa Isem nnes iɛuǧa! \x ◘ \xo 12:4 \xt Yḥ. 17:1, 4, 6, 26\x*
\v 5 Zehhdem i SIDI, maɣar Netta igga timesřayin timeqqranin. Ejj aya ad ittwassen di marra tammurt.
\v 6 Sřiwřew u ɣennej, \add a cem\add* tenni izeddɣen di Ṣihyun, minzi d ameqqran Amqeddas n Israil di řwesṭ nnem.’”
\b
\b
\c 13
\m 
\v 1 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden x Babil\bd* nni iẓra Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ.
\m 
\v 2 “Sgeɛɛdem taɛeǧant x wedrar aqeccar, sɣuyyem ɣarsen, ceyyarem s ufus aqa ad adfen zi tewwura n tarwa n taṣiřet!”
\m 
\v 3 “Necc umureɣ imqeddasen inu, Necc řaɣiɣ x ayt n bu-teɣruḍt inu di ssibbet n weɣḍab inu, inni ineggzen s řefraḥet x lɛaḍama inu.”
\m 
\v 4 “Aqa zzhir n ijj n ubarru \add ameqqran\add* x idurar, am n ijj n řgens imɣar, řḥess n ddriz n tgeldawin, n řegnus usin-dd munen. SIDI n řɛeskarat isedd řɛeskar \add nnes\add*.
\v 5 Ad dd-asen zi temmurt tiggʷej, zi ṭṭarf n ujenna, SIDI d řeqcuɛ n wesxeḍ nnes, ḥima ad xarrben marra tammurt.”
\m 
\v 6 “Sɣuyyem, maɣar ass n SIDI yudes-dd, ad dd-yas am ureddeǧ zeg Umzemmar x kuřci. \x ◘ \xo 13:6 \xt Yuw. 2:10, 31; 3:15; Ica. 13:6-13; 24:23; Am. 8:9; Mt. 24:29; Řex. 2:20; Asa. 6:12-13\x*
\v 7 X uya dewřen marra ifassen fecřen u wuř n kuř bnadem ifessi.
\v 8 Nitni nnxeřɛen, iřeqqef i-ten weɣnas d řewjeɛ n tarut, ttnezbaren am temɣart ittarun. Kuř ijj ixezzar ɣar wenneɣni, iɣembab nsen \add ggin\add* am yiceɛɛařen \add n tmessi\add*.”
\m 
\v 9 “Xzar, ass n SIDI ad dd-yas, \add s\add* řeqsaḥet iwɛaren u \add s\add* řḥaduq n weɣḍab \add nnes\add*, ḥima ad yarr tammurt d wareddeǧ u ḥima ad zzayes imḥa imednab.
\v 10 Maɣar itran n ujenna d iwrafen n itran war ttejjin ɛad tafawt nsen ad tarɣ, tafuct ad tebbarcen xmi dd ɣa tenqar, uca taziri war ttejji ɛad tafawt nnes ad tceɛceɛ. \x ◘ \xo 13:10 \xt Ḥiz. 32:7; Yuw. 3:4; 3:15; Mt. 24:29; Mk. 13:24; Lk. 21:25\x*
\v 11 \add Maɣar\add* ad xeǧṣeɣ i ddunect tuɛeffna nnes u i iɛeffanen řmuɛṣiyyet nsen u Necc ad ssbeddeɣ nnfaxet n imɛeffaren u ad ssehwiɣ nnfaxet n ayt n bu-řexcunet.
\v 12 Ad arreɣ aryaz ad yiři iɣřa x wureɣ azdad, uřa d bnadem x wureɣ iɣřan zi Ufir.
\v 13 X uya ad ssarjijeɣ ijenwan uca ad tenhezz temmurt zeg wemcan nnes zeg uduqqez \add n ufugem\add* n SIDI n řɛeskarat u zeg wass n řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes.”
\v 14 “Am tɣayḍet n wezɣar injerfen, am wuǧi war ɣares dd-iksi uřa d ijj, \add ammu\add* i ɣa nnqeřben nitni kuř ijj ɣar řgens nnes u kuř ijj ad yarweř ɣar temmurt nnes.
\v 15 Qaɛ wenni i ɣa ittwafen, ad xas cuqen, u qaɛ wenni i ɣa ṭṭfen, ad iwḍa s ssif.
\v 16 Zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen ad ttwaddzen iḥenjiren nsen, ad ttwakeccḍent tudrin nsen u timɣarin nsen ad ttwassnuqqbent.”
\m 
\v 17 “Xzar, Necc ad xasen ssḥarrceɣ Imadiyyen, nitni war d asen tecqi nnuqart u ɣarsen nitni ureɣ war isekkwi.
\v 18 Řeqwas nsen ad xarrgen iḥudriyyen, war areḥḥmen ca x řɣiǧet n uɛeddis, u tiṭṭ nsen war tᵉttziǧiz i iḥenjiren.
\v 19 \add Tandint n\add* Babil, talwizt jar tgeldatin, \add tenni\add* d řɛezz d usemɣar n Ikaldaniyyen, ad tedweř am mammec řami tuɣa AREBBI issneqřeb Sadum d Ɛamurra. \x ◘ \xo 13:19 \xt Amz. 19:25; Ica. 1:9; Irm. 49:18; 50:40\x*
\v 20 I řebda war ittɣimi din uřa d ijj, war \add dayes\add* zeddɣen ɛad zi jjiř ař jjiř. Aɛrab war dinni iccit aqiḍun nnes \add ɛad\add* u imeksawen war ttejjin ad tareyyeḥ din \add tḥimart nsen\add* ɛemmarṣ. \x ◘ \xo 13:20 \xt Irm. 50:39\x*
\v 21 Řewḥuc n řexřa ad zzřen dinni u tizeddiɣin nsen ad ccurent s mukat, yessis n nnɛamet ad zedɣent dinni uca imuyan \add ijennen\add* ad dinni negzen.
\v 22 Ad ssmiɛɛiwen ifisen ijj ɣar wenneɣni di lqelɛat ittwajjen \add n Babil\add* uřa d uccanen n řexřa di řeqṣur n řehzuṭ. Řweqt nnes ad dd-taweḍ deɣya u ussan nnes war ttzuggarten ca.”
\b
\b
\c 14
\m 
\v 1 “Maɣar SIDI ad iḥinn x Yaɛqub uca ad ifarz Israil ɛad. Netta ad asen iwc řhudnet di temmurt nsen. Abarrani ad kidsen imun u nitni ad dewřen ɣar taddart n Yaɛqub.
\v 2 Řegnus ad ten awyen u ad \add ten\add* ssidfen ɣar wemcan nsen. Taddart n Israil ad ten tᵉṭṭef d tasɣart di temmurt n SIDI, am yisemɣan d tiyya. Ad ḥebbsen inni ten iḥebbsen, uca ad ḥekmen x inni ten iḥeṣṣaren.”
\m 
\v 3 “Deg wass i d ac i ɣa issareyyeḥ SIDI zi řeḥriq nnec, zeg unexřiɛ nnec u zi tsexxart nnec iqesḥen i zi ggin ad \add asen\add* tsexxared, \x ◘ \xo 14:3 \xt Aɛwd. 28:48\x*
\v 4 ad tessgeɛɛded amettiř-a x ujeǧid n Babil, ad tinid: ‘Mammec issbedd wenni iḥeṣṣaren zi \add řeḥṣaret\add* nnes, \add mammec\add* tᵉttwaqḍa řeqsaḥet?’
\v 5 Yarẓa SIDI aɛmud n iɛeffanen, azeǧaḍ n ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa,
\v 6 wenni iwtin řegnus deg ijj n uduqqez \add n ufugem\add* s tiyyita břa qeṭṭu, wenni tuɣa iḥekkmen x řegnus s weɣḍab, iḍaffar \add i-ten\add* břa aziǧez.
\v 7 Marra tammurt tarsa, tesqar. \add Xenni\add* duqquzen s řefraḥet.
\v 8 Uřa d ticejjura n umerzi farrḥent zzayek u ticejjura n tengelt n \add idurar n\add* Lubnan \add qqarent\add*: ‘Zeg wami cek tmedded ɣar temmurt, war da dd-ittis uřa d ijjen ɛad ḥima ad aneɣ yarẓ!’” \f ◼ \fr 14:8 \fk amerzi\ft - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*
\m 
\v 9 “Řaxart swadday ad tenhezz di ṭṭweɛ nnec, maḥend ad ffɣen nitni ɣar umsagar akidek xmi dd ɣa tased. Di ṭṭweɛ nnec ad tessfaq řexyařat \add n imettan\add*, marra řḥukkam n temmurt, ad tegg marra ijeǧiden n temmurt ad kkaren zi řekrasi nsen igellden.
\v 10 Nitni marra ad ṭṭfen deg wawař, ad ac inin: ‘Uřa d cek tdewřed tarehfed, am neccin, \add řexxu\add* cek tarewsed dayneɣ!’
\v 11 Aqa tmenḍar nnfaxet nnec di řaxart, řḥess n lharpat nnec. Sadu nnec ttwabezzɛen iwekkiwen \add am řemtaḥ\add*, u ikeccawen d malta nnec.
\v 12 Mammec \add teggid\add* tewḍid-dd zeg ujenna, \add cek,\add* \add a yitri n řefjar\add* ittseqsiqen, mmis n tuffut n řḥař! Mammec tᵉttwarẓed ɣar temmurt, \add cek\add* amarniw n řegnus!
\v 13 Tennid deg wuř nnec: ‘Necc ad geɛɛdeɣ ɣar ujenna, ad ssbeddeɣ řɛarc inu tiwa i yetran n Arebbi, ad qqimeɣ x wedrar n umuni ɣar ṭṭrufa n ccamal qaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 14:13 \xt Izhd. 48:3\x*
\v 14 Necc ad geɛɛdeɣ tiwa n tqiccatin n iseynuten, ad arwseɣ deg Umɛuǧi x kuřci!’
\v 15 Lla, ad cek dd-ssehwan di řaxart, di řaǧaɣ qaɛ n wanu!
\v 16 Inni cek i ɣa iẓaren, ad dayek jɛaren, ad fehmen \add uca ad inin\add*: ‘Ma wa d aryaz nni issarjijen tammurt, wenni ijjin tigeldin ad nhezzent,
\v 17 wenni yarrin tammurt d řexřa uca yareddeǧ tineddam nnes, wenni war yarxun i imeḥbas nnes ad arekkʷeḥen?’
\v 18 Marra ijeǧiden n řegnus, marra nitni zzřen \add din\add* di ccan, kuř ijj di taddart nnes.
\v 19 \add Maca\add* cek tmenḍared, ssiggʷejen cek x wenḍeř nnec, \add am\add* ict n nnɛi n tɣeddut \add mmenḍaren tt\add*, ssduryen tt s imettan ittwassnuqqben s ssif, inni dd ɣa ihwan ɣar iẓra n tesraft \add n wenḍeř\add*, am řxecbet i x ɛefsen.
\v 20 War temmarsed deg wenḍeř d ijjen akidsen, maɣar txarrbed tammurt nnec uca tenɣid řgens nnec. Zzariɛet n iɛeffanen ɛemmarṣ war tt ittidaren i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 14:20 \xt Ayub 18:19; Izhd. 21:11; 37:28; 109:13\x*
\v 21 Swejdem ṭṭabřa n tɣarṣt i iḥenjiren nnes x řmuɛṣiyyet n ibabaten nsen, maḥend nitni ɛemmarṣ war ttbeddin \add ɛad\add*, ad warten tammurt uca ad ccuren udem n temmurt s tneddam. \x ◘ \xo 14:21 \xt Uf. 20:5; Mt. 23:25\x*
\v 22 Necc ad xasen kkareɣ, \add ammu\add* i issawař SIDI n řɛeskarat, Necc ad teḥḥiɣ zi Babil \add kuř\add* isem d \add marra\add* min iqqimen, am mmis uřa d mmis n mmis, ammu i iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 14:22 \xt Ayub 18:19; Izhd. 21:11; 37:28\x*
\v 23 Necc ad arreɣ \add Babil\add* d tasɣart n twuct n ǧiřet uřa d iyeřmamen. Ad ten mḥiɣ s tmedwast n ureddeǧ, \add ammu\add* i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.” \x ◘ \xo 14:23 \xt Ica. 34:11; Ṣaf. 2:14\x*
\b
\m 
\v 24 SIDI n řɛeskarat ijjuǧ, inna “S tidett, am mammec Necc i tt xarrṣeɣ, ammu i ɣa imsar, am mammec Necc i tt uriɣ, ammu i dd ɣa yas.
\v 25 Aqa Necc ad arẓeɣ \bd Accur\bd* di temmurt inu u ad xas ɛefseɣ x idurar inu, ḥima \add a\add*zayřu nnes ad zzaysen ittwaksi u řeḥmeř nnes ad iwḍa x tɣarḍin nsen.
\v 26 Wa d acawar nni ittwaggen x marra tammurt u wa d afus i isswiẓẓḍen i marra řegnus.
\v 27 Maɣar SIDI n řɛeskarat ixarreṣ aya, man wen izemmaren ad t ibḍeř? Aqa afus nnes isswiẓẓaḍ i-t, man wen izemmaren ad t yarr \add ɣar uɣezdis\add*?” \x ◘ \xo 14:27 \xt 2 Im. 20:6; Ayub 9:12; Awřn. 21:30; Dan. 4:32\x*
\b
\s1 Awař n Arebbi x Filicit
\m 
\v 28 Deg useggʷas n řmewt n Aḥaz, yusa-dd řḥukm issaggʷaden wanita: \x ◘ \xo 14:28 \xt 2 Ij. 16:20\x*
\m 
\v 29 “War farreḥ, \add a cem,\add* marra \add tammurt n\add* \bd Filicit\bd*, aqa akeccuḍ nni cem iwtin, ittwarẓ, maɣar zeg weẓwar n ufiɣar ad dd-iffeɣ urefsiw amesmum u řɣiǧet nnes ad tiři d řḥaycet icemḍen iṭṭawen. \x ◘ \xo 14:29 \xt Ica. 30:6\x*
\v 30 Imenza n imuqřiřen ad hdan \add s řhudnet\add* uca imezřaḍ ad zzřen di řaman, \add maca\add* ad nɣeɣ aẓwar nnem s řaẓ uca \add arefsiw\add* ad ineɣ min zzayem iqqimen.”
\m 
\v 31 “Ru, \add a\add* tawwart, sɣuyy, \add a\add* tandint, aqa fecřen marra \add imezdaɣ n\add* Filicit! Maɣar zi ccamal ad dd-yas ddexxan uca uřa d ijjen ad yaggʷej zeg iseddiyyen nnes n řɛeskar.”
\m 
\v 32 “Min i dd ɣa yarren x ireqqasen n řgens?”
\m “Aqa SIDI igga \add dsas\add* n Ṣihyun ḥima řmusakin n řgens nnes ad ɣares arewřen!”
\b
\b
\c 15
\m 
\v 1 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden x Mu’ab.\bd*
\m “Di ǧiřet ittwahdem Ar-Mu’ab, idweř issusem, wah, di ǧiřet ittwahdem Qir-Mu’ab, idweř issusem! \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt Irm. 48:1; Ḥiz. 25:9; Ɛam. 2:1\x*
\v 2 Geɛɛden ɣar Bayit d Dibun, ɣar řegɛudi ḥima ad run. \add Dinni\add* ad iru Mu’ab x Nabu d Maydaba. Qaɛ azeǧif nsen iřsa d aqeccar, marra timira ttwaḥeffent. \x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt Irm. 48:37; Ḥiz. 7:18\x*
\v 3 Beysen s txuncay \add n wecḍan\add* deg izniqen nsen, aqa \add din\add* mɣir tɣuyyit x tzeɣwin nsen u deg wazzayen nsen, imeṭṭawen weṭṭan-dd \add x uɣembub\add*.
\v 4 Ḥacbun isɣuyyu, uřa d Aliɛala. Ttesřan i tmijja nsen ař Yahaṣ. X uya sɣuyyun \add uřa d\add* iryazen n Mu’ab nni ɣar iǧa řesnaḥ, buḥbeř \add n mkuř aryaz\add* ifceř dayes.”
\m 
\v 5 “Uř inu isɣuyyu x Mu’ab. Imarwařen nnes iwḍen ař \add tandint n\add* Ṣuɣar, \add tenni iǧan am\add* taɛejmit n třata n iseggʷusa. Am ttrun ttgeɛɛaden tasawent n Luḥit, \add wah,\add* deg webrid ɣar Ḥurunayim ssgaɛɛaden nitni taɣuyyit n txessart.
\v 6 Wah, aman n Nimrim ad dewřen imucan xřan, \add wah,\add* arbiɛ isřaw, aɣemmuy n arbiɛ iqḍa, war ittiři ɛad uɣemmuy aziza.
\v 7 X uya ad arbun min iceṭṭen d min \add ɛad\add* ɣarsen, ɣar ujemmaḍ n iɣzar n Iṣefṣafen.
\v 8 Wah, ad dd-teffeɣ tɣuyyit n ucetci di temmurt n Mu’ab, aweɛɛeḍ nnes \add ad dd-iffeɣ\add* ař Ajlayim, aɣuyyi s imeṭṭawen ař Bi’r-Ilim.
\v 9 Ɛad ccuren waman n Dimun s idammen, waxxa Necc ad arenyeɣ x Dibun ɛad ktar: ayrad \add ad dd-yas\add* x yinni dd-yarewřen zi Mu’ab, x min iqqimen di temmurt.”
\b
\b
\c 16
\m 
\v 1 “‘Sekkem \add ddmani ccuren s\add* izmaren n řḥakem n temmurt, zi Salaɛ ɣar řexřa, ɣar wedrar n yeǧis n Ṣihyun!’
\v 2 Am ijḍaḍ yarewřen, ittwasseḍwen zi řɛucc, ammu i ɣa ggent yessis n Mu’ab ɣar imucan n uẓekkwu n \add yeɣzar\add* n Arnun.
\v 3 ‘Awyem \add xenni\add* ccwar, ksim awař, ggem tiři nnem am ǧiřet deg uziř, snuffar imetlaɛ, war znuzi inni yarewřen!’
\v 4 ‘Jjem inni zzayi x yuẓẓřen ad ɣarem qqimen, \add a\add* \add tammurt n\add* Mu’ab! Iři d adurri i nitni zzat i wudem n umteḥḥay!’”
\b
\m “Řeḥṣaret \add maca\add* ad tbedd, ateḥḥi ad iqḍa, inni iɛeffsen x temmurt ad mweddaren zi temmurt.
\v 5 Řkursi igellden ad ittwacedd s tmexsiwt icuwwaren u Netta ad xas iqqim di tidett deg Uqiḍun n Dawud, Netta d wenni iḥekkmen d wenni yarezzun řḥeqq uca issefřeḥ tasegda.” \x ◘ \xo 16:5 \xt Ica. 9:6; Dan. 7:14, 27; Mixa 4:7; Lk. 1:33\x*
\b
\m 
\v 6 “Neccin nesřa x nnfaxet n \add temmurt n\add* Mu’ab, aqa nettat d taɛeffart ař ṭṭarf. Taɛeffart nnes d nnfaxet nnes d zzɛamet nnes, aqa \add marra\add* řhard nnes ixwan war iǧi ca nican. \x ◘ \xo 16:6 \xt Irm. 48:29, 30\x*
\v 7 S uya i ɣa tru \add temmurt n\add* Mu’ab x Mu’ab, marra nitni ad run, ad sɣuyen x zzbib n Qir-Ḥarisat, nitni dewřen ttwaɣeřben qaɛ.
\v 8 Maɣar isřawent tzayarin deg imarjaɛen n uḍiř n Ḥacbun. Tiseḍwin n ḍḍiřect n Sibma arennyent řḥukkam n řegnus. Tiseḍwin yiwḍent ař Yaɛzir, suḥent di řexřa, bezzɛent, aqa ẓwant řebḥar. \x ◘ \xo 16:8 \xt Irm. 48:32, 33\x*
\v 9 X uya ttruɣ \add x\add* ḍḍiřect n Sibma, am mammec ruɣ x Yaɛzir. Ssuɣ cem s imeṭṭawen inu, \add a, tineddam n\add* Ḥacbun d Aliɛala, minzi ruḥen iɣuyyan n usřiwřew zi tini nnem n unebdu u zeg weřqaḍ nnem. \x ◘ \xo 16:9 \xt Irm. 48:32\x*
\v 10 Tḥeyyed řefraḥet d zzhu zeg iyyar\add en\add* isseɣmayen n tfeǧaḥt, war ttɣennijen u war sřiwřiwen \add ɛad\add* deg imarjaɛen n uḍiř. Wenni yareffsen war yareffes \add ɛad\add* aḍiř di tsiřt \add n uḍiř\add*. Ssbeddeɣ Necc řeɛyudat n usřiwřew.
\v 11 X uya sɣuyyunt tekricin inu am yijj n řgambri x Mu’ab, u daxeř inu x Kir-Ḥaris.
\v 12 Xmi i ɣa yaḥeř Mu’ab x řgeɛɛdet \add mani ttqeddamen tiwhibin nnes\add* uca ad yadef ɣar zzawect nnes iqeddsen ḥima ad iẓẓaǧ, \add xenni\add* ad ẓaren aqa Mu’ab war izemmar ad igg walu.” \x ◘ \xo 16:12 \xt Aɛwd. 32:37, 38, 39\x*
\m 
\v 13 Wa d awař i issiweř SIDI x Mu’ab.
\v 14 \add Uca\add* řexxu issawař SIDI, iqqar: “Di třata n iseggʷusa ɛlaḥsab iseggʷusa n ucewwař, ad idweř uɛuǧi n Mu’ab ittwasseḥqar ak-d marra abarru nni ameqqran. Min \add zzayes\add* i ɣa iqqimen, ad yiři drus qaɛ, war iǧi aṭṭas.”
\b
\b
\c 17
\m 
\v 1 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden x Dimacq.\bd*
\b
\m “Aqa da, Dimacq war tᵉttiři ɛad d tandint, ad tedweř d řxarbet ittwahedmen.
\v 2 Tineddam n Ɛaruɛir ad dewřent xřant, ad iřint i tḥimriwin. Tina ad dinni zzřent uca uřa d ijjen war tent issfeɛfiɛ.
\v 3 Ad tᵉttwaqḍa x lqelɛa zi Ifrayim uřa x tageldit zi Dimacq u x min iqqimen n Aram. Nitni ad asen imsar am mammec imsar i uɛuǧi n ayt n Israil, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.”
\m 
\v 4 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad isřaw uɛuǧi n Yaɛqub uca ad tedweř tadunt n arrimet nnes teqqiǧet.
\v 5 Ad yiři axmi ittqebbeḍ wenni imejjaren imendi ibedden uca imejjar uɣiř nnes tidrin, ad yiři axmi ijj iřeqqeḍ tidrin di teɣzurt n Irafawiyyen.
\v 6 Ad iqqim \add mɣir\add* ijj n uceṭṭi i weřqaḍ, am ɣar wezwaḍ n izemmuren, tnayen niɣ třata \add n tzitunin\add* ɣar tqiccet n taseṭṭa sennej, uca arebɛa niɣ xemsa ɣar tiseḍwin iɣemmayen aṭṭas, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.”
\m 
\v 7 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ixzar bnadem x wenni t iggin u tiṭṭawin nnes ad ẓaren Amqeddas n Israil.
\v 8 War ittwaři iɛalṭaren, řxedmet n ifassen nnes, uřa d min iggin iḍewḍan nnes war t iẓẓar, tirebbin n cwarti lla uřa d ipilaren n arebbi n tfuct lla.”
\m 
\v 9 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad iřint tneddam nnes ifaryen am wemcan ixřa deg wezɣar u taqiccet n wedrar nni jjin zzat i tiṭṭawin n ayt n Israil, ad yiři d amcan ittwareddǧen.
\v 10 Maɣar cek tᵉttud AREBBI n usenjem nnec, war teɛqiřed x Teṣḍart nnec ijehden. X uya tᵉtteẓẓud aɣemmuy iḍarfen uca tzarrɛed tiɣeddutin tibarraniyyin.
\v 11 Deg wass nni di tent teẓẓuḍ, ad tent tfaryed, u ɣar uteffu tejjid zzariɛet nnem ad tessfuffi: \add d man aya\add* d tamejra iɛurrcen deg wass n řeḥřac nnec d řeḥriq war ittgenfin.”
\m 
\v 12 “\bd Uct\bd* x ubarru n řegnus nni izehharen am zehharen řebḥur, uřa \add uct x\add* ddriz n ccuɛub nni \add iggin\add* am řeḥweř n waman imeqqranen inhewřen!
\v 13 Ad hewřen ccuɛub am řeḥweř n waman imeqqranen, \add maca\add* Netta ad ten yarebba u nitni ad arewřen ɣar řaggʷaj. Ad ittwaɛarn \add ubarru n řegnus\add* am uřum x idurar \add ittwaɛarnen\add* zeg usemmiḍ, am \add useynu n tɛejjajt\add* tenneḍ as-dd tḥaryaḍt. \x ◘ \xo 17:13 \xt Ayub 21:18; Izhd. 1:4; 35:5; 83:14; Ḥuc. 13:3\x*
\v 14 Ɣar řweqt n tmeddit, xzar, anexřiɛ! Qbeř ma ad iṣbeḥ řḥař, war iǧi netta ɛad. Ta d tasɣart n yinni d aneɣ ikeccḍen, zzhar n yinni d aneɣ yucaren.”
\b
\b
\c 18
\s1 Tammurt n Kuc ad tsellem ixef nnes i SIDI AREBBI
\m 
\v 1 “\bd Uct\bd* x temmurt n řḥess n wafriwen, tenni ɣar urendad iɣezran n \add temmurt n\add* Kuc,
\v 2 tenni issekken imsekkan \add nnes\add* x řebḥar, di tɣarrabutin n uɣanim tiwa i waman.
\m Uyurem, \add a kenniw\add* ireqqasen ifsusen, ɣar ijj n řgens izzuggarten u ittwessgen \add n teřmect\add*, ɣar ijj n řgens nni zi ggʷeden zeg wami iǧa u zi ssa tsawent, ɣar řgens nni ittamaran řebda u iɛeffes, wenni zi qeḍɛen iɣezran tammurt nnes.
\v 3 \add A kenniw\add* marra imezdaɣ n ddunect d yinni izeddɣen x temmurt xmi ɣa ssgeɛɛden taɛeǧant x idurar, \add xenni\add* ad \add t\add* tẓarem, u xmi ɣa suḍen deg uyicc n icarri, ad \add t\add* tesřem!”
\m 
\v 4 “Maɣar ammu i d ɣari inna SIDI: ‘Necc ad ḥḍiɣ di řhudnet x řɛarc inu, am řehmu yareqqen ɣar ṭṭḥa \add n uziř\add*, am useynu \add iccuren s\add* nnḍa ɣar řehmu n ṣṣabet.’
\v 5 Maɣar qbeř ṣṣabet, xmi ɣa ikemmeř nnuwwar, tedweř tnewwart d aḍiř inenna, ad izbar Netta izbiren s ijeqqaḍen n wezbar, ad ikkes arbiben, ad ten iqḍu.
\v 6 Nitni marra ad ttwajjen i ijḍaḍ ittkeccaḍen x idurar u i řewḥuc n temmurt. Deg unebdu ad xasen arsen ijḍaḍ ittkeccaḍen u di řmecta ad xasen arsen řewḥuc n řexra.
\v 7 Di řweqt nni ad awyen ict n tarzeft i SIDI n řɛeskarat: ijj n řgens izzuggarten d ittwessgen \add n teřmect\add* - u \add man aya\add* zeg ijj n řgens imeggʷed zzayes zeg wami iǧa d tsawent, zeg ijj n řgens nni ittamaren řebda u iɛeffes, nni zi qeḍɛen iɣezran tammurt nnes - ɣar wemcan n Yisem n SIDI n řɛeskarat: ɣar wedrar n Ṣihyun.”
\b
\b
\c 19
\m 
\v 1 \bd Řḥukm x Miṣra.\bd* “Xzar, SIDI innya x ict n tseynut ittazzřen. Netta yudef ɣar Miṣra uca l’aṣnam ad arjijen zzat i wudem nnes u ayt n Miṣra ad asen ifceř wuř deg idmaren nsen.
\v 2 Maɣar ad ssḥarrceɣ Imiṣriyyen x Imiṣriyyen, maḥend kuř ijj ad immneɣ ak-d umas, u kuř ijj ak-d wajjar nnes, tandint ak-d tendint, tageldit ak-d tgeldit.
\v 3 Buhbeř n Imiṣriyyen ad yarjef daysen u Necc ad fesxeɣ ixarriṣen nsen. \add Xenni\add* ad sseqsan l’aṣnam nsen d yinni ittɛezzmen uřa d yinni issawařen ak-d imettan d igezzanen.
\v 4 Ad ggeɣ Imiṣriyyen deg ufus n aytbab iqesḥen uca ajeǧid iwɛaren ad xasen iḥkem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi, SIDI n řɛeskarat.
\v 5 Aman di řebḥar ad aẓɣen u iɣzar ad idweř d ijdi, ad yaẓeɣ.
\v 6 Iɣezran ad arxun i arriḥet yursuḍen u iɣezran n Miṣra ad arsen uca ad aẓɣen, aɣanim d telga ad isřawen.
\v 7 Ddmani n tarewsa ɣar Nil, ɣar uqemmum n iɣzar \add n Nil\add*, uřa d marra tammurt ɣar iɣezran mani zarrɛen, ad aẓɣen, ad ttwakksen, war ttiřin ɛad.
\v 8 Ibeḥriyyen n iseřman ad ceḍnen u marra inni inḍaren tasennart nsen deg iɣzar \add n Nil\add*, u inni ibezzɛen tracca n udellaɛ x waman, ad isřawen \add zeg wecḍan\add*.
\v 9 Inni ixeddmen tiffest azdad meccḍen ad seḍḥan, uřa d idarrazen n řkettan d acemřař.
\v 10 Ad ttwaddzen ipilaren n temmurt, marra inni ixeddmen di ṭṭweɛ n řmunet icḍen as řeɛmar.”
\m 
\v 11 “Wah, řḥukkam n Ṣuɛan d ibuhařiyyen, ccwar n imcawaren imiɣisen n firɛun idweř ibbuhři. Mammec tzeɛɛmem ad teqqarem \add ɛad\add* i firɛun: ‘Necc d mmis n imiɣisen, mmis n ijeǧiden n wecḥař uya?’
\v 12 Mani ǧan xenni imiɣisen nnec? Ejj i-ten ad ac ssargben u ad \add cek\add* ssecnen min ixarreṣ SIDI n řɛeskarat ḍidd i Miṣra!
\v 13 Řḥukkam n Ṣuɛan dewřen d ibuhařiyyen, ttwacemten řḥukkam n Nuf. Ad ssweddaren Miṣra, \add aqa\add* inni d iẓra n teɣmart n tqebbař nnes.”
\m 
\v 14 “SIDI ikebb di Miṣra buḥbeř issdewwaxen di řwesṭ nnes. Nitni ssweddaren Miṣra di marra min igga, am umeskar iweddar di tɛuqqit nnes.
\v 15 War ittiři \add ɛad\add* i Miṣřa min ɣa yegg, min izemmar ad \add t\add* igg uzeǧif niɣ akennas, taseṭṭa niɣ aɣanim.” \x ◘ \xo 19:15 \xt Ica. 9:13\x*
\m 
\v 16 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad iřin Imiṣriyyem am temɣarin. Ad arjijen, ad nnxeřɛen zi ssibbet n wenhezzi \add issaggʷaden\add* n ufus n SIDI n řɛeskarat, i zi ɣarsen i ɣa inhezz ssa d ssa.
\v 17 Tammurt n Yahuda ad tedweř d amedya n unexřiɛ i Imiṣriyyen. Marra wenni t ittidaren, ad innexřeɛ zi ssibbet n uxarreṣ n SIDI n řɛeskarat nni xasen ixarreṣ.”
\m 
\v 18 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad din iřint xemsa n tneddam di temmurt n Miṣra, ad \add din\add* ssiwřen \add iwdan\add* iřes n Kenɛan uca ad jjaǧen ɣar SIDI n řɛeskarat. Ict n zzaysent ad as qqaren ‘Ir-ha-Heres!’, \add ‘Tandint n wareddeǧ’\add*.\x ◘ \xo 19:18 \xt Aɛwd. 10:20; Irm. 12:16\x*
\v 19 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad \add din\add* yiři ijj n uɛalṭar di řwesṭ n temmurt n Miṣra u ijj n umayḍu \add iqeddsen\add* ɣar weymir nnes.
\v 20 Aya ad yiři d řeɛřamet d cchadet i SIDI n řɛeskarat di temmurt n Miṣra: xmi ɣa řaɣan i SIDI zi ssibbet n yinni ten iḥeṣṣaren, Netta ad ɣarsen issekk Amsenjem d ameqqran, u wanita ad ten ifekk.
\v 21 Ad idweř SIDI ittwassen ɣar Imiṣriyyen uca Imiṣriyyen ad ssnen SIDI \bd deg wass nni\bd*. Nitni ad as sexxaren s tɣarṣt d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* uca ad wcen awař i SIDI u ad t kemmřen. \x ◘ \xo 19:21 \xt Mal. 1:11\x*
\v 22 Ad iwwet SIDI Imiṣriyyen s tiyyita, Netta ad \add ten\add* iwwet u ad \add ten\add* issgenfa. Nitni ad dd-dewřen ɣar SIDI u Netta ad yejj ixef nnes ad ittwasseṣřeḥ s tẓaǧit yuǧɣen nsen u ad ten issgenfa.”
\m 
\v 23 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad \add din\add* yiři webrid ameqqran zi Miṣra ař Accur. Ayt n Accur ad dd-asen di Miṣra uca Imiṣriyyen di Accur. Ad \add as\add* ɛebden Imiṣriyyen \add i Netta\add* \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ayt n Accur.”
\m 
\v 24 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad yiři Israil d wiss třata ak-d Miṣra d Accur, d lbaraka di řwesṭ n temmurt.
\v 25 Maɣar SIDI n řɛeskarat ad ten ibarek, ad yini: ‘Iři ad ittwabarek řgens inu Miṣra, u řxedmet n ifassen inu Accur, uřa d tasɣart inu Israil!’”
\b
\b
\c 20
\s1 Řḥukm x Miṣra d Kuc
\m 
\v 1 Deg useggʷas nni di dd-yusa ukumandar n řɛeskar ɣar Acdud, umi t issekk Sarjun, ajeǧid n Accur, u immneɣ netta ak-d Acdud uca iṭṭef i-t,
\v 2 di řweqt nni tuɣa issawař SIDI, s uqemmum n Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ, inna: “Uyur, sars arruḍ n txancet \add n wecḍan\add* nni x tejɛinna nnec u kkes sandaliyat nnec x iḍaren nnec!” Igga i-t \add Icaɛya\add*, iggur d aɛaryan u s řeḥfa x iḍaren nnes. \f ◼ \fr 20:2 \fk aqemmum\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘afus’.\f*
\v 3 \add Řexdenni\add* inna SIDI: “Am mammec iggur umsexxar inu Icaɛya \add řexxu ɛad\add* třata n iseggʷusa d aɛaryan u s řeḥfa da d diha, am řeɛřamet u am yijj n řeɛjeb i Miṣra u i Kuc,
\v 4 ammu i ɣa indeh ujeǧid n Accur imeḥbas n Miṣra d imenfiyyen n Kuc, ameẓyan d umeqqran, aɛaryan d uḥefyan n iḍaren, uřa s ddabub iɛarran, \add aqa\add* d řefḍiḥet i Miṣra.
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* ad ggʷeden u ad seḍḥan zi ssibbet n ayt n Kuc i ɣar tuɣa xezzaren d ca, u zi ssibbet n Imiṣriyyen, afeyyec nsen. \f ◼ \fr 20:5 \fk ayt n Kuc\ft - ixs ad yini řgens n Ssudan d Itiyupiyya.\f*
\v 6 Imezdaɣ n temmurt-a x tma n řebḥar ad inin \bd deg wass nni\bd*: ‘Xzar, ammu i imsar i wenni ɣar nxezzar d ca, d wenni ɣar narweř ḥima ad narzu twiza, ḥima ad nettwafekk zi zzat n wudem n ujeǧid n Accur. Mammec \add xenni\add* nzemmar ad nenjem \add řexxu\add*?’”
\b
\b
\c 21
\m 
\v 1 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden x řexřa n řebḥar.\bd*
\b
\m “Am mammec ttazzřent tḥaryaḍin di \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub, \add ammu i\add* ɣa iffeɣ netta zi řexřa, zi temmurt issaggʷaden. \f ◼ \fr 21:1 \fk řebḥar\ft - niɣ ‘il’.\f*
\v 2 Tusa-dd ɣari ijj n řewḥiy iqseḥ: ‘Aɣeddar ittegg s řeɣdaret u amteḥḥay ad iteḥḥa. Geɛɛed-dd, \add a\add* Ɛilam, ḥṣar, \add a\add* Maday!’ Necc ad ssbeddeɣ marra azehhar nnes.
\v 3 X uya tteksent dayi tejɛinnatin inu, u ṭṭfen ayi řewjeɛ n tarut am řewjeɛ n ict n temɣart ittarwen. Necc ttnezbareɣ xmi \add d as\add* ttesřiɣ, nnxeřɛeɣ umi t ttwařiɣ.
\v 4 Uř inu innejref, aqarqeb \add nnes\add* issenhezza dayi tiggʷudi. Tbambast n tmeddit nni wehhceɣ aṭṭas, igga ayi tt d řɛurret.” \x ◘ \xo 21:4 \xt Ayub 7:3\x*
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Srusa-dd ṭṭabřa, sbedd aɛessas, ecc, su!”
\b
\m “Kkarem, \add a\add* řḥukkam, dehnem taseddart \add n useřqi\add*!”
\v 6 Maɣar ammu i d ayi inna Sidi: “Uyur, egg ijj n uɛessas, ejj i-t ad ixebbar min ittwařa!”
\v 7 Aqa iẓra iryazen nni inyin x yeysan, tyuya n imnayen ak-d tyuya nneɣni, ijj n ukaravan n yeɣyař d ijj n ukaravan n iřeɣman. Tuɣa iḥeṭṭa mliḥ, mliḥ aṭṭas.
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa wenni tt iẓrin: “\add A\add* Sidi inu, deg wass ttbeddiɣ břa qeṭṭu x wecbar n tɛessast u kuř ǧiřet ttɛesseɣ. \x ◘ \xo 21:8 \xt Ḥab. 2:1\x*
\v 9 Xzar, diha usin-dd iryazen nni inyin x yeysan, tyuya n imnayen ak-d tyuya nneɣni!” \add Ɛawed\add* iṭṭef netta deg wawař, inna: “Tewḍa \add tendint n\add* Babil, tewḍa, d marra řexyařat ineqcen n irebbiten nnes iřbez i-ten x temmurt!” \x ◘ \xo 21:9 \xt Irm. 25:12; 51:8; Asa. 14:8; 18:2 \x*
\v 10 \add A\add* asarwat inu, \add a\add* mmis n unedrar inu! Min sřiɣ zi SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil, xebbareɣ kenniw xas.
\b
\m 
\v 11 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden x Duma.\bd*
\m “Zi Saɛir řaɣan ayi-dd: ‘Aɛessas, mecḥař \add ɛad\add* ɣa tekk ǧiřet? Aɛessas, mecḥař \add ɛad\add* ɣa tekk ǧiřet?’
\v 12 Inna uɛessas: ‘Yusa-dd uteffu n řḥař, uřa d ǧiřet \add tusa-dd\add*. Mařa kenniw texsem ad tesseqsam, seqsam! Dewřem-dd, asem-dd!’”
\b
\m 
\v 13 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden di tmeddit.\bd*
\m “Deg wezɣar di \add temmurt n\add* Weɛraben ad tessensem, \add a kenniw\add*, ikaravanen n ayt n Dadan! \f ◼ \fr 21:13 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\v 14 Uyurem ɣar wumsagar ak-d wenni iffuden ḥima ad as tawyem aman! Imezdaɣ n temmurt n Tayma ffɣen-dd ɣar umsagar ak-d umarwař s weɣrum.
\v 15 Maɣar nitni arewřen zi řesyuf, zi ssif i dd-ittwajebden, zi řqews ittwameḥden u zi řeɣben n umenɣi.
\v 16 Maɣar ammu i d ayi inna Sidi inu: ‘Ɛad deg ijj n useggʷas, ɛlaḥsab iseggʷusa n ucewwař, \add xenni\add* ad iqḍa marra x uɛuǧi n Qidar!
\v 17 Řqedd n ayt n bu-řqews iqqimen, ayt n bu-teɣřudṭ n Qidar, ad yiři drus waha, maɣar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil d wenni innan \add aya\add*.’”
\b
\b
\c 22
\m 
\v 1 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden x Teɣzurt n Řewḥiy.\bd*
\m “Min cem yuɣin ařami tgeɛɛded cem ak-d marra \add iwdan\add* x tzeɣwin?
\v 2 \add A\add* cem, tenni iccuren s ddriz, \add a cem\add* tandint izruddḥen, tandint ineggzen s řefraḥet: inni dayem ittwanɣen, war ttwanɣen s ssif u war mmten deg umenɣi.
\v 3 Marra imgewwaden nnem munen arewřen, \add maca\add* ttwaḥebbsen nhřa uřa d ict n tecti n řqews, marra inni dayem ufin, ttwacarfen, waxxa arewřen ɣar řaggʷaj.”
\m 
\v 4 “X uya qqareɣ: ‘Saggʷejem xafi řxezrat, ejj ayi ad ruɣ s imeṭṭawen imerzagen. War d ayi ḥeṣṣarem ḥima ad ayi tɛezzam x wareddeǧ n yeǧis n řgens inu!’ \x ◘ \xo 22:4 \xt Irm. 8:23\x*
\v 5 Maɣar d ijj n wass n wezruddeḥ d uɛfas d uxarweḍ i dd-issekk Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat, di Teɣzurt n Řewḥiy, \add ijj n wass\add* n weɣdař n řḥiḍ u n iɣuyyan i x dd-ttarran idurar.
\v 6 Maɣar Ɛilam iṭṭef aqrab nnes s fřitcat, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ukarru n umenɣi u ak-d aryaz \add nni t ineddhen\add* d yinni inyin x yeysan, u Qir iɛarra taseddart \add n uɛeskari\add*. \f ◼ \fr 22:6 \fk inni inyin x iysan\ft - niɣ ‘imnayen’.\f*
\v 7 Ad imsar aqa řemxeyyer n teysarin nnec ad ttwaccuren s ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add* u imnayen ad sedden ixef nsen \add i umenɣi\add* \add arendad n\add* tewwart \add n tendint\add*. \f ◼ \fr 22:7 \fk imnayen\ft - niɣ ‘inni inyin x yeysan’.\f*
\v 8 Ad ikkes Netta arruḍ x Yahuda. \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad texzared ɣar řesnaḥ \add i iǧan\add* di Taddart n Wezɣar. \f ◼ \fr 22:8 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\v 9 Ad tẓarem tizzeyyin di tendint n Dawud, minzi aqa atent deg waṭṭas. Ad tessmunem aman n uyeřmam n wadday.
\v 10 Ad tḥesbem tudrin n Urcalim uca ad thedmem tudrin ḥima ad tessjehdem řḥiḍ.
\v 11 Ad teggem ijj n uyeřmam jar řeḥyuḍ, ḥima ad tessmunem aman n uyeřman aqdim, \add maca\add* war txezzarem ɣar wenni t iggin, u war tḥeṭṭim wenni t iṣennɛen zeg wecḥař uya.”
\m 
\v 12 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad iřaɣa Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat, maḥend ad trum, ad tesɣuyem, ad tḥeffem azeǧif u maḥend ad tyarḍem taxancet \add n wecḍan\add*.
\v 13 \add Maca\add* xzar, \add řexxu aqa din\add* arcaq d řefraḥet, neqqen ifunasen, ɣarṣen i wuǧi, ttᵉtten aysum u sessen binu, \add am qqaren:\add* ‘Ejj aneɣ ad necc, ad nsu, maɣar tiwecca ad nemmet!’ \x ◘ \xo 22:13 \xt Ica. 56:12; 1 Kur. 15:32\x*
\v 14 \add Maca\add* SIDI n řɛeskarat issargeb ayi \add x uya\add* deg imezzuɣen inu, \add inna:\add* ‘Řmuɛṣiyyet-a war ittwasseṣřeḥ i kenniw ař ɣa temmtem!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat.”
\b
\s1 Awař n Arebbi x Cibna d Ilyaqim
\m 
\v 15 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Uyur, adef ɣar wewkiř nni, ɣar Cibna, řemqeddem n tzeddiɣt \add n ujeǧid\add*, \add uca ini\add*:
\v 16 Min ɣarek \add iǧan\add* danita, niɣ man wen ɣarek \add iǧan\add* danita, aqa cek tneqced da ijj n wenḍeř i yixef nnec? \add Iwa\add* ineqqec anḍeř nnes sennej, ineqqec i yixef nnes ict n tzeddiɣt di jjarf!
\v 17 Xzar, SIDI ad zzayek iḥejjar s ijj n uḥejjar imɣar, Netta ad cek iṭṭef s ijj n wuḍuf iqseḥ.
\v 18 Netta ad cek isseḥnunneḍ qaɛ ařami \add tdewřed\add* d taqurart, ict n tcamma nni tt i ɣa nḍaren ɣar ict n temmurt temɣar. Dinni i ɣa temmted u dinni i ɣa iřin xenni ikarruten nnec icuwwaren, \add a cek\add* řefḍiḥet n taddart n bab nnec!
\v 19 Necc ad cek dd-ssuffɣeɣ zi řfusina nnec, \add wah,\add* Netta ad cek dd-iqřeɛ zeg wemcan nnec.’”
\b
\m 
\v 20 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad řaɣiɣ i umsexxar inu Alyaqim, mmis n Ḥilqiya. \x ◘ \xo 22:20 \xt 2 Ij. 18:18, 26,37\x*
\v 21 Necc ad as ssyarḍeɣ arruḍ nnec u Necc ad as beyseɣ abyas nnec u ad wceɣ tizemmar nnec deg ufus nnes. Netta ad yiři d babatsen i imezdaɣ n Urcalim d taddart n Yahuda.
\v 22 Necc ad as ssarseɣ řmeftaḥ n taddart n Dawud x teɣruḍt nnes. \add Mařa\add* netta ad yarzem, war izemmar uřa d ijj ad ibelleɛ, \add mařa\add* netta ibelleɛ, war izemmar uřa d ijj ad yarzem. \x ◘ \xo 22:22 \xt Asa. 3:7 \x*
\v 23 Necc ad t wteɣ am řewted deg ijj n wemcan imten u netta ad yiři d řɛarc n uɛuǧi i taddart n babas.
\v 24 Ad xas ayřen marra aɛuǧi n taddart n babas, iɣedduyen imeẓyanin d tɣeddutin, zi marra tiqcuɛin timeẓyanin, zi ṭṭbaṣi ař marra tiqnucin.
\v 25 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ittwakkes řewted i ittwawten deg wemcan imetnen, iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat. Ad ittwaqḍeɛ u \add xenni\add* ad iwḍa uca ddqeř i tuɣa ɣares yuyřen, ad ittwaqess, maɣar \add ammu i\add* inna SIDI.”
\b
\b
\c 23
\m 
\v 1 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden x Ṣur.\bd*
\m “‘Rum, \add a\add* iɣarruba n Tarcic, maɣar tehdem \add tendint n Ṣur\add* umi war teqqim taddart uřa d řmuyyi.’ Wah, \add ammu i\add* d asen ittwassargeb zi temmurt n ayt n Kittim. \x ◘ \xo 23:1 \xt Irm. 47:4; Ḥiz. 26; 27; 28; Zak. 9:3, 4\x*
\v 2 ‘Susmem, \add a kenniw\add* imezdaɣ n tegzirt! Isebbaben n Ṣidun inni iẓekkwan řebḥar \add s iɣarruba nsen\add*, aqa ccuren cem \add s sseřɛet\add*!’
\v 3 Zzariɛet n Sixur, ṣṣabet n iɣzar \add n Nil\add*, tedweř d řmunet nnes. \add Ammu i\add* tedweř \add tendint n Ṣur\add* d řmarsi n řegnus.”
\m 
\v 4 “‘Seḍḥa, \add a cem\add* Ṣidun!’ Maɣar řebḥar iqqar, lburj n řebḥar iqqar: ‘War dayi tuɣi řewjeɛ n tarut u necc war uriweɣ. Necc war ssɣimiɣ iḥudriyyen u war arebbiɣ tiɛzuray.’
\v 5 Xmi ɣa yaweḍ řexbar ɣar Miṣra, \add xenni\add* ad nezbaren nitni s řeḥriq xmi ɣa sřen i řexbar x Ṣur.”
\m 
\v 6 “‘Ẓwam ɣar Tarcic, sɣuyyem, \add kenniw\add* imezdaɣ n tegzirt!’
\v 7 Ma wa \add d actab\add* nwem, \add a\add* \add tandint\add* ineggzen s řefraḥet, tenni zi ř’aṣeř nnes \add iǧan\add* zeg wussan n wecḥař uya? Iṣuraf nnes ad tt arbun ɣar řaggʷaj ḥima ad \add din\add* teqqim am tbarranect.
\v 8 Wi ixarrṣen man aya di řbař nnes ḍidd i Ṣur, \add tandint\add* nni ibeṭṭan ttijan, aqa zeɛma isebbaben \add nnes\add* d řḥukkam, ittijariyyen \add nnes\add* d imcennɛen n temmurt?
\v 9 SIDI n řɛeskarat aqa ɣares di řbař nnes ḥima ad issɛiǧet nnfaxet n marra \add min iǧan d\add* talwizt, ḥima ad yarẓ řɛezz n marra imcennɛen n temmurt.”
\m 
\v 10 “‘Sesfiy tammurt nnem am yeɣzar \add n Nil\add*, \add a cem\add* yeǧis n Tarcic! War cem tmenneɛ uřa d ict n řḥajjet ɛad!’
\v 11 Netta isswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes x řebḥar, netta issenhezz tigeldiwin. SIDI yumur ḍidd i Kenɛan maḥend ad areddǧen lburjat nnes.
\v 12 Netta inna: ‘Ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad tiřid tfarḥed, tᵉttwassɛiǧted, \add a\add* taɛzarect, yeǧis n Ṣidun! \add Ruḥ\add* ɣar ayt n Kittim, kkar, ẓwa. Uřa dinni war tᵉṭṭifed řehna.’ \f ◼ \fr 23:12 \fk Kittim\ft - ixs ad yini ‘Qubrus’.\f*
\v 13 Xzar, tammurt n Ikaldaniyyen, řgens-a i tuɣa war iǧin, aqa ineyyec Accur \add d tammurt\add* i řewḥuc n řexřa - \add maɣar\add* nitni ssgeɛɛden lburjat nsen i wehjam, ssɛarran řeqṣur nnes - aqa řgens-a yarra i-tt d řxirbet. \f ◼ \fr 23:13 \ft \bd afessar\bd* - ayet-a tessiweř x Ikaldaniyyen, x mammec ɣeřben d amezwar x imperaturiya n Accur (ixs ad yini tandint n Ninwa) u xenni udfen ɣar temmurt n Ifinikiyyen (qqaren as řexxu Lubnan) uca hedmen lburj nni iǧan x tegzirt n tendint n Ṣur, di řwest n řebḥar, yudes-dd ɣar tendint n Ṣur x řbar. Tuɣa Accur war izemmar ad iṭṭef lburj-a n Ifinikiyyen, maca Ikaldaniyyen hejmen xas řmijař n 13 n iseggʷusa, xenni feřḥen maca war ɣarsen ufin bu tkeccaḍt minzi marra imezdaɣ n tegzirt ffɣen x řebḥar ɣar řegnus nni ʷik-d ggin tasebbabt nsen.\f*
\v 14 Rum, \add kenniw\add* iɣarruba n Tarcic, maɣar lburj nwem ittwahdem.”
\m 
\v 15 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad imsar, aqa Ṣur ad tᵉttwattu \add řqedd n\add* sebɛin n iseggʷusa, am \add řqedd n\add* wussan n ijj n ujeǧid. Ɣar uneggar n sebɛin n iseggʷusa \add nni\add* ad imsar i Ṣur am mammec d as qqaren deg izři n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř:
\v 16 ‘Ksi řgambri, uyur uca nneḍ di tendint, \add a cem,\add* tamɣart n farq-ccɣeř ittwattun! Irar ijj n ǧɣa mliḥ uca ɣennej aṭṭas, maḥend ad xam ɛeqřen!’
\v 17 Awarni sebɛin n iseggʷusa SIDI ad yarzef Ṣur \add ɛawed\add* uca nettat ad dd-tedweř ɣar řmunet nnes n farq-ccɣeř uca ad tessefsed ixef nnes s marra tigeldawin n ddunect nni iǧan x wudem n temmurt.
\v 18 \add Maca\add* tasebbabt nnes d řmunet nnes n farq-ccɣeř ad iřint qeddsent i SIDI. War tᵉttwaxemmeř \add deg ixxamen n txubay\add* u war tᵉttwaxezzen, maɣar sseřɛet nnes ad tiři i yinni izeddɣen zzat i wudem n SIDI, ḥima ad ccen ař i ɣa jjiwnen uca ḥima ad yarḍen arruḍ icuwwaren.”
\b
\b
\c 24
\s1 Rḥukm x ddunect
\m 
\v 1 “Xzar, SIDI ad issexwa tammurt, ad tt issxarreb, ad iqeǧeb udem nnes uca ad ibezzeɛ imezdaɣ nnes.
\v 2 Am mammec iǧa řgens, ammu \add i ɣa yiři\add* uřa d akehhan, am umsexxar uřa d sidi nnes, am tayya uřa d llalas, am umsewweq uřa d amzenzi, am areṭṭař uřa d wenni \add zzayes\add* iksin arḍař, am bab n umarwas uřa d bu-umarwas nnes. \x ◘ \xo 24:2 \xt Ḥiz. 7:12, 13\x*
\v 3 Ad ssexwan tammurt marra, ad \add tt\add* keccḍen qaɛ, maɣar SIDI inna awař-a!”
\m 
\v 4 “Tammurt tecḍen, tisřaw, ddunect teftuttes, tisřaw. Imcennɛen n řgens n temmurt teftuttusen.
\v 5 Tammurt tᵉttwassɛiǧet zeg imezdaɣ nnes, maɣar nitni ttɛeddan x izerfan, ttbeddařen tiweṣṣa, ttareẓẓan Řɛahd n řebda.
\v 6 X uya tᵉttett nneɛřet tammurt u yinni xas izeddɣen aqa daysen řɛib. S uyenni ad ttwasscemḍen imezdaɣ n temmurt, ad ceṭṭen drus n iwdan waha.” \x ◘ \xo 24:6 \xt Ica. 9:18; 10:16\x*
\m 
\v 7 “Binu n jdid icḍen, tazayart teftuttes, marra inni tuɣa ifarḥen deg wuř, zehharen.
\v 8 Ṣafi ticti issfarraḥen n ibendiren, ddriz n yinni ineggzen s řefraḥet, ṣafi \add tinext\add* issfarraḥen n řgambri. \x ◘ \xo 24:8 \xt Irm. 7:34; 16:9; 25:10; Ḥiz. 26:13; Ḥuc. 2:13\x*
\v 9 War sessen binu \add ɛad\add* di řweqt n uɣennej, ccrab ad yiři d amerzag i yinni \add t\add* isessen. \x ◘ \xo 24:9 \xt Ica. 16:1\x*
\v 10 Tandint ittwajjen d řxarbet, marra tudrin bellɛent i wadaf.
\v 11 Deg imesraq ttweɛɛḍen iwdan x binu, marra řefraḥet tweddar, asřiwřew iffeɣ zi tammurt.
\v 12 Min iqqimen n tendint d řxirbet issaggʷaden \add waha\add*, u tawwart tᵉttwařbez.
\v 13 Ammu i ɣa tiři \add tendint\add* din di řwest n temmurt, jar řegnus. Ad tiři am ɣar wezwaḍ n uzemmur, am ɣar weřqaḍ \add n uḍiř\add* xmi ɣa teɛdu ṣṣabet.” \x ◘ \xo 24:13 \xt Ica. 17:6\x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 “Nitni ad ssgeɛɛden tmijja nsen, ad sřiwřewen. Umi SIDI iɛuǧen aṭṭas, ad ssɣuyen nitni s řefraḥet zi mani tɣeǧi tfuct.
\v 15 X uya, sɛuǧem xenni SIDI di temmura n tfawt, \add sɛuǧem\add* Isem n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, di tegzirin n řebḥar! \f ◼ \fr 24:15 \fk timmura n tfawt\ft - ixs ad yini timmura ɣar ccarq n Israil manis dd-tettneqqar tfuct. \fk timmura x tma n řebḥar\ft - ixs ad yini timmura ɣar řɣarb n temmurt n Israil, tinni iǧan x tma n Řebḥar Acemřař (niɣ Řebḥar Ameqqran).\f*
\v 16 Zi tmuwwa qaɛ n temmurt nᵉttesřa i izřan, i uɛuǧi n Umsegged!”
\b
\m \add Xenni\add* nniɣ: Necc fenniɣ, fenniɣ, uct xafi! Imkeccaḍen ttkeccaḍen, u imkeccaḍen ttkeccaḍen min ma \add xsen\add* ad keccḍen.
\v 17 Tiggʷudi d tesraft d řfex \add ad\add* xak \add iřin\add*, \add a\add* amezduɣ n temmurt! \x ◘ \xo 24:17 \xt Irm. 48:43\x*
\v 18 Wenni i ɣa yarewřen zi ddriz issaggʷaden, ad iwḍa di tesraft, d wenni i ɣa igeɛɛden zi tesraft, ad innaɣ di řfex, maɣar tiburjatin di řuɛřa ad nnurzment, dsusa n temmurt ad nhezzen. \x ◘ \xo 24:18 \xt Irm. 48:44; Ɛam. 5:19\x*
\v 19 Tammurt ad tcarreg qaɛ, ad tfeǧeq temmurt d ifeǧaqen, ad tenhezz temmurt aṭṭas.
\v 20 Ad tmeyyeř temmurt ssa ɣar da am yijjen iscar, ad temraywa am yijj n uɛcuc i tmensiwt. Iɛeddiyen nnes ad xas ziyyaren aṭṭas, uca nettat ad tewḍa, war tzemmar ad tekkar ɛad.” \x ◘ \xo 24:20 \xt Ayub 27:18; Ica. 1:8; 19:14\x*
\m 
\v 21 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ixřef SIDI x řɛeskar n řuɛřa di řuɛřa, uřa x ijeǧiden nni \add iǧan\add* x wudem n temmurt \add ad zzaysen ixřef\add* x wudem n temmurt.
\v 22 Ad ttwassmunen am yimeḥbas deg ict n tesraft u ad ttwaḥebdsen di řeḥbes u awarni i waṭṭas n wussan ad ɣarsen arzfen.
\v 23 Taziri ad tezweɣ s useḍḥi u tafuct tseḍḥa xmi ɣa yiři SIDI n řɛeskarat d Ajeǧid x wedrar n Ṣihyun u di Urcalim, uca zzat i imɣaren nnes \add ad dinni yiři\add* uɛuǧi.” \x ◘ \xo 24:23 \xt Ica. 13:10; Ḥiz. 32:7; Yuw. 3:4; 3:20\x*
\b
\b
\c 25
\s1 Izři n uqadi x usenjem
\m 
\v 1 \qt “\tl A\tl* SIDI, Cek d AREBBI inu,\qt*
\m \qt necc ad Cek ssɛuǧeɣ,\qt*
\m \qt ad ṣebbḥeɣ Isem nnec,\qt*
\m \qt maɣar Cek teggid řeɛjeb,\qt*
\m \qt aṭṭas n ccwar nnec\qt*
\m \qt zeg wecḥař uya,\qt*
\m \qt aqa-t d tidett u dayes řaman.\qt*
\m 
\v 2 \qt Cek tarrid tandint d aɛurric n yeẓra,\qt*
\m \qt tandint ittwassjehden d řxirbet,\qt*
\m \qt řeqṣar n ibarraniyyen di tandint,\qt*
\m \qt war t ssbeddin ɛemmarṣ ɛawed.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 25:2 \xt Ica. 21:9; 23:13; Asa. 14:8; 18:2\x*
\m 
\v 3 \qt X uya ad Cek issɛuǧa ijj n řgens ijhed,\qt*
\m \qt tandint n řegnus iqesḥen aṭṭas\qt*
\m \qt ad zzayek teggʷed.\qt*
\m 
\v 4 \qt Maɣar tuɣa Cek d lqelɛa i umarxu,\qt*
\m \qt d lqelɛa i umezřuḍ\qt*
\m \qt xmi ittneḥṣar,\qt*
\m \qt \tl Cek\tl* d adurri i wenẓar iccaten,\qt*
\m \qt uřa d tiři di řeḥmu\qt*
\m \qt minzi lḥaraj n ayt n bu-řexcunect\qt*
\m \qt aqa-t am wenẓar iccaten x řḥiḍ.\qt*
\m 
\v 5 \qt Am řeḥmu deg ijj n wemcan yuẓeɣ,\qt*
\m \qt \tl ammu\tl* i ɣa tesseɣded lḥaraj n ibarraniyyen,\qt*
\m \qt am tiři n useynu tessesmiḍ řehmu,\qt*
\m \qt \tl ammu\tl* i ɣa ittwasseɣd\qt*
\m \qt izři n ayt n bu-řexcunect.”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 6 \qt “SIDI n řɛeskarat ad issewjed x wedrar-a\qt*
\m \qt ict n zzardet s macca\qt*
\m \qt teccur s tadunt x wedrar-a\qt*
\m \qt i marra regnus,\qt*
\m \qt ict n zzardet s binu iṣebḥen qaɛ,\qt*
\m \qt s ict n macca teccur s tadunt d waduf,\qt*
\m \qt s binu iṣebḥen iṣfan.\qt*
\m 
\v 7 \qt Netta ad ibeṭṭeř x wedrar-a ařeḥḥaf\qt*
\m \qt i zi ttřeḥḥafen marra řegnus\qt*
\m \qt uřa d dduri i zi ttwassdurruyen marra řegnus.\qt*
\m 
\v 8 \qt Netta ad isarḍ řmewt i řebda\qt*
\m \qt uca Sidi inu, SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt ad imseḥ imeṭṭawen zi marra iɣembab,\qt*
\m \qt ad ikkes řefḍiḥet n řgens nnes\qt*
\m \qt zi marra tammurt,\qt*
\m \qt maɣar \tl ammu i\tl* inna SIDI.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 25:8 \xt 1 Kur. 15:54\x*
\b
\m 
\v 9 \bdit “Deg wass nni\bdit* \qt ad inin:\qt*
\m \qt ‘Aqa da, Wa d AREBBI nneɣ,\qt*
\m \qt xas i negga asitem nneɣ\qt*
\m \qt u Netta ad aneɣ issenjem.\qt*
\m \qt Wa d SIDI nni x negga asitem nneɣ,\qt*
\m \qt ad nesřiwřew, ad nfarḥ\qt*
\m \qt x usenjem nnes!’\qt*
\m 
\v 10 \qt Maɣar afus n SIDI ad yars x wedrar-a,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* Mu’ab ad ittwaddez di \tl temmurt\tl* nnes,\qt*
\m \qt am mammec ittwaddez uřum,\qt*
\m \qt ad idweř d tazubact.\qt*
\m 
\v 11 \qt \tl Mu’ab\tl* ad dayes ibezzeɛ s ifassen nnes,\qt*
\m \qt am ufettaḥ deg weftaḥ.\qt*
\m \qt \tl AREBBI\tl* ad issaḍar nnfaxet nnes\qt*
\m \qt \tl jmiɛ\tl* ak-d marra\qt*
\m \qt min izemmar ad igg\qt*
\m \qt s teḥraymect n ifassen nnes.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 25:11 \xt Ica. 16:6\x*
\m 
\v 12 \qt Netta ad ihdem lburj n iɣebřawen nnec yuɛřan,\qt*
\m \qt ad \tl ten\tl* issehwa, ad \tl ten\tl* immenḍar\qt*
\m \qt ɣar temmurt, deg ucař.”\qt*
\b
\b
\c 26
\s1 Izři n temmurt n Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ɣennjen izři-ya
\m di temmurt n Yahuda:
\b
\m \qt “Neccin ɣarneɣ ict n tendint ijehden,\qt*
\m \qt Netta issbedd ‘Asenjem’\qt*
\m \qt d řeḥyuḍ d řeqwarat.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 26:1 \xt Izhd. 46:6; 125:1; Awřn. 18:10\x*
\m 
\v 2 \qt Arzmem tiwwura,\qt*
\m \qt maḥend řgens amsegged ad dd-yadef,\qt*
\m \qt \tl řgens\tl* nni iḥeṭṭan\qt*
\m \qt řaman \tl i SIDI\tl* řebda.\qt*
\m 
\v 3 \qt S řbař imten \tl am t iǧa\tl*,\qt*
\m \qt Cek tḥeṭṭid \tl t di\tl* řehna,\qt*
\m \qt \tl wah di\tl* řehna,\qt*
\m \qt maɣar \tl řgens\tl* ittcařa xak.”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 4 \qt “Tecřem x SIDI i řebda,\qt*
\m \qt maɣar di SIDi, SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt i teǧa d Taṣḍart n zzmanat.\qt*
\m 
\v 5 \qt Maɣar Netta ittarra ad aḍaren\qt*
\m \qt inni izeddɣen dinni di řuɛřa,\qt*
\m \qt tandint yuɛřan ad tt issehwa,\qt*
\m \qt ad tt issehwa ař tammurt,\qt*
\m \qt ad tt iɛarn deg ucař.\qt*
\m 
\v 6 \qt Ad xas iɛfes uḍar,\qt*
\m \qt iḍaren n wenni ittwaḥṣaren,\qt*
\m \qt řatarat n iḍaren n imezřaḍ.”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 7 \qt “Abrid n umsegged iwaṭa,\qt*
\m \qt nican i iǧa řatar n umsegged,\qt*
\m \qt Cek tᵉttseggamed t.\qt*
\m 
\v 8 \qt Uřa deg webrid n řeḥkamat nnec,\qt*
\m \qt \tl a\tl* \tl SIDI\tl*, tuɣa nessitim ac,\qt*
\m \qt řeɛmar \tl nneɣ\tl* immeẓri\qt*
\m \qt deg Yisem nnec u di řidaret nnec.\qt*
\m 
\v 9 \qt Tuɣa řeɛmar inu ittweḥḥac i Cek di ǧiřet,\qt*
\m \qt uřa d buḥbeř inu dayi,\qt*
\m \qt tuɣa yarezzu xak s jjehd.\qt*
\m \qt Maɣar mařa řeḥkamat nnec\qt*
\m \qt usint-i-dd x temmurt,\qt*
\m \qt ad řemden imezdaɣ n temmurt tasegda.”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 10 \qt “Mařa isscen bnadem aḥinni i uɛeffan,\qt*
\m \qt wanita war iřemmed tasegda,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* ad yegg řɣar\qt*
\m \qt di temmurt iccuren s tsegda,\qt*
\m \qt u war iẓarr aɛuǧi n SIDI.”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 11 \qt “\tl A\tl* SIDI, afus nnec ittwassgeɛɛad,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* nitni war t ttwiřin.\qt*
\m \qt \tl Waxxa amenni\tl* ad t ẓaren \tl ɛad,\tl*\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* ad seḍḥan zeg wasam \tl nnec\tl*\qt*
\m \qt i řgens \tl nnec\tl*,\qt*
\m \qt wah, timessi ad tecc iɣrimen nnec.\qt*
\m 
\v 12 \qt \tl A\tl* SIDI, řḥukm nnec xaneɣ\qt*
\m \qt ad yiři d řehna,\qt*
\m \qt maɣar Cek tkemmřed\qt*
\m \qt marra timegga nneɣ di ṭṭweɛ nneɣ.\qt*
\m 
\v 13 \qt \tl A\tl* SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ,\qt*
\m \qt isiditen nneɣni seǧḍen xaneɣ.\qt*
\m \qt Zzayek Cek weḥḥdek\qt*
\m \qt aqa nettidar Isem nnec.\qt*
\m 
\v 14 \qt Imettan war tteddaren \tl ɛawed\tl*,\qt*
\m \qt řexyařat war ttnekkaran.\qt*
\m \qt S uya txeřfed asen \tl s řɣar\tl*\qt*
\m \qt uca teqḍid ten.\qt*
\m \qt Cek tekksed marra řɛeqran xasen.\qt*
\m 
\v 15 \qt \tl A\tl* SIDI, Cek tarnid di řgens-a,\qt*
\m \qt Cek tarnid di řgens-a,\qt*
\m \qt tᵉttwassɛuǧed dayes,\qt*
\m \qt \tl aqa\tl* tesswesɛed marra iymiren n temmurt.”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 16 \qt “\tl A\tl* SIDI, di řeḥṣaret arzun xak,\qt*
\m \qt zeǧɛen tiẓaǧitin nsen s tḥessect,\qt*
\m \qt umi xasen \tl dd-tusa\tl* tarbiyyet nnec.\qt*
\m 
\v 17 \qt Am mammec tᵉttnezbar\qt*
\m \qt ict n temɣart s ddeyset,\qt*
\m \qt tenni igguren ad taru \tl aḥenjir nnes\tl*\qt*
\m \qt u tesɣuyyu s řewjeɛ n tarut nnes,\qt*
\m \qt ammu i d aneɣ tuɣa neccin, \tl a\tl* SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt zzat i tiṭṭawin nnec.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 26:17 \xt Yḥ. 16:21\x*
\m 
\v 18 \qt Tuɣa neccin \tl axmi\tl* neksi s ddeyset,\qt*
\m \qt imneɛ aneɣ řeḥriq n tarwa,\qt*
\m \qt tuɣa neccin axmi nuru asemmiḍ.\qt*
\m \qt War dd-niwi asenjem i temmurt,\qt*
\m \qt u imezdaɣ n ddunect war dd-ttwaxeřqen.”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 19 \qt “Imettan nnec ad ddaren!\qt*
\m \qt Řxecbat inu ad beddent!\qt*
\m \qt Faqem, uca sřiweřwem kenniw,\qt*
\m \qt inni izeddɣen deg ucař!\qt*
\m \qt Aqa nnda n tfawin am nnda nnec,\qt*
\m \qt uca tammurt ad taru řexyařat \tl n imettan\tl*.”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 20 \qt “Uyur, \tl a\tl* řgens inu,\qt*
\m \qt adef ɣar ixxamen nnec n daxeř,\qt*
\m \qt belleɛ tiwwura awarni ac.\qt*
\m \qt Snuffar ixef nnec\qt*
\m \qt \tl řqedd n\tl* ict n tzeḥziḥt\qt*
\m \qt ař dd iɛdu wesxeḍ.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 26:20 \xt 2 Kur. 4:17\x*
\m 
\v 21 \qt Maɣar xzar, SIDI ad iffeɣ zeg wemcan nnes\qt*
\m \qt maḥend ad ixřef i imezdaɣ n temmurt\qt*
\m \qt řmuɛṣiyyet nsen,\qt*
\m \qt uca tammurt ad tɛarra idammen\qt*
\m \qt i xas ittwassizřen,\qt*
\m \qt war txemmiř ɛad inni xas ittwanɣen.”\qt*
\b
\b
\c 27
\s1 Asenjem n Israil zeg ufus n řeḥkamat n ddunect
\m 
\v 1 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ixřef SIDI zi ‘Liviyatan’, afiɣar itteḥruǧuḍen s tazřa, s ssif nnes iqseḥ, imɣar d ijhed, \add wah ad ixřef\add* zi ‘Liviyatan’, afiɣar itteḥruruden, uca ad ineɣ řhaycet nni iǧan di řebḥar.” \x ◘ \xo 27:1 \xt Asa. 12:9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 2 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* \add ad din yiři\add* ...
\m \qt ijj n umarjeɛ n uḍiř s binu icnan.\qt*
\m \qt Ɣennjem xas \tl s nnubtat\tl*.\qt*
\m 
\v 3 \qt Necc, SIDI, ad tt iḥḍa,\qt*
\m \qt ad tt ssbezzgeɣ,\qt*
\m \qt ḥima war tt ijarreḥ ḥed,\qt*
\m \qt Necc ad xas ɛesseɣ s wass d ǧiřet.\qt*
\m 
\v 4 \qt Tafqeḥt war dayi teǧi \tl qaɛ\tl*,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* mařa ca n yijjen izɛem\qt*
\m \qt ad issars zzati tazeggʷart d isennanen,\qt*
\m \qt Necc ad kidsen mmenɣeɣ,\qt*
\m \qt ad ten ssarɣeɣ munen,\qt*
\m 
\v 5 \qt illa mařa iṭṭef bnadem di jjehd inu,\qt*
\m \qt \tl uca\tl* ad yegg řehna akidi,\qt*
\m \qt \tl wah\tl* ad yegg řehna akidi!”\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 6 “Deg \add wussan\add* i dd ɣa yasen ad iwwet Yaɛqub aẓwar, Israil ad innuwar, ad iyma, u nitni ad ccuren tammurt s řɣiǧet.” \x ◘ \xo 27:6 \xt Izhd. 72:16\x*
\b
\m 
\v 7 “Ma iwta i-t Netta, am mammec wenni iwtin, iwta i-t? Ma ittwaneɣ netta, am mammec ttwanɣen inni zzayes ittwanɣen? \f ◼ \fr 27:7 \fk Zzayes\ft - ixs ad yini ‘zi AREBBI’.\f*
\v 8 Cek tarebbid tt s řeqyas řami tt tenḍared, Netta issuzzar \add i-tt\add* s usemmiḍ nnes iqesḥen, deg ijj n wass n usemmiḍ zi manis i dd-tneqqar tfuct. \x ◘ \xo 27:8 \xt Irm. 30:11; 46:28\x*
\v 9 S uya ad ittwagg aṣřaḥ x řmuɛṣiyyet n Yaɛqub s man aya uca ad yiři aya d řɣiǧet tekmeř zeg uḥeyyed x ddnub nnes: aqa netta ad yarr marra iẓra n iɛalṭaren d iẓra n jjar ttwařebzen u war din ttbeddint \add ɛad\add* trebbin n cwarti d ipilaren n arebbi n tfuct.”
\m 
\v 10 “Maɣar tandint ittwassjehden \add ad tedweř\add* ḥafi, am yict n tzeddiɣt ittwajjen, ixřan am řexřa. Dinni ad ihda uɛejmi, ad din ijna, ad icc tiseḍwin nnes. \f ◼ \fr 27:10 \fk aɛejmi\ft - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*
\v 11 Xmi ɣa yaẓɣen řefruɛ nnes, ad ttwaqeḍɛen. Ad dd-asent temɣarin, ad ten ssarɣent, \add maɣar\add* war iǧi d ijj n řgens dayes řefhamet. X uya wenni t iggin, war d asen izziǧiz, u wenni t ikewwnen, war d as yareṭṭa.”
\m 
\v 12 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad izweḍ SIDI tidrin zi mani iǧa yeɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* ař Teɣzart n Miṣra. \add Maca kenniw\add* ad ttwařeqḍem, ijjen awarni i wenneɣni, \add a\add* ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 27:12 \xt Ica. 17:5\x*
\v 13 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad suḍen deg uyicc ameqqran n icarri. \add Xenni\add* ad dd-asen inni isswejden ad hellken di Accur uřa d yinni ittwaɛarrnen ɣar temmurt n Miṣra. Nitni ad sejden i SIDI deg wedrar iqeddsen di Urcalim.”
\b
\b
\c 28
\s1 Awař n Arebbi x Samarya
\m 
\v 1 “\bd Uct\bd* x ttaj uɛeffar n imescaren n Ifrayim, aqa talwizt nnes icuwwaren \add amecnaw\add* tanewwact isřawen x tqiccet n teɣzurt iṣebḥen n yinni x yeɣřeb binu.
\v 2 Xzar, Sidi inu ɣares \add ijjen\add* ijhed u iwɛar am tecti n tebruri, am tḥaryaḍt i ittawyen ṭṭaɛun d uxarreb. Am řḥemřat n waman imɣaren issfayen ad inḍar Netta \add ttaj nni\add* s ufus \add nnes\add* ɣar temmurt.
\v 3 Ttaj aɛeffar n imescaren n Ifrayim ad t ɛefsen s iḍaren.
\v 4 Tanewwact isřawen n telwizt nnes icuwwaren x tqiccet n teɣzurt isseɣmayen, ad tiři am tbacurt tiweḍ qbeř anebdu, tenni wenni ixezzaren da d diha iẓra i-tt uca isseɣři i-tt \add deɣya\add* umi tuɣa \add ɛad\add* deg ufus nnes.”
\b
\m 
\v 5 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad yiři SIDI n řɛeskarat d tajj n ucuwwaḍ d ttaj icewwaren i min iqqimen n řgens nnes,
\v 6 d arruḥ n řḥukm i wenni iqqimen \add x řkursi\add* i řḥukm, uřa d \add arruḥ n\add* taryast i ayt n bu-teɣruḍt i yinni ittarran amenɣi ɣar tewwart \add n tendint\add*.”
\b
\m 
\v 7 “Ɛad ina ttemmraywan s binu, uca ttwarenyen zi ccrab. \bd Ittemraywa ukehhan d unabi s ccrab\bd*. Ttwaṣarḍen s binu, ttwarenyen zi ccrab, ttemraywan ɣar iweḥḥan nsen, ttenhezzan da d diha umi ḥekkmen ɣar ucarreɛ. \x ◘ \xo 28:7 \xt Ica. 5:11\x*
\v 8 Maɣar marra ṭṭabřat ɛemmarent s trarit ixemjen, uřa d ijj n wemcan \add war iqqim d amezdag\add*.
\v 9 ‘I umi ixs netta ad issɣar tussna, i umi ixs ad isscen areqqas? \add I\add* yinni umi ittwakkes asen uɣi, \add i\add* yinni umi ikksen abbuc?
\v 10 Maɣar aqa da, řumur x řumur, řumur x řumur, lfariḍa x lfariḍa, lfariḍa x lfariḍa, da drust, diha drust.’”
\m 
\v 11 “S uya ad issiweř ak-d řgens-a s iyencicen iṭṭewṭiwen u s ijj n yiřes nneɣni, \x ◘ \xo 28:11 \xt 1 Kur. 14:21\x*
\v 12 Netta d wenni tuɣa i d asen inna: ‘Wa d arraḥet, wcem arraḥet i wenni yuḥřen!’, uca: ‘Wa d řmargeḥ!’, \add maca\add* nitni war xsen ca ad sřen.
\v 13 Ad asen yiři wawař n SIDI: ‘Řumur x řumur, řumur x řumur, lfariḍa x lfariḍa, lfariḍa x lfariḍa, da drust, diha drust!’, maḥend nitni, am uyuren, ad wḍan ɣar ḍeffar, ad ttwarẓen, ad dewřen di řfex u ad ttwaḥebbsen.” \x ◘ \xo 28:13 \xt 2 Kur. 2:16\x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 “S uya, sřem i wawař n SIDI, \add a kenniw\add* \bd imestehzayen, inni ɣar iǧa ṣṣulṭa x řgens-a nni \bdit iǧan\bdit* di Urcalim!\bd*
\v 15 Minzi teqqarem: ‘Neccin negga řɛahd ak-d řmewt u negga ict n ḍḍmana ak-d řaxart. Xmi ɣa iɛdu urekkuḍ ifarcen, war ɣarneɣ dd-yiwiḍ, maɣar negga axarriq axmi mani ɣar i ɣa narweř u ad nennuffar awarni i řɣecc!’
\v 16 S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad ssarseɣ ijj n weẓru di Ṣihyun, aẓru iqeǧben, aẓru n teɣmart iɣřan, dsas imten. Wenni yumnen war ittrikwiř.’ \x ◘ \xo 28:16 \xt Izhd. 118:22; Mt. 21:42; Řex. 4:11; Rum. 9:33; 10:11; Afa. 2:20; 1 Bṭ. 2:6, 7, 8\x*
\v 17 Ad ssarseɣ řḥeqq d ufiřu n řeɛbar uca tasegda d plumu. Tebrurri ad teḥḥa amcan n tarewřa iccuren s ixarriqen uca aman ad dd-ssefyen amcan \add nnes\add* n udduri.
\m 
\v 18 Řɛahd nwem ak-d řmewt ad ittwamḥa, ḍḍmana nwem ak-d řaxart war tᵉttɣimi tbedd. Xmi ɣa iɛdu urekkuḍ ifarcen, ad zzayes tᵉttwaɛefsem kenniw.
\v 19 Meřmi ma iɛdu, ad kenniw yawi \add akides\add*, maɣar ad teɛdu tufut awarni i tufut, s wass d ǧiret. Uca afehham n ureqqas ad yawi mɣir asnexřiɛ.
\v 20 Maɣar qama ad iquḍeḍ ařami war izemmar \add bnadem\add* ad ibbuzzer uca taɛřawt ad tiři teḥṣar ařami \add bnadem\add* war izemmar ad dayes yadef.
\v 21 Maɣar SIDI ad ikkar am x wedrar n Faraṣim, ad ihaj am di teɣzurt n Jibɛun, maḥend ad yegg ccɣeř nnes: ‘Ccɣeř nnes ad yiři d aɣrib!’, uca maḥend ad yegg řxedmet nnes: ‘Řxedmet nnes ad tiři taɣribt!’
\v 22 U řexxu, war ssehqara, ḥima ssnaseř nwem war tent ttzeyyaren ɛad ktar, maɣar sřiɣ zi Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat aqa ikkes deg wawař ad yareddeǧ imun marra tammurt.”
\b
\m 
\v 23 “Sḥessem u sřem i tmijja inu, ḥḍam u sřem ɣar wawařen inu!
\v 24 Ma icarrez umcarrez ass imun, ḥima ad izarɛ? Ma \add řebda\add* ittfeǧeḥ u ineqqec iyyar nnes?
\v 25 Ma war iǧi ammu, mařa netta iwaṭa udem \add n yeyyar\add*, issuyus ssanuǧ uca \add zzariɛet n\add* řcemmun ibezzeɛ i-tt, igga irden di řeṣfuf d imendi di ikwadrunen uca karṣana igga i-t ɣar tmawwin nnes? \f ◼ \fr 28:25 \fk karṣana\ft - niɣ ‘dduxn’ niɣ ‘jawars’.\f*
\v 26 Idarreb i-t AREBBI nnes mammec ittxeṣṣa ad ixdem nican, isseřmed i-t.
\v 27 Minzi war ssarwaten ssanuǧ s teřwiḥt itteḥřuǧuḍen i usarwet u war ssekkin tajarrart n ukarru tiwa n řcemmun, maca zekkwḍen ssanuǧ s weɛmud d řcemmun s uqeṭṭab.
\v 28 Ma ḥarryen imendi \add ɣar usarwet\add*? Lla, \add bnadem\add* war t issarwit i řebda, war \add xas\add* ineddeh tijarrarin n ukarru d yeysan nnes i řebda: war t iḥarri.
\v 29 Uřa d man aya iffeɣ-dd zi SIDI n řɛeskarat. Ccwar nnes d řeɛjeb, aqa Netta imɣar deg usuyar.” \x ◘ \xo 28:29 \xt Irm. 32:19\x*
\b
\b
\c 29
\s1 Urcalim tᵉttwaḥṣar zi řegnus
\m 
\v 1 “\bd Uct\bd* x Ariyil, Ariyil, tandint n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Dawud. Arnim \add ɛad\add* ijj n useggʷas ɣar useggʷas\add -a\add*, jjem řeɛyudat \add n useggʷas\add* ad ɛdunt,
\v 2 \add xenni\add* ad ḥṣareɣ Ariyil, uca ad \add din\add* yiři uweḥweḥ d wecḍan u nettat ad tiři i Necc am Ariyil.
\v 3 Ad am qewwareɣ u ad cem ḥṣareɣ s ijj n řɛeskar i uḥeṭṭu uca ad xam ssbeddeɣ lbarajat. \x ◘ \xo 29:3 \xt Irm. 6:3; Ḥiz. 17:17\x*
\v 4 Ad tᵉttwassehwid, ad tessiwřed zi temmurt uca awařen nnem ad ten tremremd zi tɛejjajt. Tmijja nnem ad teffeɣ zi temmurt am \add tmijja\add* n wenni issawařan ak-d imettan uca awařen nnem \add ad iřin\add* am ucewcew \add waha\add* zeg ucař. \x ◘ \xo 29:4 \xt Ica. 8:19\x*
\v 5 Abarru n iɣrimen nnem ad yiři am tɛejjajt tazdadt, uca abarru n ayt n bu-řexcunet am uřum iɛeddun, ittawy i-t usemmiḍ. Ad imsar deg wermac n wabřiwen, deg ict n tecti! \x ◘ \xo 29:5 \xt Ayub 21:18; Izhd. 1:4; 35:5; Ica. 17:13; 30:13\x*
\v 6 SIDI n řɛeskarat ad ɣarek innewju s wajjaj d wenhezzi n temmurt, \add s\add* řḥess ijehden n tmijja \add nnes\add*, \add s\add* usemmiḍ n tḥaryaḍt u \add s\add* uceɛɛař n tmessi ittetten.
\v 7 Am tarjit, ijj n řewḥiy di ǧiřet, ammu i ɣa yiři ubarru n marra řegnus nni i ɣa immenɣen ak-d Ariyil, \add wah,\add* marra inni i ɣa immenɣen akides u ak-d lburj nnes d inni tt i ɣa iḥṣaren \add ad iřin ammu\add*.
\v 8 Ad yiři am yijjen yurja umi dayes yeǧa řaẓ. Xzar, netta ittett, \add xenni maca\add* ad dd-ifaq, yufa aqa řeɛmar nnes war ijjiwen \add ɛad\add*. Niɣ \add ad yiři\add* amecnaw ijjen yurja am iffud, u xzar, netta isess, \add xenni maca\add* ad dd-ifaq, yufa aqa netta ifna, uca řeɛmar nnes ittmeẓri \add ɛad ad isu\add*. Ammu i ɣa tiři \add tmesřact\add* i marra řegnus nni i ɣa immenɣen ak-d wedrar n Ṣihyun.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Jɛarem u tbehtem, smesḥem tiṭṭawin nwem \add ař i ɣa\add* tiřim d idarɣařen! Nitni scaren, \add maca\add* war iǧi zi binu, ttemraywan, \add maca\add* war iǧi zi ccrab.
\v 10 Maɣar SIDI izeǧeɛ xawem buḥbeř n yiḍeṣ yuǧɣen. Ibelleɛ tiṭṭawin nwem, inabiyyen, uca izeǧifen nwem, imwařawen \add n tmeẓriwin\add*, iřeḥḥef i-ten. \x ◘ \xo 29:10 \xt Rum. 11:8\x*
\v 11 Ammu i d awem idweř řewḥiy n marra aya am wawařen n ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen nni immewcen i wenni issnen tiɣri, qqaren: ‘Ɣar i-t-i-d xafi!’, uca \add xenni\add* ad yarr: ‘Necc war zemmareɣ \add ad t ɣareɣ\add*, maɣar icemmeɛ.’
\v 12 Niɣ immewc wedlis i wenni war issnen ad iɣar, \add umi\add* qqaren: ‘Ɣar i-t-i-d xafi!’, uca \add xenni\add* ad yarr netta: ‘Necc war ssineɣ ad ɣareɣ.’”
\m 
\v 13 “Inna ayi Sidi inu: ‘Minzi řgens-a yudes ayi-dd mɣir s wawařen waha u \add minzi nitni\add* tteggen ayi ccan s iyencicen nsen, \add am\add* iggʷej xafi uř nsen, u minzi aweqqar i zi d ayi weqqaren \add itteffeɣ\add* zi tweṣṣa nni řemden zeg iwdan \add waha\add*, \x ◘ \xo 29:13 \xt Mt. 15:8; Mk. 7:6\x*
\v 14 s uya, xzar, Necc arenniɣ ad ggeɣ di řgens-a s řeɛjeb, s řeɛjeb d ustebhet. Tiɣit n imiɣisen ad tefna u řefhamet n ifehhamen ad tweddar.”\x ◘ \xo 29:14 \xt Irm. 49:7; Ɛub. 8; Mt. 11:25; 1 Kur. 1:19\x*
\b
\m 
\v 15 \bd Uct\bd* x yinni issnuffaran zzat i SIDI, inni issdurruyen axarriṣ nsen, uca tteggen timegga nsen di ṭṭřam, \add umi\add* qqaren: ‘Wi d aneɣ iẓrin d wi d aneɣ issnen?’ \x ◘ \xo 29:15 \xt Izhd. 94:7\x*
\v 16 Kenniw tessenqeřbem \add tamesřact\add*! Axmi zeɛma izemmar ad ittwaḥseb bu-třaxt am třaxt, ařami min ittwaggen ad yini x wenni t iggin: ‘Netta war d ayi iggi!’, uca řqecɛet n třaxt ad tini x uqeddar nnes: ‘Netta war ittḥiki walu!’” \x ◘ \xo 29:16 \xt Ica. 45:9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 17 “Ma war iǧi drus i iqqimen ař ɣa idweř Lubnan d řɛarset iṣebḥen u ad tᵉttwaḥseb řɛarset iṣebḥen d azɣar? \f ◼ \fr 29:17 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\v 18 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad sřen idehcuren awařen n wedlis-a ittwannḍen, uca ad twařant tiṭṭawin n iḍarɣařen zi taǧest u zi ṭṭřam. \x ◘ \xo 29:18 \xt Mt. 11:5\x*
\v 19 Ad arnin imwaḍɛen di řefraḥet di SIDI, uca ad farḥen imezřaḍ jar iwdan deg Umqeddas n Israil.
\m 
\v 20 Maɣar bu-řexcunet ad iqḍa, wenni isthezan ad ifna, u marra inni yarezzun řɣecc ad nnqeḍɛen,
\v 21 inni itteggen řɛib di bnadem zi ssibbet n ijj n wawař \add waha\add*, inni issrusan řefxux i yinni ideffɛen řḥeqq di tewwart \add n tendint\add*, uřa d inni iɛarrnen amsegged ɣar uɣezdis x walu.” \x ◘ \xo 29:21 \xt Ɛam. 5:10\x*
\b
\m 
\v 22 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI, wenni ifekken Ibrahim, i taddart n Yaɛqub: ‘Yaɛqub war ittseḍḥi \add ɛad\add* uca aɣembub nnes war ittewriɣ \add ɛad\add*.
\v 23 Maɣar xmi ɣa iẓar netta tarwa nnes, inni d řxedmet n ifassen inu, di řwesṭ nnes, ad ssqeddsen nitni Isem inu, ad ssqeddsen Amqeddas n Yaɛqub u ad ggʷeden AREBBI n Israil.
\v 24 Inni iweddaren di buḥbeř ad ɣarsen tiři tussna n řefhamet, uca inni ittnedqamen, ad arzmen tawwart ad řemden.’”
\b
\b
\c 30
\s1 Řɛahd ibeṭṭřen ak-d Miṣra
\m 
\v 1 “\add Ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI: ‘\bd Uct\bd* x iḥenjiren nni iɣewwɣen maḥend ad ssuffɣen ccwar, \add maca\add* war iǧi zzayi, maḥend ad ggen ijj n řɛahd, \add maca\add* war iǧi \add zi\add* Arruḥ inu, ḥima ad ssɛurrcen ddenb x ddenb,
\v 2 inni igguren maḥend ad hwan ɣar Miṣra nhřa ma ad ayi sseqsan, ḥima ad afen aseřqi ɣar jjehd n firɛun u maḥend ad arewřen ɣar tiři n Miṣra.
\v 3 \add Maca\add* jjehd n firɛun ad kenniw yarr tᵉttseḍḥam uca adurri di yiři n Miṣra ad kenniw ifḍeḥ.
\v 4 Maɣar řḥukkam nnes ǧan di Ṣuɛan uca imsekkan nnes iwḍen ɣar Ḥanis.
\v 5 Nitni marra ad ttwassbarrqen zi řgens nni war d asen ineffɛen ca, war itticen afus uřa d walu n řefḍeř, maca ad ten yawi ɣar řefḍiḥet d řhegra.” \x ◘ \xo 30:5 \xt Irm. 2:36\x*
\b
\m 
\v 6 \bd Řḥukm issaggʷaden x řmař n \bdit Temmurt n\bdit* Ljanub.\bd* “Deg ict n temmurt n řeḥṣaret d ddeǧ, mani zzayes dd-usin tayradt d weyrad d ufiɣar d řḥaycet icemḍen iṭṭawen, arebbun-dd nitni agřa nsen x weɛrur n isnusen d řeknuz nsen x teɛrurin n iřeɣman ɣar ijj n řgens war ten ineffeɛ di ca. \x ◘ \xo 30:6 \xt Ica. 14:29\x*
\v 7 \add Maɣar\add* Miṣra ad iwc afus baṭeř u i walu. S uya řaɣiɣ \add Miṣra\add* wanita: ‘Rahab, \add bu-teɣruḍt ameqqran\add*, teqqim waha!’”
\b
\s1 Taɣennant n Israil
\m 
\v 8 “\add Xenni\add* řexxu, as-dd, ari t zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen x teřwiḥt, xebc i-t deg ict n tebrat ittwannḍen, \add maḥend\add* ad tiři tᵉttwaḥḍa ař ass i dd ɣa yasen, i řebda n řebdat.
\v 9 Maɣar nitni d řgens iɣewwɣen, ayt n bu-ixarriqen, iḥenjiren nni war ixsen ad sřen i Ccariɛa n SIDI,
\v 10 inni iqqaren i imwařawen: ‘War ttwiřim walu!’, u i yinni ixezzaren iweḥḥan: ‘War ttwiřim iweḥḥan nni iǧan d tidett. Siwřem akidneɣ min dd issḥinniben, \add mři\add* d aneɣ tᵉttwařam min iɣeccen!
\v 11 Ḥeyydem zeg webrid, ffɣem zeg webrid, jjem Amqeddas n Israil ad xaneɣ yiggʷej!’”
\m 
\v 12 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Umqeddas n Israil: ‘Minzi kenniw tenḍarem awař-a, tᵉttecřem x ddeǧ u x min iffɣen \add zeg webrid\add*, \add wah,\add* tᵉtteggem řaman nwem di man aya,
\v 13 s uya ad tiři řmuɛṣiyyet-a i kenniw am tazzit \add di řḥiḍ\add* i ɣa iwḍan, nni iḍehharen di řḥiḍ yuɛřan, aqa tareẓẓit nnes ad dd-tas deɣya, deg ict n tecti. \x ◘ \xo 30:13 \xt Ica. 29:5\x*
\v 14 Ad t yarẓ am ittwarẓ ijj n uɣarraf n bu-třaxt nhřa aḥinni. Jar marra ifetwiten nnes war ittwaf \add ́́́ɛad\add* uřa d ijj n uceqquf ɛad i zi dd ɣa yawyen timessi zi řmejmar niɣ ad aymen aman zi jjub.’” \x ◘ \xo 30:14 \xt Irm. 19:11\x*
\b
\s1 Ttubet tᵉttawi-dd aḥinni d usgenfi zi Arebbi
\m 
\v 15 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, Amqeddas n Israil: ‘S ttubet d řhudnet ad ɣarwem yiři usenjem, di trusi d řaman ad ɣarwem yiři jjehd, maca kenniw war texsem.’
\v 16 Kenniw teqqarem: ‘Lla, x yeysan nexs ad narweř!’ X uya \add s uɣiř\add* ad tarewřem. Uca \add teqqarem ɛawed\add*: ‘X iysan n ḥamat nexs ad nniy \add i tarewřat\add*!’ X uya ad qeǧqen uřa d imseḍfaren nwem!
\v 17 Ijj n řuřuf ad yarweř i uheddi n yijj \add n weryaz\add*. I uheddi n xemsa ad tarewřem marra ař ɣa teqqimem am tsenyant n ucenyal x tqiccet n wedrar, am tɛeǧant x tewrirt.” \x ◘ \xo 30:17 \xt Ica. 17:6; 24:6, 13\x*
\m 
\v 18 “S uya ad raja SIDI maḥend ad awem isscen aḥinni nnes, s uyenni ad igeɛɛed sennej ařami i ɣa yarḥem kenniw \add awarni man aya\add*, maɣar SIDI d AREBBI n řḥeqq. Sseɛd n marra inni t ittrajan. \x ◘ \xo 30:18 \xt Izhd. 2:12; 34:9; Awřn. 16:20; Irm. 17:7\x*
\v 19 Maɣar řgens ad izdeɣ di Ṣihyun, di Urcalim. Cek war tᵉttrud ɛemmarṣ ɛad, Netta ad xak iḥinn, mařa isřa i tmijja nnec tᵉttřaɣa, ad xak dd-yarr.
\v 20 Sidi inu ad awem iwc aɣrum di řeḥṣaret uřa d aman di řeɣben, imesɣaren nnec war ittnuffaren \add ɛad\add*, \add maca\add* tiṭṭawin nnec ad ẓarent imesɣaren nnec.
\v 21 Imezzuɣen nnec ad sřen i wawař zi ɣar ḍeffar nnec i iqqaren: ‘Aqa abrid, uyurem dayes. War tteffɣem yefus uřa d azeřmaḍ.’
\m 
\v 22 Ad tḥesbem icellelen i ittwaggen s nnuqart nnec n řexyařat nnec ineqcen uřa d ařeḥḥef n wureɣ n řexyařat nnec ifesyen d texmuji. Ad ten tenḍared am warruḍ tessexmej i-t \add temɣart i x ǧan\add* idammen, ad tinid: ‘Ɣar barra!’”
\m 
\v 23 “\add Xenni\add* ad iwc Netta anẓar i zzariɛet nnec i tzarɛed deg iyyar uřa d aɣrum d ṣṣabet n temmurt nnec. \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad tehda tḥimart nnec x ddmani isarrḥen.
\v 24 Iyenduzen d yeɣyař imeẓyanen, inni icarrzen tammurt, ad ccen řeɛřef iredd i zuzzaren s ǧuḥ d tezzart.
\v 25 X kuř adrar u x kuř tawrirt igeɛɛden ad iřint tiɣezratin d tmizabin ccuren s waman, deg wass n tɣarṣt tameqqrant, xmi ɣa wḍan ṣṣumɛat.
\v 26 Tafawt n tziri ad tiři am tfawt n tfuct uca tafawt n tfuct ad tiři tejhed sebɛa n tseqqar x tfawt n sebɛa n wussan, deg wass i di i ɣa icfen SIDI tareẓẓit n řgens nnes uca ad issgenfa ayezzim n tecti i iwta Netta.”
\b
\s1 Řḥukm i dd ɣa yasen x Accur
\m 
\v 27 “Xzar, ittas-dd Isem n SIDI zi řaggʷaj, yareqq weɣḍab nnes u asiggʷed imɣar, ccuren iyencicen nnes s wesxeḍ u iřes nnes igga am tmessi ittetten.
\v 28 Asuḍi n nnefs nnes am yeɣzar issefyen, ittakkwaḍen ař iri, maḥend ad izzuzar řegnus s tazzart n ureddeǧ, u maḥend ad yegg i řegnus sřimet n uɣarri x iɣesmaren nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 30:28 \xt Ica. 8:8\x*
\m 
\v 29 “Ad ɣarwem yiři ijj n izři, am di ǧiřet nni di issewjed bnadem ixef nnes i řɛid, uřa d řefraḥet deg wuř am ɣar ijjen igguren umi iẓemmar di temja maḥend ad dd-yas ɣar wedrar n SIDI, ɣar Teṣḍart n Israil.
\v 30 SIDI ad yejj ad sřen i tmijja nnes yuɛřan uca ad isscen mammec ɣa ihwa uɣiř nnes ak-d wesxeḍ n weɣḍab d tmessi itteḥduduqen ittetten, aduqqez n wenẓar d řḥař n wenẓar d ibquqen n tebruri.
\v 31 Maɣar Accur ad yarjij s tmijja n SIDI xmi \add t\add* ɣa iwwet Netta s weɛmud nnes.
\v 32 Qaɛ twařa iɛeddu xas weɛmud n usegged, \add aɛmud\add* nni xas issars SIDI, \add aqa\add* d man aya ad yiři ɣar \add tinext n\add* ibendiren d \add snitrat n\add* řgambriyyat, \add maɣar\add* Netta akidsen immneɣ s iɣaǧen ittenhezzan.
\v 33 Maɣar zeg wecḥař uya iwjed \add wemcan i\add* nnɛi nni, iwjed uřa i ujeǧid. Igga i-t yuǧeɣ d umiriw. Aqellij nnes n tmessi d ukeccuḍ d ameqqran. Twarrit n nnefs n SIDI ad t iqedd am yeɣzar n řecbariyyet.”
\b
\b
\c 31
\s1 War ttecřem x Miṣra
\m 
\v 1 “\bd Uct\bd* x yinni dd-ihwan ɣar Miṣra ḥima ad afen twiza, inni ittecřen x yeysan u tteggen řaman deg ikarruten, minzi nitni deg waṭṭas, uřa x yinni inyin x yeysan, minzi nitni jjehden, \add axmi\add* war xezzaren ɣar Umqeddas n Israil u war arezzun SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 31:1 \xt Izhd. 20:8; Irm. 17:5\x*
\m 
\v 2 “\add Maca\add* uřa d Netta d amiɣis, Netta ggur ad yejj řɣar ad dd-yas. War ittdikkwiř deg wawař nnes, ad ikkar ḍidd i taddart n iɛeffanen u ḍidd i twiza n yinni itteggen řmuɛṣiyyet.
\v 3 \add Maɣar\add* Imiṣriyyen d iwdan, war ǧin d Arebbi, uca iysan nsen d aysum, war iǧi d arruḥ. Ad isarreḥ SIDI afus nnes \add ař\add* i ɣa inqarḍ wenni iwcin afus, uca \add xenni\add* ad iwḍa uřa d wenni dayes iwcin afus. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa qḍan nitni marra idsen.”
\m 
\v 4 “Maɣar ammu i d ayi inna SIDI: ‘Am mammec ittarrujdud wayrad niɣ wayrad ameẓyan x zzardet nnes xmi xas dd-ttřaɣan ijj n ubarru n imeksawen, břa ma ad innexřeɛ zi tmijja nsen u war ixennes zeg ubarru nsen, ammu i ɣa ihwa uřa d SIDI n řɛeskarat ḥima ad immneɣ x wedrar n Ṣihyun u x tewrirt nnes. \f ◼ \fr 31:4 \fk imeksawen\ft - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*
\v 5 Am yijḍaḍ ittfarfiren \add sennej i řɛucc nsen\add*, ammu i ɣa isseřqa SIDI n řɛeskarat x Urcalim. Ad tt issar, ad tt issenjem, ad \add xas\add* yekk uca ad tt issenjem.” \x ◘ \xo 31:5 \xt Aɛwd. 32:11\x*
\m 
\v 6 “Dewřem-dd ɣar wenni x ḥeyyden ayt n Israil s waṭṭas.
\v 7 Maɣar \bd deg wass nni\bd* ad immenḍar kuř ijj l’aṣnam nnes n nnuqart d l’aṣnam nnes n wureɣ, inni yeggin ifassen nwem i yixef nwem, \add i\add* ddenb. \x ◘ \xo 31:7 \xt Ica. 2:20\x*
\v 8 Accur ad iwḍa s ssif, war iǧi \add ssif\add* n ijj n weryaz. Ad t yecc ssif, war iǧi n ijj n bnadem. Ad yarweř Accur zzat i ssif uca iḥudriyyen nnes ad dewřen ɣar tesmuɣi.
\v 9 Taṣḍart nnes ad teggʷej s tiggʷudi uca řḥukkam nnes ad arewřen zi tɛeǧant!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, wenni ɣar teǧa tmessi di Ṣihyun uřa d tafqunt di Urcalim.” \x ◘ \xo 31:9 \xt 2 Ij. 19:36,37\x*
\b
\b
\c 32
\s1 Ajeǧid amsegged i d ɣa yasen
\m 
\v 1 “Xzar, ijj n ujeǧid ad iḥkem di tsegda u řḥukkam ad ḥekmen s řḥeqq. \x ◘ \xo 32:1 \xt Izhd. 45:7; Zak. 9:9\x*
\v 2 Aryaz nni ad yiři am yijj n udurri zeg wenẓar, am tseddart issřeqqan zi tḥaryaḍt, am tɣezratin n waman di temmurt yuẓɣen, am tiři n ijj n jjarf ideqřen di temmurt ittfadan.
\v 3 Tiṭṭawin n yinni ittwařan war ttbelliɛent \add ɛad\add*, u imezzuɣen n yinni ittesřan ad ssḥessen \add ɛawed\add*, \x ◘ \xo 32:3 \xt Ica. 29:18; 30:21\x*
\v 4 uř n imqeǧqen ad yiři iḥeṭṭa \add ɛawed\add* maḥend ad yaf tussna, u iřes n yinni isstewtiwen izemmar ad issiweř ɛawed s řfarz.
\m 
\v 5 Abuhaři war d as ttřiɣin \add ɛad\add* ‘Amcenneɛ!’, uca wenni icemmten war d as qqaren \add ɛad\add* ‘Mmis n řxir!’
\v 6 Maɣar abuhaři issawař tubbuheřya u uř nnes ittegg řmuɛṣiyyet umi netta ittegg afucceḥ u ittceqqef di SIDI, u umi ittejji řeɛmar n wenni iǧuẓen ad iqqim ixwa, d wenni iffuden war t ittejji ad isu.
\v 7 Taḥraymect n ucemmat tɛeffen. Netta ittxarreṣ di řefḍiḥet ḥima ad iɣḍeř inni ittwaḥṣaren s wawařen ixarriqen, \add waxxa\add* amezřuḍ iccat x řḥeqq \add nnes\add*.
\v 8 \add Maca\add* amcenneɛ ad ixarreṣ deg inwayen icennɛen, ad ikkar di ṭṭweɛ n min icennɛen.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Kkarent, \add kennint\add* timɣarin war di iǧi wemnus, sřent i tmijja inu, \add a kennint\add* tiḥenjirin ittcařen x simant nkent, sřent ɣar wawař inu!
\v 10 Awarni wussan niɣ aseggʷas, \add xenni\add* ad tarjijent, \add a\add* kennint i ittcařen x yixef nkent, maɣar ad teqḍa ṣṣabet n uḍiř, war ittiři weřqaḍ ɛad.
\v 11 Qefqfent, \add a kennint\add* nbřa amnus, arjijent, \add kennint\add* tinni ittcařent x yixef nkent, kksent arruḍ, ɛarynent, \add xenni\add* beysent tijɛinnatin nkent \add s warruḍ n wecḍan\add*.”
\m 
\v 12 “Ad wtent nitenti deg idmaren s igejduren x iḥwicen iɛizzen, x tzayarin isseɣmayen.
\v 13 Ad geɛɛden isennanen d tzeggʷart x temmurt n řgens inu, \add wah,\add* x marra tudrin n řefraḥet di tendint ineggzen s usřewřiw.
\v 14 Maɣar řeqṣar ad ittwajj, ddriz n tendint ad ibkem, \add tawrirt n\add* ‘Ɛufil’ d lburj n tɛessast ad dewřen d ifran i řebda, d amcan n řefraḥet mani ttemzuɛbuḍen iɣyař n řexřa, d ddmani i tḥimriwin.
\v 15 ař ɣa ittwafarreɣ xaneɣ Arruḥ zi sennej.”
\m “\add Xenni\add* ad idweř řexřa d řɛirst iṣebḥen u řɛirst iṣebḥen ad tᵉttwaḥseb d azɣar. \f ◼ \fr 32:15 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 32:15 \xt Ica. 29:17; Yuw. 3:1; Yḥ. 7:37, 38; Řex. 2:17, 18\x*
\v 16 Řḥeqq ad izdeɣ di řexřa uca tasegda ad teqqim deg iyyar isseɣmayen.
\v 17 Min dd-ittawyen tasegda ad yiři d řehna uca řɣiǧet n tsegda ad tiři d řhudnet d řaman i řebda.
\v 18 Řgens inu ad izdeɣ deg wemcan n řehna, di tzeddiɣin daysent řaman u deg imucan daysen arraḥet.” \x ◘ \xo 32:18 \xt Irm. 33:16\x*
\m 
\v 19 “Ad teccat tbrurri ař dd ɣa tessehwa azɣar uca tandint ad tehwa di řewḍa.”
\m 
\v 20 “Sseɛd n kenniw inni izarrɛen ɣar marra tiɣezratin, inni \add din\add* ineddhen iḍaren n ufunas d weɣyuř!”
\b
\b
\c 33
\s1 Řeḥṣaret n Urcalim d usenjem nnes
\m 
\v 1 “\bd Uct\bd* xak, \add a\add* amteḥḥay, \add cek d\add* wenni \add simant nnes\add* war ittwateḥḥi, \add cek d\add* wenni ittkeccḍen, waxxa nitni war cek keccḍen. Mařa tkemmřed ateḥḥi nnec, ad tᵉttwateḥḥid \add simant nnec\add*, mařa tkemmřed takeccaḍt, ad tᵉttwakeccḍed \add simant nnec\add*.”
\b
\m 
\v 2 “\add A\add* SIDI, ḥinn xaneɣ, aqa nessitim ac. Iři d aɣiř nsen \add ijehden\add* di kuř ṣṣbeḥ, wah, di řweqt n řeḥsaret iři d asenjem nneɣ.”
\b
\m 
\v 3 “X řḥess n zzhir ad arewřen řegnus. Mařa Cek tessgeɛɛded Ixef nnec ad ttwazeǧɛen řegnus ɣar marra iɣezdisa.
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* ad tᵉttwakkes zzardet nwem, am tmurɣi iṣarrḍen ttekksent \add ṣṣabet\add*. Am ttazzřent tmurɣi ssa d ssa, ammu i ttazzřen uřa d nitni ɣar zzardet.”
\m 
\v 5 “Ittwassuɛřa SIDI maɣar Netta izeddeɣ qaɛ sennej. Netta iccur Ṣihyun s řḥeqq d tsegda.
\v 6 Ad yiři řaman \add xmi i ɣa yiřint\add* řmijařat n řweqt nnec, ijj n ubarru n isenjamen, tiɣit d tussna. Ad tiři tiggʷudi n SIDI d řkenz nnes.”
\m 
\v 7 “Xzar, inni daysen taryast amecnaw ayrad sɣuyyun barra, \add wah,\add* ireqqasen n řehna ttrun s imeṭṭawen imerzagen.
\v 8 Ibriden iseggmen ttwajjen, wenni innumen ad yekk x umesruq, ismeḥ dayes. Aqa yarẓa řɛahd, isseḥqar tineddam, war iḥesseb bnadem.
\v 9 Tecḍen u tisřaw temmurt. Lubnan iseḍḥa, yuẓeɣ. \add Řewḍa isseɣmayen n\add* Carun tedweř d řexřa uca Bacan d Karmal ttseǧḍen \add afar nsen\add*.”
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Řexxu ad kkareɣ, řexxu ad ttwassgeɛɛdeɣ, řexxu ad ttwassɛuǧeɣ, iqqar SIDI.”
\b
\m 
\v 11 “Kenniw teksim ddeyset s uřum, ad tarwem iɣeǧ. Buḥbeř nwem d timessi i kenniw ɣa yeccen.
\v 12 Řegnus ad dewřen am jjar ssarɣen t, am řḥarrac s isennanen ittwaqessen ad ten sscemḍen s tmessi.
\v 13 Kenniw \add i iǧan\add* di řaggʷaj, sřem min ggiɣ, uca kenniw di řadas, snem ṣṣulṭa inu!
\v 14 Imednab di Ṣihyun tteggʷeden, imnafqen ttqefqafen, qqaren: ‘Man wen zzayneɣ izemmar ad izdeɣ di tmessi ittetten, man wen zzayneɣ izemmar ad izdeɣ di řḥaduq n řebda?’”
\m 
\v 15 “Wenni igguren di tsegda u iqqar řḥeqq, wenni inḍaren arbeḥ s ubeɛɛej, wenni imennɛen ifassen nnes zeg wuḍuf n terzifin n arrecwet, wenni ittbellaɛen amezzuɣ nnes meɛlik yufa ad iseř x usizzeř n idammen, wenni itteqqnen tiṭṭawin nnes meɛlik yufa ad itwařa min iǧan d aɛeffan, \x ◘ \xo 33:15 \xt Izhd. 15:2; 24:3\x*
\v 16 d wanita i ɣa izedɣen x řegɛudi. Lqelɛat di řejruf ad iřint lburj nnes yuɛřan, ad as immewc weɣrum nnes, aman nnes ad ttwaḍemnen.
\v 17 Tiṭṭawin nnec ad twařant Ajeǧid deg weẓri nnes, nitenti ad ẓarent ict n temmurt dayes ttasiɛ aṭṭas.
\v 18 Uř nnec ad iɛqeř x usnexřiɛ. Mani iǧa umarir? Mani iǧa wenni iweznen? Mani iǧa wenni isseṭṭen lburjat?
\v 19 Cek war tẓarred ɛad řgens iqesḥen \add nni\add*, řgens s yiřes ideqřen ařami war izemmar ad as iseř \add bnadem\add*, \add řgens\add* nni issṭewṭiwen s yiřes ařami war izemmar ad as ifhem \add uřa d ijj\add*.”
\m 
\v 20 “Xzar ɣar Ṣihyun, tandint n umuniten nneɣ. Tiṭṭawin nnec ad ẓarent Urcalim, tazeddiɣt nni di iǧa řaman, Aqiḍun i war ssmuṭṭuyen, i zi řewtad nnes ɛemmarṣ ad ttwaqeřɛen uřa d imurar nnes war ttwaqeṭṭasen. \x ◘ \xo 33:20 \xt Izhd. 46:6; 125:1, 2\x*
\v 21 Maɣar dinni ad ɣarneɣ yiři SIDI s řɛezz. Aya ad yiři d amcan n iɣezran d tseǧyawin imiriwen. War xasen nedhen iɣarruba imeqqranen n řemqadef, uřa d ijj n uɣarrabu s řejwad ad \add din\add* iɛdu.
\v 22 Minzi SIDI d Řqaḍi nneɣ, SIDI d Amgewwad nneɣ, SIDI d Ajeǧid nneɣ. Netta ad aneɣ issenjem.”
\m 
\v 23 “\add Řexxu maca\add* arxun iseɣwan nnem, war mennɛen \add ɛad\add* tisenyanin deg uḍar nnes, war ttbezzaɛen \add ɛad\add* řbacc. \add Maca\add* di řweqt nni ad tᵉttwabḍa zzardet tameqqrant, \add ɛad\add* ineɛḍab ad keccḍen takeccaḍt.
\v 24 Uřa d ijj n umezduɣ ad yini: ‘Necc heřceɣ!’, \add maɣar\add* řgens i dayes izeddɣen, ad \add as\add* ittwaɣfar řmuɛṣiyyet.”
\b
\b
\c 34
\s1 Řḥukm n Arebbi x Idum
\m 
\v 1 “Qarrbem-dd, \add a\add* řegnus, maḥend ad tesřem, \add kenniw a,\add* ccuɛub, arrem-dd řbař! Seř, \add a\add* tammurt d marra min dayes, ddunect d marra min zzayes dd-issfuffuyen.
\v 2 Maɣar aduqqez \add n weɣḍab\add* n SIDI \add ad dd-yas\add* x marra řegnus u asɛar x marra řɛeskar nsen. Netta iḥarrem i-ten \add i uteḥḥi\add*, aqa igga i-ten i tɣarṣt.
\v 3 Inni zzaysen ittwanɣen ad ten nḍaren, uca arriḥet n řxecbat nsen ad tgeɛɛed. Ad fesyen idurar s idammen nsen.
\v 4 Marra řɛeskar n ujenna ad ifna uca ijenwan ad ttwannḍen am wedlis ittwannḍen u ad iwḍa marra řɛeskar nsen am wafar x tzayart u am mammec dd-tewḍa tazart zeg wartu.” \x ◘ \xo 34:4 \xt Asa. 6:13, 14\x*
\m 
\v 5 “Maɣar ssif inu ad ittwaẓar deg ijenwan. Xzar, ad dd-ihwa x Idum u x řgens nni ḥarrmeɣ qaɛ i řḥukm.
\v 6 Ssif n SIDI iccur s idammen, idweř itteḥruǧuḍ s tadunt, s idammen n izmaren d iɣayḍen, s tadunt n tiẓẓař n icarriyyen, maɣar SIDI igga ijj n řɛid n tɣarṣt di Buṣra, d ict n tɣarṣt tameqqrant di temmurt n Idum. \f ◼ \fr 34:6 \fk tiẓẓař\ft - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 34:6 \xt Ica. 63:1, 2\x*
\v 7 Ad kidsen wḍan iɣayḍen n řexřa ak-d waccawen nsen d iziraren, uca uřa d ifunasen imeẓyanen \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d \add ifunasen\add* ijehden uca tammurt nsen ad tsu idammen u acař \add n temmurt\add* ad ijjwen s tadunt.
\v 8 Maɣar ad yiři ijj n wass n nneqmet i SIDI, ijj n useggʷas n uxeǧeṣ i ddeɛwet n Ṣihyun.
\v 9 Tiɣzarin n Idum ad dewřent d tizeft u acař nnes ad idweř d řecbariyyet, \add wah,\add* tammurt nnes ad tedweř d tizeft yareqqen.
\v 10 War ttxessi \add tmessi nnes\add* s ǧiřet uřa s wass, ddexxan nnes ad igeɛɛed i řebda. Zi jjiř ař jjiř ad tiři \add temmurt\add* tᵉttwareddeǧ, i řebda n řebdat ɛemmarṣ war tt iẓwi uřa d ijj. \x ◘ \xo 34:10 \xt Asa. 14:11; 19:3\x*
\v 11 Bu-uɛuqqi d twuct n ǧiřet ad tt ṭṭfen d tasɣart, bu-usuḍi \add n řmewt\add* d ubaɣeř ad dayes zedɣen. Netta ad xas imḥeḍ afiřu n řeɛbar n řexřa u ad issars plumu n řxawi. \x ◘ \xo 34:11 \xt Ica. 13:21, 22; Ṣaf. 2:14; Asa. 18:2\x*
\v 12 Tarwa nnes n taṣiřet? War din teǧi bu tgelda ařami zzayes i ɣa barrḥen u marra řḥukkam nnes qḍan.
\v 13 Di řeqṣur nnes ad igeɛɛed cbarq ak-d isennanen, irezzazen d tabɣa n usennan ad ɣemyen di lqelɛat nnes. Tammurt ad tedweř d tazeddiɣt i wuccanen n řexřa, d ijj n weḥwic i yessis n nnɛamet.
\v 14 Řewḥuc n řexřa ad mmeřqan ak-d ifisen uca amyan \add ijennen\add* ad iřaɣa i umɛacar nnes, wah, řweḥc n ǧiřet ad yareyyeḥ dinni, ad yaf aɣimi i yixef nnes.
\v 15 Dinni ad tessars tfiɣart n fřitca řɛucc nnes, ad tessars timeǧařin, ad tent tessfruriy uca di tiři nnes ad thilla \add deg imeẓyanen nnes\add*, wah, dinni ad munen ijḍaḍ ittkeccaḍen.
\v 16 Arzum deg wedlis n SIDI u ɣarem zzayes: ‘Uřa d ijj \add zi řewḥuc-a\add* izemmar ad zzayes inqeṣ, uřa d ijj war yarezzu x weɛcir nnes!’, maɣar aqemmum inu yura i-t, uca Arruḥ nnes d wenni ten i ɣa issmunen.
\v 17 Netta simant nnes inḍar taqedduḥt di ṭṭweɛ nsen, uca afus nnes ibḍa asen tammurt s ufiřu n řeɛbar. Nitni ad tt warten i řebda, zi jjiř ař jjiř ad dayes zedɣen.”
\b
\b
\c 35
\s1 Nneqmet n Arebbi ad dd-tawi asenjem
\m 
\v 1 “Ad ifarḥ řexřa d temmurt yuẓɣen, ad tesřiwřew řewḍa, ad tnewwar am tnewwact war zzayes wḍant tifray ɛemmarṣ.
\v 2 Ad tnewwar ad tcuwwar, \add wah,\add* ad tesřewřiw \add řewḍa\add* s řefraḥet d usřiwřew. Ad as immewc uɛuǧi n Lubnan, řɛezz n Karmil u \add n řewḍa n\add* Carun. Nitni ad ẓaren aɛuǧi n SIDI, řɛezz n AREBBI nneɣ.”
\m 
\v 3 “Smeḥḍem ifassen arxun u sjehdem ifadden ittemraywan. \x ◘ \xo 35:3 \xt Ɛbr. 12:12\x*
\v 4 Inim i yinni ɣar iǧa uř iggʷed: ‘Iřim d iryazen, war tteggʷedem! Xzarem, AREBBI nwem ad ixřef, ad dd-yas wexřaf n AREBBI, Netta ad dd-yas s Yixef nnes, ad kenniw issenjem.’
\v 5 Xenni ad nnurzment tiṭṭawin n iḍarɣařen uca ad ttwarezmen imezzuɣen n iduhcar. \x ◘ \xo 35:5 \xt Mt. 9:27; 11:5; 12:22; 20:30; 21:14; Yḥ. 9:6\x*
\v 6 Xenni ad ingez uqidar am udad uca iřes n uzinun ad isřiwřew, maɣar ad dduqqzen waman di řexřa uřa d tiɣzarin di řewḍa. \x ◘ \xo 35:6 \xt Mt. 9:32; 11:5; 15:30; 21:14; Yḥ. 5:8, 9; 7:38, 39; Řex. 3:2; 8:7; 14:8\x*
\v 7 Tammurt yuẓɣen ad tedweř d ssarij u tammurt iffuden d tařawin ittbeqbuqen. Di temmurt n wuccanen n řexřa, mani arreyḥen, ad yiři arbiɛ ak-d uɣanim d wezraf.”
\m 
\v 8 “Ad din yiři ijj n webrid iseggmen, abrid nni i ɣa řaɣan ‘Abrid amqeddas!’. Uřa d ijj n umexmuj war xas iggur, \add maca\add* ad yiři i nitni: man wen ma igguren x webrid-a, \add ɛad\add* ibuhařiyyen war ttweddirin.
\v 9 War dinni ittiři wayrad, \add wah,\add* war xas ittgiɛɛid niɣ ad ittwaf din uřa d ijj n řweḥc ittcarreg, \add maca\add* inni ittwafekken ad xas uyuren.
\v 10 Inni ittwaṣeřḥen zi SIDI ad ɛeqben, ad dd-asen sřiwřiwen ɣar Ṣihyun. Řefraḥet n řebda \add ad tarsa\add* x izeǧifen nsen. Afarrej d řefraḥet ad ɣarsen awḍen, acḍan d wesḥissef ad \add zzaysen\add* arewřen.” \x ◘ \xo 35:10 \xt Asa. 21:4\x*
\b
\b
\c 36
\s1 Ahuddi n Sanḥarib ḍidd i Urcalim
\m 
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss arbeɛṭac n ujeǧid Ḥizqiya igeɛɛed Sanḥarib, ajeǧid n Accur, x marra tineddam ifaryen n Yahuda uca iḥewwes i-tent.
\v 2 Isekk ujeǧid n Accur akumandar n řɛeskar zi Laxic ɣar Urcalim ɣar ujeǧid Ḥizqiya, ak-d ijj n řɛeskar d ameqqran aṭṭas. Netta ibedd ɣar uqadus n waman n uyeřmam n sennej, wenni \add iǧan\add* ɣar webrid ameqqran ɣar Weḥwic n Uṣebban. *
\b
\m 
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ ɣares Alyaqim, mmis n Ḥilqiya, řemqeddem n tzeddiɣt \add n ujeǧid\add* ak-d umarir Cibna d Yuwax, mmis n Asaf, amarir n umezruy.
\v 4 Inna asen ukumandar n řɛeskar: “Inim xenni i Ḥizqiya: Ammu i iqqar ujeǧid ameqqran, ajeǧid n Accur: ‘Man atecři wa i x tᵉttacřed?
\v 5 Nniɣ ac, aqa-t d řhard n iyencicen waha. Deg umenɣi ittxeṣṣa ccwar d tzemmar. Man wen x tᵉttacřed řexxu, aqa cek tɣewwɣed xafi?
\v 6 Xzar, tᵉttecřed x Miṣra, x uɣanim nni innḍefsen wenni ittejjun deg ufus nnes umi ḥed xas i ɣa iɛemmed, uca \add xenni\add* issnuqqeb i-t. Ammu \add i iǧa\add* firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, i marra inni xas ittacřen. \x ◘ \xo 36:6 \xt Ḥiz. 29:6, 7\x*
\v 7 Mařa kenniw ad d ayi tinim: Neccin nettaceř x SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ!, \add xenni necc ad iniɣ:\add* Ma Netta war iǧi d wenni zi iḥeyyed Ḥizqiya řegɛudi d iɛalṭaren u \add xenni\add* inna i Yahuda d Urcalim: Ad tbendqem zzat i uɛalṭar-a di Urcalim?’
\v 8 Xenni řexxu, egg ijj n umḥarrem ak-d sidi inu, ajeǧid n Accur: ‘Necc ad ac wceɣ ařfayen n iysan mařa cek zeg uɣezdis nnec ad asen-dd tawyed imnayen.’
\v 9 Mammec texsed cek ad tenqeřbed x wudem n lwali, wenni qaɛ d ameẓyan n imsexxaren n sidi inu, uca ad tᵉttecřed x Miṣra di ssibbet n ikarruten d imnayen?
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, ma necc geɛɛdeɣ-dd ḍidd n wemcan-a ḥima ad t areddǧeɣ břa SIDI? SIDI ini ayi: ‘Geɛɛed ḍidd i temmurt-a, areddeǧ i-tt.’”
\m 
\v 11 Uca inna Alyaqim, mmis n Ḥilqiya, ak-d Cibna d Yuwax i ukumandar n řɛeskar: “Siweř ɛafek s Tramit ak-d imsexxaren nnec, minzi nefhem as mliḥ. War kidneɣ ssiwiř s Tyahudect deg imezzuɣen n řgens \add i iǧan\add* x řḥiḍ.”
\m 
\v 12 \add Maca\add* akumandar n řɛeskar inna: “Ma issekk ayi-dd sidi inu ɣar sidi nnec u ɣarek \add waha\add* ḥima ad ssiwřeɣ awařen-a, war iǧi ɣar yeryazen nni iqqimen x řḥiḍ, \add maḥend ad iniɣ\add* aqa aten \add jmiɛ\add* akidwem ad ccen asuffeɣ nsen u ad swen ibeccicen nsen?” \x ◘ \xo 36:12 \xt 2 Ij. 18:27\x*
\v 13 Xenni ikkar ukumandar, iřaɣa s jjhed s Tyahudect, issiweř, inna: “Sřem i wawařen n ujeǧid ameqqran, ajeǧid n Accur!
\v 14 Ammu i iqqar ujeǧid: ‘Ḥḍam war kenniw ittɣecci Ḥizqiya minzi netta war izemmar ad kenniw ifekk.
\v 15 War ttejjim Ḥizqiya ad kenniw yarr ad tᵉtecřem x SIDI, ad tinim: SIDI ad aneɣ issenjem nican u war tᵉttmewci tendint deg ifassen n ujeǧid n Accur.
\v 16 War ttesřim ca ɣar Ḥizqiya, maɣar ammu i iqqar ujeǧid n Accur: Ggem ayi array uca ffɣem-dd \add zi tendint\add* ɣari, \add xenni\add* izemmar kuř ijjen zzaywem ad icc zi tzayart nnes u kuř ijjen zeg wartu n tazart nnes u kuř ijjen ad isu aman zeg wanu nnes,
\v 17 ař dd ɣa yaseɣ u ad kenniw awyeɣ ɣar ict n temmurt am temmurt nwem: ɣar ict n temmurt teccur s imendi d binu n jdid, ɣar ict n temmurt teccur s weɣrum u s imarjaɛen n uḍiř.
\v 18 War ttejjim Ḥizqiya ad kenniw iɣarr xmi iqqar: SIDI ad aneɣ ifekk. Ma zemmaren \add xenni\add* irebbiten n řegnus, kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add*, ad fekken tammurt nsen zeg ufus n ujeǧid n Accur?
\v 19 Mani ǧan irebbiten n Ḥamat d Arfad? Mani ǧan irebbiten n Sfarwayim? Ma ssnejmen nitni xenni Samarya zeg ufus inu?
\v 20 Man wen zi marra irebbiten n temmura-ya issenjem tammurt nnes zeg ufus inu ařami ɣa issenjem SIDI Urcalim zeg ufus inu?’”
\v 21 \add Maca\add* nitni sseɣden, war xas dd-arrin s uřa d ijj n wawař, maɣar řumur n ujeǧid tuɣa iqqar: “Kenniw war xas dd-tarrim ca!”
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd Alyaqim, mmis n Ḥilqiya, řemqeddem n tzeddiɣt \add n ujeǧid\add*, ak-d Cibna, amarir, d Yuwax, mmis n Asaf, amarir n umezruy, s warruḍ icarrgen ɣar Ḥizqiya. Nitni ḥajan as \add marra\add* awařen n ukumandar n řɛeskar.
\b
\b
\c 37
\s1 Awař amezwaru x ufekki n Urcalim i dd ɣa yasen
\m 
\v 1 Umi isřa ujeǧid Ḥizqiya aya, icarreg arruḍ nnes, idřa ixef nnes s ict n txancet \add n wecḍan\add* uca yudef ɣar Taddart n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 37:1 \xt [2 Ij. 29]\x*
\v 2 \add Awarni as\add* issekk netta Alyaqim, řemqeddem n tzeddiɣt \add n ujeǧid\add*, d Cabna, amarir, d imɣaren n ikehhanen deg warruḍ n txuncay \add n wecḍan\add* ɣar unabi Icaya, mmis n Amuṣ.
\v 3 Nitni nnan as: “Ammu i iqqar Ḥizqiya: ‘Ass-a d ijj n wass n řeḥṣaret u n weɛqab u n ubehdeř, maɣar iḥenjiren iwḍen-dd ař arzam n uɛeddis \add n yemmatsen\add*, \add maca\add* war din jjehd i twarut. \x ◘ \xo 37:3 \xt 1 Ij. 19:3\x*
\v 4 Ad taɣ SIDI, AREBBI nnec, isřa marra awařen n ukumandar n řɛeskar wenni dd-issekk sidis, ajeǧid n Accur, ḥima ad istehza zi AREBBI iddaren, u \add ad taɣ\add* SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad iɛaqeb awařen nni isřa. Sgeɛɛed \add xenni\add* ict n tẓaǧit di ṭṭweɛ n řbaqi nni i ɣa ittwafen \add ɛad\add*.’”
\m 
\v 5 \add Ammu\add* iwḍen imsexxaren n ujeǧid Ḥizqiya ɣar Icaɛya.
\v 6 Inna asen Icaɛya: “Ammu ittxeṣṣa ad tinim i siditwem: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: War teggʷed ca zeg wawařen i tesřid, i zi i d ayi ceqqfen iḥudriyyen n ujeǧid n Accur.
\v 7 Xzar, Necc ad dayes ggeɣ ijj n buḥbeř u netta ad iseř ijj n řexbar uca \add xenni\add* ad iɛqeb ɣar temmurt nnes u Necc ad t nɣeɣ \add din\add* di temmurt nnes s ssif.’”
\b
\s1 Sanḥarib iɛawed ahuddi nnes i Urcalim
\m 
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb-dd ukumandar n řɛeskar uca yufa ajeǧid n Accur ittmenɣa ak-d \add tendint n\add* Libna, maɣar isřa aqa iqřeɛ iqiḍan nnes \add iffeɣ\add* zi Laxic.
\v 9 \add Umi\add* isřa aqa nnan x Tirhaqa, ajeǧid n Kuc: “Xzar, iffeɣ-dd ḥima akidek immneɣ!”, \add umi\add* isřa \add aya\add*, issekk \add ɛawed\add* ireqqasen ɣar Ḥizqiya, inna:
\v 10 “Ammu i ittxeṣṣa ad tessiwřem ak-d Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ad tinim: ‘War ttejji ad cek iɣwa AREBBI nnec wenni x tᵉttcařed am iqqar: Urcalim war tweṭṭi i ujeǧid n Accur deg ifassen!
\v 11 Xzar, tesřid min ggin ijeǧiden n Accur ak-d marra timmura nneɣni, tinni ḥarrmen nitni i uteḥḥi. Ma ittɣiř ac ad tᵉttwassnejmed?
\v 12 Ma fekken ten irebbiten n řegnus inni yareddǧen řejdud inu? Juzan d Ḥaran d Rṣif d ayt n Ɛadan, inni \add tuɣa izeddɣen\add* di Talassar?
\v 13 Mani iǧa ujeǧid n Ḥamat d ujeǧid n Arfad d ujeǧid n tendint n Sfarwayim uřa d \add ajeǧid n\add* Hanaɛ d Ɛiwwa?’”
\b
\s1 Taẓaǧit n Ḥizqiya
\m 
\v 14 Ḥizqiya iksi tibratin zeg ufus n ireqqasen uca iɣri tent. \add Xenni\add* igeɛɛed ɣar Taddart n SIDI uca ibezzeɛ i-tent Ḥizqiya zzat i wudem n SIDI.
\v 15 Iẓẓuǧ Ḥizqiyai SIDI, inna:
\v 16 “\add A\add* SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil, wenni ittɣiman \add jar\add* ikiruben! Cek, \add wah\add* Cek weḥḥdek d AREBBI n marra tigeldiwin n ddunect. Cek teggid ijenwan d temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 37:16 \fk ikiruben\ft - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*
\v 17 Ewc amezzuɣ nnec, \add a\add* SIDI, arzem tiṭṭawin nnec uca texzared! Seř marra awařen n Sanḥarib wenni dd-issekk netta ḥima ad iɛeyyeb AREBBI iddaren.
\v 18 D tidett, \add a\add* SIDI, ijeǧiden n Accur qḍan timmura nni, xarrben tammurt nsen
\v 19 u nḍaren irebbiten nsen di tmessi, maɣar tuɣa war ǧin d irebbiten, maca d timegga n ufus n yewdan waha, zeg ukeccuḍ d weẓru, uca nitni qḍan ten.
\v 20 Řexxu \add maca\add*, \add a\add* SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, senjem aneɣ zeg ufus nnes, maḥend marra tigeldiwin n ddunect ad ssnen, \add a\add* SIDI, aqa Cek weḥḥdek d AREBBI.”
\b
\s1 Awař wiss tnayen x ufekki n Urcalim i dd ɣa yasen
\m 
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* issekk Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ, \add ijj n ureqqas\add* ɣar Ḥizqiya, inna: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Necc sřiɣ s minzi teẓẓuǧed-dd ɣari x Sanḥarib, ajeǧid n Accur.
\v 22 Wa d awař i xas inna SIDI: ‘Taɛzarct, yeǧis n Ṣihyun, tesseḥqar i cek, nettat testehza zzayek, yeǧis n Urcalim thezz azeǧif awarni ac.
\v 23 Man wen tɛeyybed u di man wen tceqqfed, man wen ɣar tessgeɛɛded tmijja u x man wen i xef tessgeɛɛded s nnfaxet tiṭṭawin nnec? \add Cek tᵉttɣennaned\add* x Umqeddas n Israil!
\v 24 S uqemmum n imsexxaren nnec tedɛid Sidi inu, tennid: S ubarru n ikarruten inu geɛɛdeɣ idurar yuɛřan, iɣezdisen n Lubnan. Necc ad zedmeɣ ticejjura nnes n tengelt yuɛřan uřa d ticejjura nnes icnan qaɛ n imerza u necc ad dd-aseɣ ař taqiccat nnes yuɛřan qaɛ, ɣar wezɣar n umarjeɛ nnes n uḍiř. \f ◼ \fr 37:24 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’. \fk ameḍzi\ft - niɣ ‘amerzi’, ixs ad yini tacejjart n umeḍzi.\f*
\v 25 Necc ɣziɣ \add anuten\add* u swiɣ aman. S třeqqa n iḍaren inu ssiẓɣeɣ marra iɣezran n Miṣra!’”
\m 
\v 26 “Ma war tesřid aqa \add aṭṭas\add* zeg wami ggiɣ man aya uca wciɣ as udem deg wussan n mecḥař uya? Řexxu jjiɣ t ad dd-iffeɣ, aqa cek d wenni i ɣa yarren tineddam ifaryen d řxirbat.
\v 27 Imezdaɣ nsen tuɣa arxun, arẓin, seḍḥan. Nitni tuɣa aten am wefsu deg iyyar, \add am\add* uɣemmuy aziza, \add am\add* uřum x tzeɣwin, \add am\add* \add imendi\add* icemḍen \add s usemmiḍ\add* qbeř i ɣa iffeɣ.
\v 28 \add Maca\add* Necc ssneɣ aɣimi nnec d uffuɣ nnec d twasit nnec d uɣewweɣ nnec xafi.
\v 29 Minzi cek tɣewwɣed xafi u tuffet nnec tiweḍ-dd ɣar imezzuɣen inu, ad ac dd-ssekkeɣ ict n tsennart deg wenzaren u \add ad ggeɣ\add* ict n sřimet jar iyencicen nnec u Necc ad cek arreɣ x webrid i di dd-tusid da.”
\m 
\v 30 “Ta ad ac tiři d řeɛřamet: deg useggʷas-a ad teccem min ɣa iɣemyen s yixef nnes u deg useggʷas wiss tnayen min zzayes ɣa iɣemyen ɛawed, maca deg useggʷas wiss třata ad tzarɛem u ad temjarem, ad teẓẓum tizayarin deg imarjaɛen uca ad teccem řɣiǧet nnes.
\v 31 Maɣar min inejmen, min iqqimen zi taddart n Yahuda, ad iwwet ɛawed iẓewran ɣar swadday u sennej ad yawi řɣiǧet.
\v 32 Maɣar zi Urcalim ad dd-iffeɣ min iqqimen u zeg wedrar n Ṣihyun ad iffeɣ min i ɣa innejmen, asam \add iqeddsen\add* n SIDI n řɛeskarat ad tt igg.”
\m 
\v 33 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI x ujeǧid n Accur: ‘Netta war dd-ittidef ca ɣar tendint-a u war dayes iccit ca uřa d ict n fřitca u war ɣares dd-iqarreb ca s uřa d ict n tseddart \add n uɛeskari\add* u war xas ittbeqqiḍ uřa d ijj n lbaraj i řeḥṣaret.
\v 34 X webrid i x dd-yusa, ad dd-iɛqeb. War ittidif ca ɣar tendint-a, iqqar SIDI.
\v 35 Necc ad sseřqiɣ x tendint-a ḥima ad tt ssnejmeɣ di ṭṭweɛ inu u di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar inu Dawud.’” \x ◘ \xo 37:35 \xt 2 Ij. 20:6\x*
\b
\s1 Afekki n Urcalim
\m 
\v 36 Xenni iffeɣ lmalak n SIDI uca inɣa mya u-xemsa u-tmenyin-ařef \add n yeryazen\add* di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Accur. Umi dd-kkaren nitni tiwecca nnes, xzar, aqa aten marra idsen d řxecbat. \x ◘ \xo 37:36 \xt 2 Ij. 19:35\x*
\m 
\v 37 Uca ifsi Sanḥarib, ajeǧid n Accur, iqiḍan nnes, iruḥ, iɛqeb \add ɣar temmurt nnes\add*. Iqqim izeddeɣ di Ninwa.
\v 38 Umi isjed \add ijj n wass\add* di taddart n arebbi nnes Nisrux, imsar, aqa iḥenjiren nnes Adrammilik d Caraṣar nɣin t s ssif. Nitni arewřen ɣar temmurt n Ararat. Mmis Asarḥaddun idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\b
\c 38
\s1 Řehřac d usgenfi n Ḥizqiya
\m 
\v 1 Deg wussan nni iḥřec Ḥizqiya s ijj n řeḥřac ineqqen. Yusa-dd ɣares unabi Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ, inna as: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ewc řumurat i taddart nnec, maɣar ad temmted, war tᵉttɣimid teddared \add ɛad ktar\add*.’”
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inneqřeb Ḥizqiya s uɣembub nnes ɣar řḥiḍ uca iẓẓuǧ ɣar SIDI,
\v 3 inna: “A, SIDI, ɛqeř aqa necc uyureɣ zzat i wudem nnec s řaman u s yijj n wuř ikemmřen u ggiɣ min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin nnec.” Uca ibda Ḥizqiya ittru s jjhed.
\m 
\v 4 Yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Icaɛya, inna:
\v 5 “Uyur, ini i Ḥizqiya: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n babac Dawud: Necc sřiɣ i tẓaǧit nnec u ẓriɣ imeṭṭawen nnec. Xzar, Necc ad arniɣ xemmesṭac n iseggʷusa i wussan n tudart nnec.
\v 6 Necc ad cek ssnejmeɣ zeg ufus n ujeǧid n Accur, uřa d tandint. Necc ad sseřqiɣ x tendint-a.
\v 7 Aya ad yiři d řeɛřamet n SIDI i cek, aqa SIDI ad igg awař-a nni inna.
\v 8 Xzar, ad ssɛeqbeɣ tiři x treffidin n Aḥaz nni dd-ihwan x treffidin n ddruj n tfuct, ɛecra n treffidin.’” \add Xenni\add* teɛqeb-dd tfuct ɛecra n treffidin x treffidin nni zi dd-tehwa. \x ◘ \xo 38:8 \xt 2 Ij. 20:7-9\x*
\b
\s1 Taẓaǧit s uqadi n Ḥizqiya
\m 
\v 9 Tira n Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, řami tuɣa iḥřec uca iggenfa zi řehřac nnes.
\m 
\v 10 “Necc nniɣ: ‘\add Řexxu\add* deg wezyen n wussan \add n tudart\add* inu ittxeṣṣa ad uyureɣ x tewwura n řaxart. Min iqqimen n iseggʷusa inu ttwakksen zzayi.’
\v 11 Necc nniɣ: ‘War ẓarreɣ ɛad SIDi, SIDi, di temmurt n yinni iddaren, war ttwiřiɣ ɛad iwdan ak-d imezdaɣ n řaxart.’
\v 12 Ticři \add n tudart inu\add* ad tt \add xafi\add* arẓen, ad zzayi tt kksen am \add kksen\add* aqiḍun n umeksaw. Am bu-uzeṭṭa ḍefseɣ tudart inu. Ad ayi iqess zi ddebbuz n txeyyaḍt: Ad teqḍid \add tudart inu\add* jar wass d ǧiřet! \f ◼ \fr 38:12 \fk ameksaw\ft - niɣ ‘aniči’.\f*
\v 13 Rajiɣ s ṣṣbar ař ateffu. Netta ad yarẓ marra iɣsan inu am wayrad: Ad teqḍid \add tudart inu\add* jar uteffu d ǧiřet!
\v 14 Ttjiwjiweɣ am tfařǧest ittennḍen am tᵉṭṭaw, ttgergureɣ am tedbirt. Ssgeɛɛdeɣ tiṭṭawin inu: ‘\add A\add* Sidi inu, necc ttwaḥṣareɣ, iři d aḍman i necc!’ \x ◘ \xo 38:14 \xt Ica. 59:11\x*
\m 
\v 15 Min ɣa iniɣ? Min d ayi inna, aqa igga i-t. Marra iseggʷusa \add n tudart\add* inu ad kkeɣ x tarzugi n řeɛmar inu.
\v 16 ‘\add A\add* Sidi inu, x man aya izemmar \add bnadem\add* ad iddar uca sennej i marra aya aqa dayes tudart n buḥbeř inu, \add maɣar\add* Cek ad ayi teggenfid u Cek ad ayi tarrid ad dewřeɣ ɣar tudart!
\m 
\v 17 Xzar, tarzugi tuɣa tarzeg ayi i řehna. Cek třesqed ɣar řeɛmar inu aṭṭas \add ařami d ayi teḥḍid\add* zeg \add weḥfur n\add* turṣuḍi, maɣar tenḍared marra ddnub inu awarni i weɛrur nnec.
\v 18 Maɣar řaxart war Cek tqada ca, řmewt war Cek issemɣar. Wi ɣa ihwan deg weḥfur, war ttrijin řaman nnec.
\v 19 Wenni iddaren, \add a\add* wenni iddaren, aqa netta ad Cek iqada. Babatsen ad isscen řaman nnec i iḥenjiren \add nnes\add*.’”
\b
\m 
\v 20 “SIDI \add yusa-dd\add* ḥima ad ayi issenjem. Ad nurar s uzenzun x ifiřan inu marra ussan n tudart nneɣ di Taddart n SIDI.”
\b
\m 
\v 21 Aqa inna Icaɛya: “Ejj i-ten ad awyen ijj n weɣrum n tazart uca ad t řetfen x tḥebbuct, \add xenni\add* ad iggenfa.” \x ◘ \xo 38:21 \xt 2 Ij. 20:7\x*
\m 
\v 22 Ḥizqiya aqa inna: “Man i ɣa tiři řeɛřamet aqa necc ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ \add ɛawed\add* ɣar Taddart n SIDI?”
\b
\b
\c 39
\s1 Tarzeft n ireqqasen zi Babil
\m 
\v 1 Di řweqt nni issekk Baradux-Baladan, mmis n Baladan, ajeǧid n Babil, tibratin d ict n tarzeft ɣar Ḥizqiya, maɣar tuɣa isřa aqa Ḥizqiya ihřec uca iggenfa.
\v 2 Ifarḥ zzaysen Ḥizqiya uca isscen asen marra taddart n txubay nnes: nnuqart d wureɣ d řeɛṭur d zzect d řehri n řesnaḥ nnes d marra min ittwafen deg ixxamen nnes n txubay. War iqqim walu di taddart nnes u di marra řeḥkamet nnes nni war tuɣi d asen t isscen.
\m 
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd unabi Icaɛya ɣar ujeǧid Ḥizqiya, inna asen: “Min nnan iryazen nni u manis ɣarek dd-usin?” Ḥizqiya inna: “Nitni usin-dd zeg ict n temmurt tiggʷej, zi Babil.”
\v 4 Netta inna: “Min ẓrin nitni di taddart nnec?” Ḥizqiya inna: “Nitni ẓrin marra min iǧan di taddart inu. War iqqim ca zi min iǧan deg ixxamen n txubay inu, war d asen t ssecneɣ.”
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* inna Icaɛya i Ḥizqiya: “Seř i wawař n SIDI n řɛeskarat:
\v 6 ‘Xzar, ad dd-asen wussan meřmi marra min iǧan di taddart nnec uřa d min yarwen řejdud nnec ař ass-a, ad t awyen ɣar Babil. War ittɣimi walu, iqqar SIDI.
\v 7 Ad awyen uřa zeg iḥenjiren nnec inni dd ɣa iffɣen zzayek, inni dd ɣa tejjed, ḥima ad iřin d imsexxaren imcennɛen di řeqṣar n ujeǧid n Babil.’”
\v 8 Ḥizqiya inna i Icaɛya: “Awař n SIDI i d ayi tennid iṣbeḥ.” Netta inna ɛawed: “Mařa \add xenni\add* deg wussan inu ad \add din\add* yiři řehna d řaman!”
\b
\b
\c 40
\s1 Afewwej i řgens n Arebbi
\m 
\v 1 “Sfewwej, sfewwej řgens inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar AREBBI nwem!
\v 2 Siwřem ɣar wuř n Urcalim uca barrḥem as aqa amenɣi nnes iqḍa, aqa řmuɛṣiyyet nnes teṣřeḥ, aqa teksi s uḍeffus zeg ufus n SIDI i marra ddnub nnes.
\v 3 Tmijja n wenni isɣuyyun di řexřa: ‘Swejdem abrid i SIDI, sarrḥem di řexřa abrid i AREBBI nneɣ!’ \x ◘ \xo 40:3 \xt Mt. 3:3; Mk. 1:3; Lk. 3:4; Yḥ. 1:23\x*
\v 4 Marra tiɣzurin ad ttwassgeɛɛdent, marra idurar d tewririn ad ttwassehwan. Min ifarɣen, ad idweř iseggem uca ijj n useddi n idurar ad idweř d řewḍa iwaṭan.
\v 5 Ad ittwassargeb uɛuǧi n SIDI uca marra ddat ad tẓar aqa aqemmum n SIDI issiweř.” \x ◘ \xo 40:5 \xt Yḥ. 1:14\x*
\m 
\v 6 “Tmijja tenna: ‘Barreḥ!’ U netta inna: ‘Min ɣa barrḥeɣ?’ ‘Marra ddat am arbiɛ d marra tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren am tnewwact deg iyyar. \x ◘ \xo 40:6 \xt Ayub 14:2; Izhd. 90:5, 6; 102:12; 103:15; Yaɛ. 1:10; 1 Bṭ. 1:24\x*
\v 7 Arbiɛ ittaẓeɣ, tanewwact tesřaw xmi xas ittsuḍ Arruḥ n SIDI. D tidett, řgens d arbiɛ.
\v 8 Arbiɛ ittaẓeɣ, tanewwact tesřaw, maca awař n AREBBI nneɣ ittɣima i řebda.’” \x ◘ \xo 40:8 \xt 1 Bṭ. 1:25\x*
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Geɛɛed x ijj n wedrar d ameqqran, \add a\add* Ṣihyun, \add a\add* cem tambeccart n řexbar aṣebḥan, sgeɛɛed tmijja nnem s jjehd, \add a\add* Urcalim, \add a\add* cem tambeccart n řexbar aṣebḥan, sgeɛɛed tmijja nnem, war teggʷed, ini i tneddam n Yahuda: ‘Xzar, AREBBI nkent!’
\v 10 Xzar, ad dd-yas Sidi inu, SIDI, Netta ijhed uca aɣiř nnes ad iḥkem. Xzar, řmunet nnes ɣares uca axeǧeṣ nnes izwar as. \x ◘ \xo 40:10 \xt Ica. 62:11\x*
\v 11 Ad yarwes taḥimart nnes am umeksaw, ad issmun izmaren ɣar uɣiř nnes uca ad ten yarbu deg weḥsin nnes. Ad indeh inni issuṭṭuḍen s řeɛqeř.” \x ◘ \xo 40:11 \xt Ica. 49:10; Ḥiz. 34:23, 24; Mixa 7:14; Yḥ. 10:11\x*
\b
\m 
\v 12 “Man wen iɛbaren aman \add n řebḥar\add* s wuru n ufus nnes u \add man wen\add* iksin řeqyas n ijenwan s řeɛbar n ufus? U \add man wen\add* iṭṭfen ucař n temmurt s ijj n řmud? Man wen iwezznen idurar s ijj n řbasku u tiwririn s řmizan?
\v 13 Man wen ibeqqcen x Arruḥ n SIDI u \add man wen\add* t issɣaren am umcawar nnes? \x ◘ \xo 40:13 \xt Rum. 11:34; 1 Kur. 2:16\x*
\v 14 Wi t iseqsan Netta x ccwar d man wen i d as isscnen řefhamet u wi d as issřemden abrid n řḥeqq uca yarni as tussna? Wi d as issargben abrid iccuren s řefhamet?”
\m 
\v 15 “Xzar, řegnus ttwaḥesben am yict n tuddint zeg ubuqař u am \add cwayt n\add* tneɣda x řmizan. Aqa da, Netta issgeɛɛed tigzirin am tɛejjajt ifsusen.
\v 16 Lubnan war ittqiddi i ukeccuḍ n tmessi uca řmař nnes war ttqiddin i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.
\v 17 Marra řegnus aqa aten am war din ǧin qibač nnes uca iḥesseb i-ten d walu, d řeɛwin. \x ◘ \xo 40:17 \xt Dan. 4:32\x*
\v 18 Wi ak-d i ɣa tessemquddem Arebbi niɣ man arwas i zi t ɣa txeřfem?”\x ◘ \xo 40:18 \xt Ica. 46:5; Řex. 17:29\x*
\m 
\v 19 “Aḥrayfi ittkebba řexyař ineqcen u amziř n wureɣ ittɣeǧef i-t s wureɣ u ifessi as tiseddyin n nnuqart.
\v 20 Wenni iǧan d amezřuḍ i tewhibt n usgeɛɛed ad ixḍar ijj n ukeccuḍ war yarecci. Netta yarezzu ijj n bu-ṣṣenɛet maḥend ad igg řexyař ineqcen nni war ittenhezzin.”
\m 
\v 21 “Ma war \add tt\add* tessinem? Ma war \add tt\add* ttesřim? Ma war \add tt\add* tuɣi ɣarwem ittwassen zeg umezwaru? Ma war tuɣi tḥeṭṭam dsusa n temmurt?
\v 22 Netta d wenni iqqimen x tqurart n tayyut i dd-innḍen i \add marra\add* tammurt, \add tammurt\add* mani imezdaɣ nnes \add ttbanen-dd\add* am yiburexsen, Netta d wenni imeḥḥḍen ijenwan am arwaq, ittbezzeɛ i-ten am uqiḍun i wezdaɣ, \x ◘ \xo 40:22 \xt Ayub 9:8; Izhd. 104:2; Ica. 44:24\x*
\v 23 Netta d wenni ittarran ayt n jjehd d walu, u issexwa řquḍat n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 40:23 \xt Ayub 12:21; Izhd. 107:40\x*
\v 24 Ɛad cwayt waha ttwaẓẓun, ɛad cwayt waha ttwazarɛen, ɛad cwayt waha iwta jjdeɛ \add n tcejjart\add* nsen aẓwar di temmurt, aqa isuḍ Netta xasen ařami uẓɣen uca taḥaryaḍt teksi ten am uřum.”
\m 
\v 25 “Ak-d man wen texsem kenniw ad ayi tessemquddem, man wen i di arewseɣ?, iqqar Umqeddas.
\v 26 Sgeɛɛdem tiṭṭawin nwem u xzarem, man wen iggin man aya? D Netta wenni issuffuɣen řɛeskar nsen marra, wenni d asen ittřaɣan marra s isem nsen s řemɣaret n jjehd \add nnes\add* u s řɛezz \add nnes\add* ijehden, war ibeṭṭeř uřa d ijj!”
\m 
\v 27 “Mayemmi teqqared \add xenni\add*, \add a\add* Yaɛqub, u tessawařed \add ammu\add*, \add a\add* Israil: ‘Abrid inu innuffar x SIDI u tasɣart inu tᵉttekk x AREBBI inu?’
\v 28 Ma war \add tt\add* tessined? Ma war \add tt\add* tesřid aqa AREBBI n řebda, SIDI, wenni dd-ixeřqen ṭṭrufa n temmurt, war ittiḥeř u war yarexxu? War izemmar \add bnadem\add* ad ifhem řeɛqeř nnes. \x ◘ \xo 40:28 \xt Izhd. 147:5\x*
\v 29 Netta ittic jjehd i wenni yuḥřen u wenni war ɣar iǧi jjehd yarenni as jjehd s waṭṭas.
\v 30 Iḥenjiren ttaḥřen u arexxun, ibřiɣen ttenqraḍen uca weṭṭan,
\v 31 \add maca\add* inni ittrajan SIDI, ttaymen jjehd n jdid. Nitni ttᵉṭṭfen afriwen am ugider, ttazzřen, \add maca\add* war ttiḥřen, gguren \add maca\add* war arexxun.”
\b
\b
\c 41
\s1 Amqeddas n Israyil d Amefdi n umsexxar nnes Israyil
\m 
\v 1 “Seɣdem-dd zzati, \add a\add* tigzirin x tma n řebḥar, uca jjem ccuɛub ad ṭṭfen jjehd n jdid, jjem ten ad dd-adsen, xenni ad ssiwřen, jjem aneɣ ad nqarreb ɣar řeḥkam marra nmun.
\v 2 Man wen i dd-issfaqen zi manis d tneqqar tfuct ijjen wenni akides temsagar tsegda ɣar iḍaren nnes? \add Man wen\add* isellmen řegnus deg ufus nnes uca igga i-t ad yareyyes x ijeǧiden? \add Man wen\add* yarrin \add řegnus\add* i ssif nnes am tɛejjajt, i řqews nnes am uřum nni di ittsuḍ usemmiḍ?
\v 3 Netta iḍfar i-ten, ikemmeř ɣar zzat di řehna x webrid war \add t\add* iḥidi ɛemmarṣ s iḍaren nnes.
\v 4 Man wen isseqfeř uca igga aya? Netta, wenni zeg umezwaru ibarrḥen i jjiřat: ‘Necc, SIDI, d Amezwaru u ɣar ineggura \bd Necc Necc\bd*.’ \x ◘ \xo 41:4 \xt Ica. 43:10; 44:6; 48:12; Asa. 1:17; 22:13\x*
\v 5 Tigzirin ẓrint \add t\add*, ggʷedent, ineggura n temmurt arjijen, nitni udsen-dd, iwḍen-dd.
\v 6 Ijjen iwca afus i umeddukkeř nnes, inna i umas: ‘Iři d aryaz!’”
\b
\m 
\v 7 “Aṣnayɛi igga uř deg wemziř n wureɣ nni \add t\add* isserɣen s wefḍis, wenni iwettin x ẓẓebra, am iqqar x mammec ssřesqen iziynan: ‘D lemliḥ!’. \add Xenni\add* issemten \add wemziř\add* i řexyař s imesmar, ařami war ittenhezzi.”
\b
\m 
\v 8 “\add Maca\add* cek, \add a\add* Israil, amsexxar inu, \add a\add* Yaɛqub nni ixḍareɣ, zzariɛet n Ibrahim, ameddukkeř inu iɛizzen, \x ◘ \xo 41:8 \xt Aɛwd. 7:6; 10:15; 14:2; 2 Im. 20:7; Izhd. 135:4; Ica. 43:1; 44:1; Yaɛ. 2:23\x*
\v 9 ṭṭfeɣ cek zeg ineggura n temmurt uca řaɣiɣ-dd xak zi ṭṭrufa nnes qaɛ, nniɣ ac: ‘Cek d amsexxar inu, ixḍareɣ cek, war cek nḍareɣ.’
\v 10 War tteggʷed ca, maɣar Necc ǧiɣ akidek, war sḥissif, maɣar Necc d AREBBI nnec. Necc ad cek ssjehdeɣ, ad ac wceɣ afus, \add wah,\add* Necc ad dayek menɛeɣ s ufusi iccur s tsegda inu.”
\b
\m 
\v 11 “Xzar, nitni ad seḍḥan, ad dewřen i řefḍiḥet, marra inni xak issḥemman. Iryazen nni akidek ittemcubbucen, ad dewřen d walu, ad ttwahellken. \x ◘ \xo 41:11 \xt Uf. 23:22; Ica. 60:12; Zak. 12:3\x*
\v 12 Cek ad xasen tarzud, \add maca\add* war ten tᵉttifed. Iryazen nni kidek ittemcubbucen ad dewřen d walu d řbaṭeř, \add wah,\add* iryazen nni ittmenɣan akidek.
\v 13 Maɣar Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni iṭṭfen afus afusi nnec d wenni d ac iqqaren: ‘War tteggʷed ca, Necc ad ac wceɣ afus!
\v 14 War teggʷed ca, \add a cek\add* akeccaw Yaɛqub, \add a\add* yeryazen n Israil! Necc ad ac wceɣ afus, Amefdi nnec d Amqeddas n Israil!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.
\v 15 Xzar, Necc ggiɣ cem d tařwiḥt itteḥřuǧuḍen i usarwet d tamaynut, s teɣmas iqeḍɛen ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen. Idurar ad ten tssarwted u ad ten teddzed u tiwririn ad tent tegged d řum. \x ◘ \xo 41:15 \xt Ica. 17:13; 29:5\x*
\v 16 Cek ad ten tezzuzared, ad ten yawi usemmiḍ, ad ten tareyyec tḥaryaḍt. Cek maca ad tesřiwřewed x SIDI, ad tcennɛed ixef nnec deg Umqeddas n Israil.”
\b
\m 
\v 17 “Inni ittwaḥṣaren d imezřaḍ arezzun x waman, \add maca\add* walu da. Iřes nsen yuẓeɣ s ufadi. Necc, SIDI, ad asen sřeɣ, Necc, AREBBI n Israil, war daysen semmḥeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 41:17 \xt Mt. 5:6\x*
\v 18 X tewririn tiqeccura ad jjeɣ iɣezran ad dduqqzen uřa d řɛunṣarat di řwesṭ n řewḍat. Necc ad arreɣ řexřa d ayeřmam n waman uřa d tammurt yuẓɣen d tinedwin. \x ◘ \xo 41:18 \xt Izhd. 107:35; Ica. 35:7; 44:3\x*
\v 19 Di řexřa ad ẓẓuɣ tacejjart n tengelt d tcejjart n ukasiya d tcejjart n tariḥant d uzemmur, di tnezruft ad ggeɣ tacejjart n umerzi d tcejjart n dulb d tayda ak-d wayawya, \f ◼ \fr 41:19 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’). \fk amerzi\ft - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*
\v 20 ḥima ad ẓaren, ad neɛmen, ad argben, ad fehmen jmiɛ, aqa afus n SIDI igga aya, aqa Amqeddas n Israil ixřeq i-tt-i-dd.”
\b
\m 
\v 21 “Qeddmem ddeɛwet nwem \add zzati\add*, iqqar SIDI, awyem-dd burhanat nwem ijehden qaɛ, iqqar Ujeǧid n Yaɛqub.
\v 22 Ejj i-ten ad awyen u ad aneɣ barrḥen min ɣa imsaren. Sargbem aneɣ x tmesřayin timezwura qaɛ, mammec ǧant, ḥima ad \add tent\add* neksi ɣar wuř uca ad nessen aneggar nsent, niɣ ejj aneɣ ad nseř x tmesřayin i dd ɣa yasen \add ɛad\add*.
\v 23 Barrḥem timesřayin i ɣa yiřin daweḥda ɛad, \add maḥend\add* ad nessen aqa kenniw d irebbiten. Ggem ca d řxar niɣ d řɣar, \add ḥima\add* ad nxezzar deg wayawya s řxezrat ibeqqcen, ad \add tt\add* nẓar \add jmiɛ\add*.
\v 24 Xzar, kenniw qell x walu u min tᵉtteggem war dayes bu nnfaɛ, wenni kenniw ixḍaren aqa-t d nnɛi.”
\b
\m 
\v 25 “Necc ad dd-ssekkareɣ \add ijjen\add* zi ccamal u netta ad dd-iffeɣ zi manis dd-tneqqar tfuct, ad iřaɣa x Isem inu. Netta ad dd-yas am bu-třaxt nni iɛeffsen x ubeǧaɛ, ad iɛfes x ayt n jjehd am x tarrist.”
\b
\m 
\v 26 “Man wen \add i-tt\add* ibarrḥen zeg umezwaru qaɛ, \add ḥima\add* ad \add tt\add* nessen, niɣ \add xenni\add* man wen \add i-tt\add* ibarrḥen qbeř, ḥima nzemmar ad nini: ‘Aqa netta dayes řaman!’ Maca war din wi \add tt\add* ibarrḥen, \add war din\add* wi d aneɣ ittarran ad nseř ca, uřa d ijj war isři awem tneṭqem s ca.
\v 27 \add Am\add* Umezwaru \add nniɣ Necc\add* i Ṣihyun: ‘Aqa-ten da!’, u i Urcalim: ‘Necc ad awyeɣ ijj n ureqqas s řexbar aṣebḥan.’
\v 28 Necc xzareɣ, \add maca\add* war din tuɣi uřa d ijj! War \add din\add* tuɣi uřa d ijj zzaysen wenni izemmaren ad iwc ccwar, \add ařami\add* zemmareɣ ad sseqsiɣ u nitni ad xafi dd-arren.
\v 29 Xzar, nitni marra di řbaṭeř, řexdayem nsen war daysen nnfaɛ, řexyařat ifesyen nsen d řeɛwin \add waha\add* u xwant.”
\b
\b
\c 42
\s1 Amsexxar n SIDI d amsexxar nnes adarɣař, Israil
\m 
\v 1 “Xzar, Amsexxar inu Wenni ttɛawaneɣ, d Wenni farzeɣ, d Wenni dd-yusin x řxaḍar inu. Necc ssarseɣ xas Arruḥ inu. Netta ad issuffeɣ řeḥkam ɣar řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 42:1 \xt Ica. 11:2; Mt. 3:17; 17:5; Yḥ. 3:34; Afa. 1:6\x*
\v 2 War isɣuyyu u war issgiɛɛid tmijja nnes u war ittarri tmijja nnes ad as sřen di barra.
\v 3 Aɣanim inḍefsen war t ittareẓẓi ca u taftič n tiffest ittduxxunen war t issexsiy ca, \add wah,\add* s tidett ad issuffeɣ tasegda.
\v 4 Netta war ittiḥeř u war ittwareẓẓi ař dd-issbedd tasegda x temmurt u ɣar Ccariɛa nnes ad rajant tigzirin.”
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Ammu i iqqar Arebbi, SIDI, wenni iggin u ibezzɛen ijenwan, wenni iggin tammurt d min xas iɣemmyen, wenni itticen twarrit n nnefs i řgens i dayes izeddɣen, u buḥbeř i yinni igguren x \add temmurt\add*:
\v 6 ‘Necc, SIDI, řaɣiɣ ac di tsegda uca ad Cek menɛeɣ zeg ufus, ad Cek ḥḍiɣ uca ad Cek arreɣ d Řɛahd i řgens d tfawt i řegnus, \x ◘ \xo 42:6 \xt Yḥ. 8:12\x*
\v 7 ḥima ad tarzmed tiṭṭawin idaɣařen, ad tessuffɣed imeḥbas zi řeḥbes u yinni iqqimen di taǧest zi taddart n tɛessast.
\v 8 Necc d SIDI, wa d Isem inu, uca war tticeɣ ccan inu i wenneɣni u asemɣar inu war \add t tticeɣ\add* i řexyařat ineqcen. \x ◘ \xo 42:8 \xt Ica. 48:11\x*
\v 9 Xzar, timesřayin timezwura iwḍent uca timesřayin n jdid ad tent barrḥeɣ. Qbeř mma ad ffɣent, ad awem tent ssecneɣ.’”
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Ɣennjem izři n jdid i SIDI, asemɣar nnes zeg ineggura n temmurt, \add kenniw\add* inni ineddhen řebḥar, d marra min dayes: \add kennint a\add* tigzirin d imezdaɣ nsent. \x ◘ \xo 42:10 \xt Izhd. 33:3\x*
\v 11 Ad issgeɛɛed řexřa \add tmijja nnes\add* uca uřa d tneddam nnes, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ředcur nni di izeddeɣ Qidar. Ejj inni izeddɣen di řejruf ad sřiwřewen, \add ejj i-ten\add* ad sɣuyen s řefraḥet x tqiccitin n idurar,
\v 12 ejj i-ten ad ssɛuǧen SIDI, ad barrḥen ccan nnes x \add marra\add* tigzirin.
\v 13 SIDI ad dd-iffeɣ am bu-teɣruḍṭ, ad issekkar meẓri deg umenɣi am weryaz imeḥḍen, Netta ad isřiwřew, ad isɣuy i umenɣi, ad iḥṣar qaɛ řɛedyan nnes.”
\b
\m 
\v 14 “Necc tuɣa sseɣdeɣ zeg wecḥař uya, tuɣa sqareɣ, ttebbateɣ ixef inu. Ad sɣuyeɣ am yicten ittarun, ad \add ten\add* areddǧeɣ u ad \add ten\add* ṣarḍeɣ \add jmiɛ\add*.
\v 15 Idurar d tewririn ad ten arreɣ d amessuci u ad jjeɣ aɣemmuy aziza nsen marra ad yaẓeɣ, iɣezran ad ten ggeɣ d tigzirin, uca ad ssiẓɣeɣ iyeřmamen.
\v 16 Idarɣařen ad ten nedheɣ x ijj n webrid war t ssinen, ad ten jjeɣ ad uyuren x tbridin war tent argben. Ṭṭram zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen ad t ggeɣ d tfawt, min ifarɣen, ad t seggdeɣ. Tina d timesřayin i ɣa ggeɣ di ṭṭweɛ nsen u war daysen semḥeɣ.
\v 17 Inni ittcařan x řexyařat ineqcen, inni iqqaren i řexyařat ifesyen: ‘Kenniw d irebbiten nneɣ!’, aqa nitni ad dewřen ɣar ḍeffar, ad seḍḥan aṭṭas.” \x ◘ \xo 42:17 \xt Izhd. 97:7; Ica. 1:29; 44:11; 45:16\x*
\b
\m 
\v 18 “Sřem, \add kenniw\add* iduhcar! Idarɣařen, xzarem u wařam.
\v 19 Man wen iǧan d adarɣař am umsexxar inu, d adehcur am ureqqas inu? Man wen iǧan d adarɣař am umtiqqi u d adarɣař am umsexxar n SIDI?
\v 20 Aṭṭas i tᵉttwařid, \add maca\add* war tucid walu, \add iwa\add* netta yarzem imezzuɣen, \add maca\add* war ittesři ca. \x ◘ \xo 42:20 \xt Rum. 2:2-11\x*
\v 21 Tuɣa yarḍa SIDI di ṭṭweɛ n tsegda nnes \add maḥend\add* ad issemɣar d issɛuǧa Ccariɛa.
\v 22 \add Maca řexxu\add* nitni d ijj n řgens acaren tt, keccḍen tt. Marra ttwacedden deg ifran, ttwaqqnen di řeḥbes. Nitni dewřen d taymart, \add am\add* war din iǧi umsenjem, dewřen nitni i tkeccaḍt, \add maca\add* uřa d ijj iqqar: ‘Arr i-t-i-dd!’
\v 23 Man wen zzaywem ad iwc amezzuɣ i man aya? Man wen i ɣa iḥekkaren, \add man wen\add* i ɣa iseř di ṭṭweɛ n min ɣa yiřin awarni man aya?
\v 24 Man wen issiwḍen Yaɛqub am teymart d Israil i ixewwanen? Ma war tt iggi SIDI, wenni di nexḍa? \add Maɣar\add* nitni war xsen ad uyuren x ibriden nnes, war xsen ad sřen ɣar Ccariɛa nnes.
\v 25 S uyenni izeǧeɛ xas asɛar n weɣḍab nnes uřa d lɛunf n garra. Iqewwar as s iceɛɛařen, \add maca\add* netta war d as iḥekkar, iqqed as timessi, \add maca\add* netta war tt ikessi ɣar wuř nnes.”
\b
\b
\c 43
\s1 SIDI d ayenni n Umsenjem d Umefdi n Israyil
\m 
\v 1 “\add Maca\add* řexxu, ammu i iqqar SIDI, wenni cek dd-ixeřqen, \add a\add* Yaɛqub, d wenni d Amkewwan nnec, \add a\add* Israil, war tteggʷed ca, maɣar Necc fekkeɣ cek, řaɣiɣ ac s yisem nnec, cek inu.
\v 2 Mařa tcuqed deg waman, ad iřiɣ akidek, mařa deg iɣezran, war cek ttiwyen. Mařa teẓwid x tmessi, war tcemmḍed, uca aceɛɛař war cek issruɣa. \x ◘ \xo 43:2 \xt Izhd. 66:12\x*
\v 3 Maɣar Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nnec, Amqeddas n Israil, Amsenjem nnec. Necc wciɣ Miṣra d ddeyyet i cek, Kuc d Seba deg wemcan nnec.
\v 4 Minzi tsekkwid aṭṭas di tiṭṭawin inu, aqa tᵉttwassɛuǧed u Necc ttexseɣ cek. Wciɣ iwdan deg wemcan nnec d ccuɛub deg wemcan n řeɛmar nnec.
\v 5 War tteggʷed ca, maɣar Necc akidek. Ad awyeɣ iḥenjiren nnec zi mani dd-tneqqar tfuct, ad cek ssmuneɣ zi mani dd-tɣeǧi tfuct. \x ◘ \xo 43:5 \xt Ica. 44:2; Irm. 30:10; 46:27\x*
\v 6 Necc ad iniɣ i ccamal: ‘Ewc!’ u i ljanub: ‘War ttᵉṭṭef!’, arekkʷeḥ iḥenjiren inu zi řaggʷaj, yessi zi tma n temmurt,
\v 7 kuř ijjen wenni umi ttřaɣan s Yisem inu, wenni dd-xeřqeɣ i ccan inu, wenni kewwneɣ d wenni ggiɣ ɛawed.”
\b
\m 
\v 8 “Ejj ad iffeɣ řgens adarɣař, waxxa \add ɣarsen\add* tiṭṭawin, uřa d iduhcaren, waxxa ɣarsen imezzuɣen.
\v 9 Ejj ad ttwassmunen marra řegnus uca ejj ccuɛub ad nnjarwen! Man wen zzaysen izemmar ad ibarreḥ ta, d man wen izemmar ad aneɣ yini min tuɣa iǧan zic? Ejj i-ten ad awyen řechud nsen maḥend ad ttwaseggden, uca \add ejj řechud\add* ad sřen, ad inin: ‘D tidett!’
\v 10 Kenniw d řechud inu uřa d amsexxar inu nni farzeɣ, ḥima ad tessnem, ad dayi tamnem, ad tfehmem aqa \bd Necc Necc\bd*. Qbeř Necc war ittwagg uřa d ijj n Arebbi uca awarni ayi war ittiři uřa d ijjen!, iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 43:10 \xt Ica. 41:4; 44:8; 45:21; Ḥuc. 13:4\x*
\v 11 Necc, Necc d SIDI, u war iǧi Umsenjem mɣir Necc.
\v 12 Necc barrḥeɣ u ssnejmeɣ u Necc iwyeɣ awem \add t-i-dd\add* ɣar umejjun. Uřa d ijj n \add arebbi\add* řbarrani war tuɣi jar awem. Kenniw d řechud aqa Necc d Arebbi, ammu i iqqar SIDI.
\v 13 Uřa zeg wass-a, aqa \bd Necc Necc\bd* uca uřa d ijj war izemmar ad issfekk zeg ufus inu! \add Mařa\add* Necc xedmeɣ, man wen izemmaren ad t inneqřeb?” \x ◘ \xo 43:13 \xt Ica. 14:27\x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, Amefdi nwem, Amqeddas n Israil: ‘Di ṭṭweɛ nwem ssekkeɣ \add ijjen\add* ɣar Babil uca ad ten arreɣ ad arewřen, uca ad hwan marra Ikaldaniyyen deg iɣurraba nni zi tuɣa farrḥen \add ammu qbeř\add*.
\v 15 Necc d SIDI, Amqeddas nwem, wenni dd-ixeřqen Israil, Ajeǧid nwem.’”
\m 
\v 16 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI nni iggin abrid di řebḥar d tebridt deg waman ijehden,
\v 17 wenni ijjin ikarruten d yeysan, řɛeskar d jjehd ad ffɣen - aqa da, zzřen munen, war ttnekkaren ɛemmarṣ, xesyen, qḍan am teftič n tiffest! -
\v 18 \add ammu i iqqar SIDI\add*: ‘War ttɛeqiřem \add ɛad\add* x min tuɣa iǧan zic, war ttidarem \add ɛad\add* min iɛdun.
\v 19 Xzar, ad ggeɣ min iǧan n jdid, řexxu ad dd-iffeɣ. Ma war d as tḥekkarem ca? Wah, Necc ad ssarseɣ abrid di řexřa, iɣzaren di tnezruft. \x ◘ \xo 43:19 \xt Asa. 21:5\x*
\v 20 Řmař n řexřa ad ayi ssɛuǧan, uccanen n řexřa d yessis n nnɛamet, maɣar Necc ad ggeɣ aman ad azzřen di řexřa uřa d iɣezran di tnezruft, ḥima ad ssesweɣ řgens inu, inni farzeɣ.
\v 21 Řgens-a ggiɣ t i Necc, nitni ad barrḥen ccan inu.’” \x ◘ \xo 43:21 \xt Lk. 1:74, 75\x*
\b
\m 
\v 22 “\add Maca\add* cek war d ayi dd-třaɣid, \add a\add* Yaɛqub, war tessiḥřed ixef nnec akidi, \add a\add* Israil!
\v 23 Cek war d ayi dd-tiwyed ijjen zeg wuǧi n tɣarṣa nnec n wecmaḍ, uca s tɣarṣi nnec war d ayi tcennɛed. Ɛemmarṣ war cek ḥṣareɣ ɣar tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* u war cek ssiḥřeɣ ɛemmarṣ s jjawi.
\v 24 Cek war d ayi tesɣid aɣanim n uḥemmum ittfuḥen s tmenyat n nnuqart uca war d ayi tessjiwned s tadunt n tɣarṣa nnec, maca s ddnub nnec tarnid ayi-dd řxedmet, s řmuɛṣiyyat nnec tessiḥřed ayi.”
\b
\m 
\v 25 “Necc, d Necc, wenni i ɣa imesḥen iɛeddiyen nnec di ṭṭweɛ inu, Necc war ttidareɣ ɛad ddnub nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 43:25 \xt Ḥiz. 36:22-38\x*
\b
\m 
\v 26 “Arr \add i-ten\add* ɣar řbař inu, ejj aneɣ ad nemcarreɛ, wwet x yixef nnec maḥend ad dd-tawyed tasɣart nnec. \x ◘ \xo 43:26 \xt Ica. 1:18\x*
\v 27 Babac amezwaru ixḍa u uřa d imseṣřaḥen nnec ɛdun xafi. \f ◼ \fr 43:27 \fk imseṣřaḥen\ft - ixs ad yini ‘ikehhanen d inabiyyen nnec’ inni tuɣa ibedden jar AREBBI d řgens nnes.\f*
\v 28 \add Xenni\add* ssɛiǧteɣ imeqqranen n Zzawect Iqeddsen, u arriɣ Yaɛqub maḥend ad ittwaḥarrem \add i uteḥḥi\add* uca jjiɣ Israil maḥend ad t ɛeyyben.”
\b
\b
\c 44
\s1 Asfarreɣ n Arruḥ n SIDI - Kurac d ameksaw
\m 
\v 1 “Řexxu \add maca\add*, seř, \add a\add* amsexxar inu Yaɛqub, Israil nni farzeɣ! \x ◘ \xo 44:1 \xt Ica. 41:8; 43:5; Irm. 30:10; 46:27\x*
\v 2 Ammu i iqqar SIDI, Wenni cek iggin, Wenni cek iggin zeg uɛeddis \add n yemmac\add*, Wenni d ac iwcin afus: ‘War tteggʷed ca, \add a\add* Yaɛqub, amsexxar inu, Yacurun nni farzeɣ!
\v 3 Maɣar Necc ad seyyḥeɣ aman x min iffuden d tseǧyawin x min yuẓɣen. Necc ad zeǧɛeɣ Arruḥ inu x zzariɛet nnec uřa d lbaraka inu x tarwa nnec. \x ◘ \xo 44:3 \xt Ica. 35:7; Yuw. 3:1; Yḥ. 7:38; Řex. 2:18\x*
\v 4 Nitni ad ɣemyen jar arbiɛ, am yiṣefṣafen ɣar tɣezratin n waman.
\v 5 Ijjen ad yini: ‘\add Necc\add* n SIDI!’ uca ijjen nneɣni ad iřaɣa ixef nnes s yisem n Yaɛqub, u \add ɛawed\add* ijjen nneɣni ad yari s ufus nnes: ‘\add Necc\add* n SIDI!’ uca ad ikenna ixef nnes s yisem \add icennɛen\add* ‘Israil’.’”
\b
\m 
\v 6 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, Ajeǧid n Israil, d Amefdi nnes, SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Necc d Amezwaru, Necc d Aneggaru, nhřa Necc war iǧi uřa d ijj n AREBBI nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 44:6 \xt Ica. 41:4; 48:12; Asa. 1:8, 17; 22:13\x*
\v 7 Man wen izemmaren ad ibarreḥ am Necc? Ejj i-t ad \add t\add* yini u ad ayi t isscen zeg wass nni di ẓẓuɣ řgens n wecḥař uya. Ejj i-ten ad asen ɛawden timesřayin n tiwecca, min i dd ɣa yasen.
\v 8 War ttnexřiɛem u war tteggʷdem. Ma war d awem t-i-dd-ssiwḍeɣ zeg \add wakud n\add* zic ɣar imezzuɣen nwem u ma war ḥajiɣ t? Kenniw d řechud inu: Ma aqa din ijj n Arebbi nhřa Necc? War \add din\add* iǧi uřa d ict n teṣḍart nneɣni, Necc war ssineɣ uřa d ijjen.’” \x ◘ \xo 44:8 \xt Aɛwd. 4:35,39; 32:39; 1 Ṣm. 2:2; Ica. 45:21\x*
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Inni itteggen řexyařat ineqcen ixwan, u \add řexyařat\add* nni ttexsen nitni war neffɛent deg walu. Nitni \add s yixef nsen\add* d řechud nsent aqa war ttwiřint u war ssinent walu, ařami ɣa dewřen ttseḍḥan nitni.
\v 10 Man wen itteggen ijj n arebbi u \add man wen\add* ittkebban řexyař n l’aṣnam am war ɣares bu tizi zzayes?
\v 11 Xzar, marra icricen nsen ad dewřen ttseḍḥan, maɣar ayt n bu-ṣṣenɛet \add i ixeddmen s ukeccuḍ d weẓru\add* d iwdan waha. Ejj i-ten ad munen, ad kkaren, ad nnxeřɛen, nitni ad dewřen ttseḍḥan jmiɛ. \x ◘ \xo 44:11 \xt Izhd. 97:7; Ica. 1:29; 42:17; 45:16\x*
\m 
\v 12 Amziř n wuzzař ɣares imeydi n wemziř, ixeddem ɣar řefḥem itteḥduduqen, ittqarres řexyař s ifḍisen \add nnes\add*. Ixeddem i-t s uɣiř ijehden. Netta iǧuẓ ařami war ɣares iqqim bu jjhed ɛad. War isess aman ař ɣa yaḥeř aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 44:12 \xt Irm. 10:3\x*
\v 13 Anejjar iɛebbar tafrewt s ufiřu nnes n řeɛbar, yareccem \add řexyař ineqcen\add* s ukerraj, u inejjar i-t s řmus uca yareccem i-t s ddewara u igga i-t d ijj n řexyař n bnadem maḥend ad ittwassars deg ict n taddart.
\v 14 Izeddem bnadem ticejjura n tengelt i yixef nnes, ikessi ict n \add tcejjart n\add* ssidri niɣ n řbeǧuḍ, yarezzu i yixef nnes jar tcejjura n wezɣar. Itteẓẓu ict n tayda uca tmeqqar s wenẓar. \f ◼ \fr 44:14 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\v 15 Ad tiři \add tcejjart\add* d řefḥem i bnadem. Ikessi zzayes uca iẓɣařa ixef nnes ɣares. Ɛawed issraqqa timessi, issnenna zzayes aɣrum. Zi tcejjart ittegg \add bnadem\add* ɛawed ijj n arebbi uca ittbendaq as, ittegg zzayes řexyař ineqcen uca isejjad as.
\v 16 Ijj n wezyen \add n ukeccuḍ\add* zzayes issecmaḍ i-t s tmessi, ak-d wezyen iqqimen ittett aysum. Icennef aysum uca ittyawan. Iẓɣařa ixef nnes, iqqar: ‘Ah, mammec ḥemmiɣ, necc ttaciɣ ak-d tmessi!’
\v 17 Zi min iqqimen \add n ukeccuḍ\add* ittegg ijj n arebbi, ijj n řexyař ineqcen. Isejjad as, ittbendaq zzates, ittẓaǧa ɣares, iqqar: ‘Senjem ayi, minzi cek d arebbi inu!’”
\b
\m 
\v 18 “War ssinen, war ttḥikin, maɣar tiṭṭawin nsen mesḥent umi war ttwiřin walu, uca uřawen nsen war tteftinen.
\v 19 Uřa d ijj ittegg i-tt ɣar wuř nnes uca war din bu tussna uřa d řefhamet ḥima ad inin: ‘Ijj n wezyen zzayes sscemḍeɣ t di tmessi. Ssnenneɣ aɣrum x řefḥem nnes \add itteḥduduqen\add* u cenfeɣ aysum u cciɣ t. Zi min iqqimen \add n ukeccuḍ\add* ma ad zzayes ggeɣ jjɛifect \add n ṣṣanam\add*, ma ad sejdeɣ zzat i ukeccuḍ n tcejjart?’ \f ◼ \fr 44:19 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*
\v 20 Netta issecca ixef nnes s iɣɣeḍ, uř nnes ittwaɣarren iɣekkwa i-t. War izemmar ad issenjem řeɛmar nnes, ad yini: ‘Ma \add xenni\add* war \add din\add* iǧi řɣecc deg ufus afusi inu?’”
\b
\m 
\v 21 “Ɛqeř x man aya, \add a\add* Yaɛqub, \add a cek\add* Israil! Maɣar aqa cek d amsexxar inu, Necc kewwneɣ cek, cek d amsexxar inu, \add a\add* Israil, war cek ttᵉttuɣ ca.
\v 22 Necc messḥeɣ iɛeddiyen nnec am tayyut uřa d ddnub nnec am useynu. Dweř-dd ɣari, maɣar Necc fekkeɣ cek.”
\b
\m 
\v 23 “Ɣennjem s řefraḥet, \add a\add* ijenwan, maɣar SIDI igga i-t. Sřiwřewet, \add a\add* řaǧaɣ n temmurt, ksim deg iɣuyyan s řefraḥet, \add a\add* idurar, sřiwřiwem, \add a cek\add*, azɣar d kuř tacejjart i dayes \add iǧan\add*! Maɣar SIDI ifekk i Yaɛqub, issɛuǧa Ixef nnes di Israil.” \f ◼ \fr 44:23 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 24 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, Amefdi nnec, Wenni cek iggin zeg uɛeddis \add n yemmac\add*: ‘Necc d SIDI wenni iggin marra, wenni ittbezzaɛen ajenna, Necc waha, Necc d wenni issarsen tammurt. Man wen \add tuɣa xenni\add* akidi? \x ◘ \xo 44:24 \xt Ayub 9:8; Izhd. 104:2; Ica. 40:22; 42:5; 45:12\x*
\v 25 \add Necc\add* d wenni ibeṭṭřen řeɛřamat n ayt n bu-ixarriqen uca ssbuhřiɣ igezzanen, d wenni isswexxaren imiɣisen u yarra tussna nsen d taɣyuři,
\v 26 wenni issmetnen awař n umsexxar nnes u isseqfeř ccwar n ireqqasen nnes, wenni iqqaren i Urcalim: ‘Ad dayem iřin imezdaɣ ɛad!’ uca i \add kuř ict zi\add* tneddam n Yahuda: ‘Cem ad tᵉttwassbedded ɛawed!’ uca ‘Necc ad ssbeddeɣ řxirbat nnes ɛawed!’,
\v 27 wenni iqqaren i \add waman\add* yuǧɣen: ‘Aẓɣem, Necc ad ssiẓɣeɣ iɣezran nwem!’,
\v 28 wenni iqqaren i Kurac: ‘\add Netta d\add* ameksaw inu, netta ad isseqfeř řxaḍar inu, umi ɣa inin i Urcalim: ‘Ad cem ɛedřen!’, u i Zzawect Tameqqrant: ‘Ad am ggen dsas!’”
\b
\b
\c 45
\s1 Kurac, amedhun n SIDI, ad ibarreḥ s ufekki
\m 
\v 1 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI i umedhun nnes, i Kurac, wenni zi ṭṭfeɣ afus nnes afusi maḥend ad as ssaḍareɣ řegnus zzat i wudem nnes: ‘Ad ssarxuɣ tiḥezzamin s řesnaḥ x tejɛinnatin n ijeǧiden, ḥima ad as arzmeɣ tiwwura, u řebniyyat n tewwura war ttwabelliɛent ca.
\v 2 Necc ad ac izwareɣ, ad waṭiɣ min war ihewnen, ad arẓeɣ tiwwura n nnḥas u ad wtiɣ zzekrunat n wuzzař d iwetwiten.
\v 3 Ad ac wceɣ řeknuz n taǧest, agřa innuffaren, ḥima ad tessned aqa Necc, SIDI, d wenni cek iřaɣan s yisem nnec, AREBBI n Israil.
\v 4 Di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar inu Yaɛqub, Israil wenni farzeɣ, řaɣiɣ ac s yisem nnec, wciɣ ac isem \add n ccan\add*, \add waxxa\add* war d ayi tessined ca.
\v 5 Necc d SIDI, war din iǧi wenneɣni, nhřa Necc war iǧi AREBBI. Ad ac ḥezzmeɣ abyas, waxxa war d ayi tessined ca, \x ◘ \xo 45:5 \xt Aɛwd. 4:35,39; 32:39; Ica. 44:8\x*
\v 6 maḥend ad ssnen zi mani dd-tneqqar tfuct ař mani tɣeǧi, aqa nhřa Necc war \add din\add* iǧi uřa d ict n tmesřact, Necc d SIDI, war din iǧi nneɣni.
\v 7 Necc tteggeɣ tafawt u xeǧqeɣ-dd taǧest, tteggeɣ řehna u xeǧqeɣ-dd řɣar, Necc, SIDI, d wenni itteggen marra aya.’”
\b
\m 
\v 8 “Udumem, \add a kenniw\add* ijenwan, zi sennej, jjem iseynuten ad dd-farrɣen tasegda, ad tennurzem temmurt, uca \add jjem ten\add* ad awyen asenjem i řɣiǧet u ejj tasegda ad teɣmi jmiɛ akides. Necc, SIDI, xeřqeɣ t.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “\bd Uct\bd* x wenni ittemcubbucen ak-d Wenni t iggin, ijj n uqedduḥ jar iqedduḥen nneɣni? Ma tzemmar třaxt ad tini i wenni t iggin: ‘Min teggid?’ Niɣ tzemmar řqecɛet nnec ad tini: ‘War ɣares bu ifassen’? \x ◘ \xo 45:9 \xt Irm. 18:6; Rum. 9:20\x*
\v 10 \bd Uct\bd* x wenni iqqaren i baba\add s\add*: ‘Min dd-tejjid?’ Niɣ i temɣart: ‘Min dd-turud?’”
\b
\m 
\v 11 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, Amqeddas n Israil, d Wenni t iggin: ‘Seqsam ayi x tmesřayin i dd ittasen, ttecřem xafi ad ḥḍiɣ iḥenjiren inu uřa d řxedmet n ifassen inu.
\v 12 Necc ggiɣ tammurt u xeřqeɣ-dd xas bnadem. \add Wah\add* d Necc \add i tt yeggin\add*, ifassen inu bezzɛen ijenwan, u marra řɛeskarat nsen ttumureɣ tent. \f ◼ \fr 45:12 \fk řɛeskarat nsen\ft - ixs ad yini: tafuct d tziri d itran d temmura n ijenwan, maca uřa d lmalakat d imqeddasen n SIDI AREBBI.\f*
\v 13 Necc ssekkareɣ t di tsegda uca ad seggmeɣ marra ibriden nnes. Netta ad ibna tandint inu ɛawed uca ad issnufseř imeḥbas inu, war iǧi i ttaman u war iǧi i tarzeft!’ iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.” \f ◼ \fr 45:13 \fk Necc ssekkareɣ t\ft - ixs ad yini ‘Necc ssekkareɣ Kurac’ (xzar ayet 1).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 45:13 \xt 2 Im. 36:22; Ɛiz. 1:1; Ica. 44:28; Ɛbr. 11:10\x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Arber n Imiṣriyyen d ṣṣeřɛet n ayt n Kuc d Saba, iryazen imɣaren di tiddi, ad ɣarem dd-ẓwan uca ad iřin nnem. Nitni ad cem ḍfaren, ad ɣarem ɛdun di ssnaseř, ad am sejden, ad am sellmen ixef nsen, ad neɛmen: ‘S tidett, ɣarem i iǧa Arebbi, war din iǧi wenneɣni, uřa d ijj nneɣni mɣir AREBBI!’
\v 15 D tidett, Cek d Arebbi inuffaren, AREBBI n Israil, Amsenjem.
\v 16 Nitni marra ad seḍḥan, ad ttwafeḍḥen ɛawed. Imziřen n řexyařat n l’aṣnam ad ffɣen jmiɛ, nnfeḍhen. \x ◘ \xo 45:16 \xt Ica. 44:11\x*
\v 17 Israil ad ittwassenjem s \add ufus n\add* SIDI s ijj n usenjem ittduman. War tᵉttseḍḥim u war tᵉttnefḍiḥem i řebda qaɛ.’”
\b
\m 
\v 18 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI, wenni dd-ixeřqen ijenwan, Netta, AREBBI, d wenni ikewwnen tammurt uca ittegg i-tt, Netta, d wenni tt issmetnen. War tt-i-dd-ixřiq texwa, \add maca\add* ikewwen i-tt maḥend ad xas zeddɣen: Necc d SIDI, war iǧi uřa d ijj nneɣni!” \x ◘ \xo 45:18 \xt Ica. 42:5; 45:5, 14\x*
\b
\m 
\v 19 “War ssiwřeɣ s tnuffra, di ca n wemcan ibarrecnen di temmurt. Necc war nniɣ i tarwa n Yaɛqub: Arzum ayi baṭeř! Necc d SIDI nni issawařen tasegda, d wenni ittbarrḥen min iǧan iseggmen.” \x ◘ \xo 45:19 \xt Aɛwd. 30:11\x*
\b
\m 
\v 20 “Munem, asem-dd, qarrbem-dd munen, \add a kenniw,\add* inni innejmen zi řegnus! Nitni war ssinen walu, inni yarebbun řexyařat ineqcen n ukeccuḍ uca ttɛebbden i yijj n arebbi nni war izemmaren ad issenjem. \x ◘ \xo 45:20 \xt Ica. 44:18, 19\x*
\v 21 Barrḥem, qarrbem-dd. Mcawarem di win jar awem: Man wen iggin ad sřen aya zeg wecḥař uya, man wen zzayes ibarrḥen zi meřmi? Ma war iǧi d Necc, SIDI? Nhřa Necc war iǧi uřa d ijj n AREBBI nneɣni, nhřa Necc war \add din\add* iǧi Arebbi Amsegged d Umsenjem. \x ◘ \xo 45:21 \xt Ica. 41:22, 26, 27; 43:9, 10; 45:5, 14, 18\x*
\v 22 Qeřbem-dd ɣari u tejjem ixef nwem ad ttwassnejmem, \add a kenniw,\add* marra \add iwdan n\add* ṭṭrufa n temmurt, maɣar Necc d Arebbi u war \add din\add* iǧi uřa d ijj n nneɣni.
\v 23 Necc jjuǧeɣ ɣar Ixef inu, iffeɣ-dd ijj n wawař zeg uqemmum inu di tsegda uca \add awař-a\add* war din iqqim wedwař: Aqa marra afud ad yaḍar zzati, marra iřes ad ɣari ijjaǧ! \x ◘ \xo 45:23 \xt Rum. 4:11; Fil. 2:10\x*
\v 24 Ad xafi qqaren: ‘Di SIDI waha teǧa tasegda ifeyyḍen d jjehd!’ Nitni ad ɣares dd-asen, \add maca\add* marra inni xas ittfugmen, ad seḍḥan. \x ◘ \xo 45:24 \xt Ica. 41:11\x*
\v 25 \add Maca\add* marra zzariɛet n Israil, ad ttwaseggden nitni di SIDI uca ad \add t\add* cennɛen.”
\b
\b
\c 46
\s1 Aweṭṭu n irebbiten n Babil
\m 
\v 1 “\add Ṣṣanam\add* Bil yuḍar, Nabu iqwes \add ɣar temmurt\add*, aqa řexyařat n l’aṣnam nsen \add deqqřent\add* i řmař u i řebhayem. Min tuɣa tarebbum kenniw, \add aqa řexxu\add* d řeḥmuř, ddqeř i \add řmař\add* ifnan s řweḥřan.
\v 2 Aqa qewsen am kemmřen, uḍaren, war zemmaren ad ssnejmen ddqeř, uca uřa d nitni simant nsen uyuren di tmeḥbast.”
\b
\m 
\v 3 “Sřem ɣari, \add a\add* taddart n Yaɛqub, d marra min iqqimen n taddart n Israil, \add kenniw,\add* inni ksiɣ zeg uɛeddis n yemmatwem, inni arbureɣ zeg wami tsemḥem deg uɛeddis n yemmatwem.
\v 4 Ař tawsart \add nwem\add* \bd Necc Necc\bd*, ař ɣa tcabem, ad \add kenniw\add* arbuɣ. Necc ggiɣ \add t\add* u Necc ad \add kenniw\add* ksiɣ, ad \add kenniw\add* arbuɣ u ad \add kenniw\add* ssnejmeɣ.”
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Ak-d man wen texsem ad ayi tessemquddam, u man wen texsem akidi tᵉssekkwim \add maḥend\add* ad nemrawas? \x ◘ \xo 46:5 \xt Ica. 40:18, 25\x*
\v 6 Ttfarraɣen nitni ureɣ zi tecyart u wezznen nnuqart x řmizan. Ttxeǧṣen ijj n wemziř n wureɣ, \add maḥend\add* netta ad zzayes igg ijj n arebbi. Sejjaden, wah, bendqen as.
\v 7 Arebbun t x teɣruḍt, kessin t da d diha, xenni ssbeddan t deg wemcan nnes. Dinni ittɣima ibedd, war ittenhizzi ssenni. Wah, mařa ḥed iřaɣa as, war dd-ittarri, war t issenjam zi řeḥṣaret nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 46:7 \xt Ica. 45:20\x*
\m 
\v 8 “Ɛeqřem x man aya, dewřem ɣar řbař nwem, ksim t ɣar wuř, \add a kenniw\add* inni ittɛeddan!
\v 9 Ɛeqřem x tmesřayin timezwura zeg wecḥař uya: aqa Necc d Arebbi: war din iǧi uřa d ijj n AREBBI nneɣni, uca uřa d ijj war iǧi am Necc, \x ◘ \xo 46:9 \xt Ica. 45:5, 14, 18, 21, 22; 48:12\x*
\v 10 wenni ibarrḥen zeg umezwar min ɣa yiři ɣar uneggar, uřa zeg wecḥař uya min war imsaren \add ɛad\add*, wenni iqqaren: ‘Axarreṣ inu yarcem, ad ggeɣ marra arḍa inu!’, \x ◘ \xo 46:10 \xt Izhd. 33:11; Awřn. 19:21; 21:30; Ɛbr. 6:17\x*
\v 11 wenni iřaɣan ajḍiḍ ittkeccaḍen zi ccarq, aryaz n uxarreṣ nnes zi temmurt iggʷejen. \add Wah\add*, am mammec ssiwřeɣ, \add ammu i\add* tt ɣa ggeɣ ad dd-yas, Necc sswejdeɣ tt, ad tt ggeɣ.”
\m 
\v 12 “Sřem ɣari, \add kenniw\add* ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa, inni iggʷejen x tsegda!
\v 13 Ad dd-ssqarrbeɣ tasegda inu, aqa war tᵉtteggʷij, war ittɛeṭṭiř usenjem inu. Ad awyeɣ asenjem di Ṣihyun, \add ad wceɣ\add* aɛuǧi inu i Israil.”
\b
\b
\c 47
\s1 Aweṭṭu n Babil
\m 
\v 1 “Hwa, qqim di tɛejjajt, \add a cem,\add* taɛzarect, yeǧis n Babil! Qqim x temmurt, war \add din\add* iǧi ɛad ijj n řɛarc, \add a\add* yeǧis n Ikaldaniyyen! Maɣar war d am qqaren ɛad ‘Tamudrust’ niɣ ‘Llif’. \x ◘ \xo 47:1 \xt Ica. 26:5\x*
\v 2 Ksi tasirt uca ḥriy awren! Kkes ařeḥḥaf nnem, sgeɛɛed abeḥrur nnem, ɛarra ifadden uca tcuqed deg iɣezran!
\v 3 Řeḥya nnem ad ittwaɛarra, ad tᵉttwaẓar ɛad řefḍiḥet nnem. Ad xeřfeɣ u war ssɛizziɣ x uřa d ijj n bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 47:3 \xt Ica. 3:17; Nḥm. 3:5\x*
\v 4 Amefdi nneɣ, SIDI n řɛeskarat d Isem nnes, aqa-t d Amqeddas n Israil.”
\m 
\v 5 “Qqim din uca sseɣd, ffeɣ \add ɣar barra\add* di taǧest, \add a\add* yeǧis n Ikaldaniyyen, maɣar war d am qqaren ɛad ‘Llalas n tgeldiwin’.
\v 6 Necc ggiɣ aɣḍab inu ad idduqqez x řgens inu, ssɛiǧteɣ tasɣart inu uca ggiɣ ten deg ifassen nnem, \add maca\add* cem war d asen tessecned arreḥmet. Ɛad i uwessar teqqned as taɣnact tedqeř.
\v 7 Tennid: ‘Necc ad iřiɣ d llalas \add n tgeldiwin\add* i řebda!’, mintra war teksid aya marra ɣar wuř, ɛemmarṣ war tidared qeṭṭu n uya \add marra\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 47:7 \xt Asa. 18:7\x*
\m 
\v 8 “\add Xenni\add* řexxu, seř i uya, \add a cem,\add* \add tamɣart\add* n meẓri, tenni \add i din\add* iqqimen di řaman, tenni iqqaren deg wuř nnes: ‘D necc, war \add din\add* teǧi uřa d ict nneɣnit! Ɛemmarṣ ad da qqimeɣ d tajjač, nhřa iḥenjiren war t ssineɣ!’ \x ◘ \xo 47:8 \xt Asa. 18:7\x*
\v 9 \add Maca\add* tnayen-a ad xam wḍan deg ict n tecti, deg ijj n wass: nhřa iḥenjiren d tajjač ad tiřid! \add Tnayen-a\add* ad xam wḍan zi ssibbet n waṭṭas n tgezzant nnem d ubarru n tseḥḥart nnem. \x ◘ \xo 47:9 \xt Ica. 51:19; Asa. 18:8\x*
\v 10 \add Maɣar\add* tᵉttecřed x tuɛeffna nnem, \add tennid\add*: ‘War d ayi ittwiři uřa d ijjen!’ Tiɣit nnem d tussna nnem arrint cem ad tarred s weɛrur \add ɣari\add*. Deg wuř nnem tennid: ‘D necc, war \add din\add* iǧi uřa d ijj n nneɣni!’
\v 11 Ad xam dd-yas řɣar d ameqqran. Mammec ad dd-inqar, war tessined \add qbeř\add*. Aweddar ad xam iwḍa ařami war tzemmared ad as tessḥeyded. Deɣya ad xam dd-tas tecti, břa ma ad xas targbed \add qbeř\add*.”
\m 
\v 12 “Iwa, arzu ad teqqimed tbedded \add din\add* ak-d tgezzant nnem u ak-d ubarru nnem n tseḥḥart nni zi tessiḥřed ixef nnem zi temẓi nnem. Balak tzemmared ad ɣarem tiři tizi zi man aya, niɣ balak tzemmared ad tessiggʷeded s uya!
\v 13 Tessiḥřed ixef nnem ak-d waṭṭas n ixarriṣen nnem. Iwa, ad kkaren inni ittfekkan ajenna u ḥeṭṭan itran, inni ittkacafen min i dd ɣa yasen ɣar ubeddi n uyur, ejj i-ten ad cem ssnejmen zi min xam ɣa ikken ɣar zzat.
\v 14 Xzar, nitni ad dewřen am uřum: ad ten tessecmeḍ tmessi, war zemmaren ad fekken řeɛmar nsen zeg ifassen n iceɛɛařen n tmessi. War ittiři řefḥem itteḥduduqen nni ɣar zɣařen, war iǧi uḥaduq nni ɣar zemmaren ad qqimen.
\v 15 Ammu i ɣa iřin i cem inni umi tuɣa tessaḥařed ixef nnem, isebbaben nnem zi temẓi nnem. Kuř ijj ad yuyur deg webrid nnes, uřa d ijj war cem issenjim.” \x ◘ \xo 47:15 \xt Asa. 17:16\x*
\b
\b
\c 48
\s1 Afekki zi Babil
\m 
\v 1 “Sřem aya, \add a kenniw\add* taddart n Yaɛqub, inni umi ttřaɣan s yisem n Israil, \add inni\add* iffɣen zeg waman n Yahuda, inni ittjaǧan ɣar Yisem n SIDI u ttidaren AREBBI n Israil, \add maca\add* war iǧi di tidett, u war iǧi di tsegda.
\v 2 Nitni ttřaɣan ixef nsen ‘\add Řgens\add* zi tendint tamqeddast!’ u ttcařen x AREBBI n Israil, aqa SIDI n řɛeskarat d Isem nnes.”
\b
\m 
\v 3 “Timesřayin timezwura ssargbeɣ xasent ɛad aṭṭas zeg wami, aqa ffɣent-i-dd zeg uqemmum inu uca barrḥeɣ zzaysent. Deɣya ggiɣ \add tent\add* uca \add xenni\add* usint-i-dd.
\v 4 Minzi Necc ssneɣ, aqa cek tessqesḥed ixef nnec, aqa ijiman nnec am tbarrat n wuzzař u tanyart nnec \add axmi dd-tekka zi\add* nnḥas,
\v 5 ssargbeɣ \add ac tent\add* ɛad aṭṭas zeg wami. Qbeř ma imsar, barrḥeɣ zzaysent maḥend cek war teqqared: ‘Ṣṣanam inu igga i-tent!’, \add niɣ\add* ‘Řexyarat inu ineqcen!’ \add niɣ:\add* ‘Řexyař inu ifesyen yumur i-tent!’
\v 6 Cek tesřid xasent, xzar mliḥ ɣar marra aya. Ma war texsem ad zzaysent tbarrḥem? Zi řexxu ad ac barrḥeɣ timesřayin n jdid, timesřayin innuffaren nni war tessined.
\m 
\v 7 Řexxu ttwaxeřqent-dd, war iǧi aṭṭas zeg wami. Qbeř ass-a war xasent tesřid maḥend war teqqared: ‘Xzar, ssneɣ tt meřmi!’
\v 8 Wah, war xasent tesřid u ɛawed war tent tessined u ɛawed amezzuɣ nnec tuɣa war yarzim, maɣar Necc ssneɣ, aqa cek ad tegged s řeɣdaret aṭṭas uca ad ac řaɣan ‘Wenni ittɛeddan!’ \add ɛad\add* zeg uɛeddis n yemmac.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem inu ad ssɛeḍřeɣ aɣḍab inu, u \add di ṭṭweɛ\add* n ccan inu ad tebbteɣ Ixef inu i řxar nnec, maḥend war cek meḥḥiɣ qaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 48:9 \xt Ica. 43:21, 25\x*
\v 10 Xzar, Necc sseṣfiɣ cek, \add maca\add* war iǧi am nnuqart, qeǧbeɣ cek di tefqunt n usefṣi n řeɣben.
\v 11 Di ṭṭweɛ inu, di ṭṭweɛ inu ad t ggeɣ, maɣar mammec i ɣa ittwaɛarra Isem inu? Aɛuǧi inu war t tticeɣ i uřa d ijjen nneɣni.” \x ◘ \xo 48:11 \xt Ica. 42:8\x*
\b
\m 
\v 12 “Seř-dd ɣari, \add a\add* Yaɛqub, \add cek, a\add* Israil, wenni umi řaɣiɣ! \bd Necc Necc\bd*, Necc d Amezwaru uřa d Aneggaru. \x ◘ \xo 48:12 \xt Ica. 41:4; 44:6; Asa. 1:17; 22:13\x*
\v 13 Afus inu issars ɛawed dsusa n temmurt, uca afusi inu ibezzeɛ ijenwan. Mařa řaɣiɣ asen, ttbeddan nitni \add dinni\add* jmiɛ.
\v 14 Munem marra kenniw u sřem: Man wen jar asen ibarreḥ zi \add marra\add* man aya? SIDI ittexs i-t, u wanita ad yegg ɛlaḥsab řxaḍar nnes ḍidd i Babil, aɣiř nnes ad yiři ḍidd i Ikaldaniyyen. \x ◘ \xo 48:14 \xt Ica. 41:22, 23\x*
\v 15 Aqa Necc, \add wah,\add* Necc nniɣ t, u Necc řaɣiɣ as \add ɛawed\add*. Ad ggeɣ ad dd-yas, uca netta ad ifřeḥ deg webrid nnes.
\v 16 Qarrbem-dd ɣari, sřem aya: Zeg umezwaru Necc war ssiwřeɣ s tnuffra. Zeg wami marra aya imsar, aqa ayi Necc din! ‘U řexxu Sidi inu, SIDI, issekk ayi-dd, ak-d Arruḥ nnes.’”
\b
\m 
\v 17 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, Amefdi nnec, Amqeddas n Israil: ‘Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni cek issřemden min ineffɛen, d wenni cek ineddhen deg webrid nni x i ɣa tuyured.
\v 18 Ax, mři texzared \add maca\add* ɣar tweṣṣa inu, \add xenni\add* ad yaf řehna nnec ad yiři am yeɣzar u tasegda nnec am řemwaj n řebḥar, \x ◘ \xo 48:18 \xt Aɛwd. 32:29; Izhd. 81:14\x*
\v 19 zzariɛet nnec tuɣa-tt am yijdi, u \add iḥenjiren nnec\add* nni dd-itteffɣen zi tejɛinna nnec am řḥebb i dd-yusin zzayes. Isem nnes war ittneqḍiɛ u war ittwateḥḥi zzat i wudem inu.’”
\b
\m 
\v 20 “Ffɣem zi Babil, arewřem zeg Ikaldaniyyen, barrḥem \add as\add* s iɣuyyan n usřiwřew, maḥend ad sřen aya, suffɣem \add řexbar\add* ař aneggar n ddunect, inim: ‘SIDI ifekk amsexxar nnes Yaɛqub!’ \f ◼ \fr 48:20 \fk ddunnit\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘tammurt’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 48:20 \xt Ica. 52:11; Irm. 50:8; 51:6,45; Asa. 18:4\x*
\v 21 War xasen ikki ufadi umi ten dd-igewwed s imucan ittwaxarrben. Netta issuffeɣ asen-dd aman zi teṣḍart. Umi Netta ifeǧeq jjarf, dduqqzen-dd zzayes waman.”
\m 
\v 22 “Iɛeffanen war ttifen řehna!, iqqar SIDI.”\x ◘ \xo 48:22 \xt Ica. 57:21\x*
\b
\b
\c 49
\s1 Cchadet n Umsexxar n SIDI x Yixef nnes
\m 
\v 1 “Sřem-dd ɣari, \add a\add* tigzirin, sḥessem, \add a\add* ccuɛub n řaggʷaj! SIDI iřaɣa ayi-dd zeg \add wami d ayi tuɣa deg\add* uɛeddis n yemma, zeg \add wami d ayi tuɣa ɛad di\add* řemřawet iřaɣa ayi-dd s Yisem inu.
\v 2 Netta igga aqemmum inu d ssif iqeḍɛen, Netta issduriy ayi di tiři n ufus nnes. Netta igga ayi d fřitca s tixeft iqeḍɛen, igga ayi deg weqrab nnes n fřitcat.
\v 3 Inna ayi: ‘Cek d Amsexxar inu Israil nni di ɣa ttwassɛuǧeɣ!’”
\b
\m 
\v 4 “\add Maca\add* Necc nniɣ: ‘Necc arbreɣ x walu, ḍeyyɛeɣ jjehd inu di řxawi d řbaṭeř. S tidett, tasɣart inu ɣar SIDI u řmunet inu ɣar AREBBI inu.’”
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Uca řexxu iqqar SIDI, wenni d ayi iggin d Amsexxar zeg wami d ayi tuɣa deg uɛeddis n yemma maḥend ad ɣares dd-ssɛeqbeɣ Yaɛqub u maḥend ad ɣares ssmuneɣ Israil - \add wah,\add* Necc ttwassɛuǧeɣ di tiṭṭawin n SIDI uca AREBBI inu d Jjehd inu! -
\v 6 \add wah,\add* Netta iqqar: ‘Drus, aqa cek ad tiřid d Amsexxar inu maḥend ad tessnekkared \add ɛawed\add* tiqebbař n Yaɛqub u maḥend ad dd-tarred inni ittwaḥdan zi Israil. Necc ggiɣ Cek d Tafawt i řegnus, maḥend ad tiřid d asenjem inu ař uneggar n temmurt!’
\v 7 Ammu i iqqar SIDI, Amefdi n Israil, Amqeddes nnes, i weryaz ittwasseḥqaren, i wenni d nnɛi n řgens, i Umsexxar n ayt n ṣṣulṭa: ‘Ijeǧiden ad \add Cek\add* ẓaren u ad kkaren, řḥukkam ad aḍaren zzatek di ṭṭweɛ n SIDI, wenni d amtiqqi, Amqeddas n Israil, wenni Cek ifarzen!’”
\b
\m 
\v 8 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Di řḥař n arḍa, sřiɣ ac, u deg wass n usenjem, wciɣ ac afus. Necc ad Cek ḥḍiɣ u ad Cek areccḥeɣ d Řɛahd n řgens, maḥend ad tessbedded tammurt, maḥend ad tᵉṭṭfed tiseqqar yareddǧen ɛawed d tasɣart, \x ◘ \xo 49:8 \xt 2 Kur. 6:2\x*
\v 9 maḥend ad tinid i imeḥbas: Ffɣem-dd!, i yinni \add iǧan\add* di taǧest: Ḍharem-dd! Ad arewsen ɣar ibriden, x marra tiwririn iquccaren ad iřin ddmani nsen n tarewsa.
\v 10 War xasen ittekk řaẓ uřa d afadi, řeḥmu d tfuct war ten teccit ca, maɣar wenni xasen ittḥinnan ad ten igewwed, ad ten indeh ɣar tařawin n waman. \x ◘ \xo 49:10 \xt Asa. 7:16\x*
\v 11 Marra idurar inu ad ten ggeɣ d ibriden u ibriden inu iwaṭan ad ttwassuɛřan.
\v 12 Xzar, ad dd-asen zi řaggʷaj. Xzar, ina \add ad dd-asen\add* zi ccamal u zi řebḥar u inneɣni zi temmurt n Aswan.’” \f ◼ \fr 49:12 \fk Aswan\ft - tandint di ljanub n Miṣra, maca ca n řmaxtuṭṭat nneɣni qqarent: ‘Sinim’. Ad taɣ nitni d Icinwiyyen n ass n yiḍa.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 13 “Sřiwřiwem, \add a kenniw\add* ijenwan, farḥet, \add a cem,\add* tammurt! Arrem idurar ad dduqqzen s usřiwřew, maɣar SIDI issfewwej x řgens nnes, Netta ad iḥinn x řmusakin nnes!”
\b
\m 
\v 14 “\add Maca\add* Ṣihyun tenna: ‘SIDI ismeḥ dayi, Sidi inu ittu ayi.’
\v 15 Ma tzemmar temɣart ad tᵉttu aseymi nnes, umi war tᵉttḥinni x mmis n uɛeddis nnes? Waxxa tᵉttu t, Necc war cem ttᵉttuɣ.
\v 16 Xzar, Necc neqceɣ cem di tnayen n třeqqa n ifassen \add inu\add*, řeḥyuḍ nnem řebda ɣari zzat i tiṭṭawin.
\v 17 Iḥenjiren nnem ad ɛeřfen, \add maca\add* imteḥḥayen nnem u inni cem ixarrben ad xam uyuren.
\v 18 Sgeɛɛed tamuɣři nnem uca xzar da d diha. Xzar, marra munen usin-dd ɣarem. S tidett am ddareɣ Necc, iqqar SIDI, ad tarḍed ixef nnem s marra ina am s řehzuṭ, uca ad zzaysen tzewwqed ixef nnem am \add t tegga\add* tesřit.’ \x ◘ \xo 49:18 \xt Ica. 60:4\x*
\v 19 Maɣar řxirbat nnem d imucan nnem ittwareddǧen, \add wah\add* tammurt nnem ittwateḥḥan ad tiři teḥṣar i imezdaɣ, uca inni ixsen ad cem ṣarḍen, ad iřin ɣar řaggʷaj.
\v 20 Uřa d iḥenjiren nni zzayem ittwacaren, ad inin deg imezzuɣen nnem: ‘Amcan dayes řḥeṣran xafi, egg ayi amcan i necc, \add maḥend\add* zemmareɣ ad \add dayes\add* zedɣeɣ!’
\v 21 Ad tinid deg wuř nnem: ‘Man wen i d ayi dd-yurwen marra iḥenjiren-a? Ucaren ayi iḥenjiren u war dd-ttirweɣ, ssuffɣen ayi-dd d ameḥbus uca nḍaren ayi-dd. Man wen i ten isseymen? Xzar, necc waha d tenni tuɣa iceṭṭen, manis dd-usin nitni?’”
\b
\m 
\v 22 “Ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ afus inu ɣar řegnus u ad ssbeddeɣ taɛeǧant inu i řegnus. \add Xenni\add* ad awyen iḥenjiren nnem deg weḥsin nsen \add ɣar danita\add* uca ad arbun yessim x tɣarḍin nsen.
\v 23 Ijeǧiden ad cem ṣunen, tijeǧidin ad cem ssuṭṭdent. Ad aḍaren zzatek s uɣembub nsen ɣar temmurt, ad am řesḥen taɛejjact zeg iḍaren nnem. \add Xenni\add* ad tessned aqa Necc d SIDI, uca inni xas i ɣa isitimen, war ttseḍḥin ca.’”
\b
\m 
\v 24 “Ma izemmar ijj ad ikkes x wenni ijehden zzardet? Ma izemmar ad yarweř wenni iǧan d ameḥbus n umsegged? \x ◘ \xo 49:24 \xt Mt. 12:29\x*
\v 25 \add Maca\add* ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ad dd-ttwakksen imeḥbas zeg ufus n umzemmar uřa d takeccaḍṭ n uqehhar ad textutteř zi jar ifassen nnes. \add Maɣar\add* wenni ixsen ad cem icarreɛ, Necc ad t carrɛeɣ, uca iḥenjiren nnem ad ten ssnejmeɣ.
\v 26 I yinni cem iḥeṣṣaren ad asen wceɣ ad ccen aysum \add n yixef\add* nsen u nitni ad scaren s idammen nsen am s binu ẓemmen t jdid, u marra iwdan ad ssnen aqa Necc, SIDI, d Amsenjam nnem d Amefdi nnem, Amzemmar n Yaɛqub.’” \x ◘ \xo 49:26 \xt Asa. 16:6\x*
\b
\b
\c 50
\s1 Acetci iɣeccen
\m 
\v 1 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Mani teǧa tebrat n waǧaf, tenni zi ssqebbḍeɣ yemmatwem? Niɣ i man wen zeg aytbab n wareṭṭar inu kenniw zzenzeɣ? Xzar, zi ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyet nwem temmenzem u zi ssibbet n iɛeddiyen nwem temmenz yemmatwem.
\v 2 Mayemmi dd-usiɣ, war din iǧi uřa d ijj, mayemmi i řaɣiɣ, war dd-yarri uřa d ijj? Ma afus inu d aquḍaḍ ařami war izemmar ad ifekk, ma war dayi iǧi jjhed, ḥima ad fekkeɣ? Xzar, s usiggʷed inu ad ssiẓreɣ řebḥar, ad ggeɣ iɣezran d řexřa uca ad aẓɣen \add ařami\add* i ɣa yarṣuḍen iseřman nsen maɣar war \add din\add* iǧi \add ɛad\add* waman, uca ad mmten zeg ufadi. \x ◘ \xo 50:2 \xt Řxř. 11:23; Ica. 59:1\x*
\v 3 Ad ssyarḍeɣ ajenna s tubbarcent, ad ten řeḥḥfeɣ s txancet \add n wecḍan\add* am warruḍ \add nsen\add*.’”
\b
\m 
\v 4 “Sidi inu, SIDI, iwca ayi iřes n umeḥḍar, maḥend Necc ad ssneɣ mammec ɣa ssmeḥdeɣ wenni yuḥḥřen s ijj n wawař. Qaɛ tuffut Netta issfaqa ayi, issfaqa ayi amezzuɣ, maḥend Necc ad \add ɣares\add* sřiɣ am umeḥḍar.
\v 5 Sidi inu, SIDI, yarzem ayi amezzuɣ u Necc war ɣewwɣeɣ ca, war dd-ddwiřeɣ ɣar ḍeffar. \x ◘ \xo 50:5 \xt Yḥ. 14:31; Fil. 2:8; Ɛbr. 10:5-10\x*
\v 6 Necc wciɣ aɛrur inu i yinni d ayi iwtin, u iɣemmizen inu i yinni d ayi issnecfen \add tmart\add*. Aɣembub inu war t ssnuffareɣ zzat i useḥqar d ususef.
\v 7 \add Maca\add* Sidi inu, SIDI, ad ayi iwc afus, x uya war qeṭṭiɣ di řefḍiḥet, x uya jjiɣ aɣembub inu iqseḥ am sseǧaḥ, \add minzi\add* ssneɣ, aqa Necc war ttseḍḥiɣ ca.
\v 8 Wenni d ayi ittseggden, aqa-t yudes. Man wen i ɣa izeɛmen ad kidi icarreɛ? Jjem aneɣ ad nbedd nmun! Man wen kidi ittemcarraɛen, ejj i-t ad ɣari dd-yas. \x ◘ \xo 50:8 \xt Rum. 8:32,33\x*
\v 9 Xzar, Sidi inu, SIDI, ad ayi iwc afus. Man wen izemmaren ad ayi igg řɛib? Xzar, nitni marra am warruḍ idduysaren, ad ten tecc tcinda.”
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Man wen \add i din\add* jar awem itteggʷed zi SIDI, man wen \add jar awem\add* ittesřan i tmijja n Umsexxar nnes? Wenni igguren di taǧest d wenni umi war ɣar teǧi tafawt, ejj i-t ad ittceř x Yisem n SIDI, \add ejj i-t\add* ad iɛemmed x AREBBI nnes.
\v 11 Xzar, kenniw marra tessarɣem timessi, tbeysem ixef nwem s fřitcat i usecmaḍ. \add Iwa,\add* uyurem \add xenni\add* di tfawt n tmessi nwem u ɣar \add tfawt n\add* fřitcat yareqqen nni tessarɣem. Aya ad xawem dd-yas zeg ufus inu, s řeḥriq ad tezzřem \add dinni\add*.”
\b
\b
\c 51
\s1 Afaqi n uɣiř n SIDI, Urcalim d Siḥyun
\m 
\v 1 “Sřem ɣari, \add a kenniw\add* inni iḍaffaren tasegda, \add kenniw\add* inni yarezzun SIDI! Xzarem ɣar teṣḍart manis tᵉttwaneqcem u ɣar wexbuc n wanu manis dd-tᵉttwaɣzem.
\v 2 Xzarem ɣar Ibrahim, jedditwem, u ɣar Sara, tenni kenniw i dd-yurwen. Maɣar tuɣa-t \add ɛad\add* ḥafi umi t řaɣiɣ, \add maca\add* Necc barkeɣ t u arzfeɣ as aṭṭas n wara.
\v 3 Maɣar SIDI ad issfewwej Ṣihyun, ad issfewwej marra řxirbat nnes uca ad tt yarr am \add jjennet n\add* Ɛadn u řexřa nnes am weḥwic di jjennet n SIDI. Arcaq d řefraḥet ad dayes ten afen, aqadi d řḥess n izehhiden.”
\b
\m 
\v 4 “Sřem-dd ɣari, \add a\add* cceɛb inu, u wcem ayi amezzuɣ, \add a\add* řgens inu, maɣar ad zzayi teffeɣ Ccariɛa u Necc ad ḍemneɣ řḥeqq inu ař ɣa yiři \add řḥeqq inu\add* d tafawt i řegnus.
\v 5 Tasegda inu tudes-dd, asenjem inu itteffeɣ-dd u iɣaǧen inu ad carrɛen řegnus, ad ayi rajant tegzirin uca ad ssitment x uɣiř inu.”
\b
\m 
\v 6 “Sgeɛɛdem tiṭṭawin nwem ɣar ujenna, xzarem tammurt da swadday, maɣar ajenna ad iffarfar am ddexxan, tammurt ad tedduysar am warruḍ, uca ammu i ɣa mmten \add uřa d\add* imezdaɣ nnes, \add maca\add* asenjem inu ad iqqim i řebda, tasegda inu ɛemmarṣ war tt qeṭṭin.”
\b
\m 
\v 7 “Sřem-dd ɣari, \add a kenniw\add* inni issnen tasegda, \add a cek\add* řgens nni \add yarebbun\add* Ccariɛa inu deg wuř. War tteggʷdem zi řḥegra n yewdan u war ten ttejjim ad cem arẓen s uɛeyyeb nsen! \x ◘ \xo 51:7 \xt Izhd. 37:31; 118:6; Ica. 51:12\x*
\v 8 Maɣar tacinda ad ten tecc am tᵉttett arruḍ, uca akiccu ad ten yecc am taḍuft, \add maca\add* tasegda inu ad teqqim i řebda u asenjem inu zi jjiř ař jjiř.” \x ◘ \xo 51:8 \xt Ica. 50:9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 9 \bd “Faq, faq,\bd* arḍ s jjhed, \add a\add* aɣiř n SIDI! Faq am deg wussan n zic, am di jjiřat n zzmanat n wecḥar uya. Ma war iǧi d Cek, wenni iqessen Rahab, d wenni issnuqqben řhaycet?
\v 10 Ma war iǧi d Cek wenni issiẓɣen řebḥar, aman n řḥemřet n \add waman\add* imeqqranen innhewřen \add Ma war iǧi d Cek\add* wenni yarrin abrid deg waman yuǧɣen n řebḥar, ařami zemmaren ad ẓwan inni ittwafekken? \x ◘ \xo 51:10 \xt Ica. 43:16\x*
\v 11 Inni ifda i-ten SIDI ad dd-dewřen, ad dd-asen ɣar Ṣihyun s usřiwřew. Řefraḥet n řebda ad tiři x izeǧifen nsen, nitni ad sswiẓẓḍen \add ifassen nsen\add* ɣar warcaq d řefraḥet, \add am\add* i ɣa yarweř zzaysen wecḍan d wesḥissef.”
\b
\m 
\v 12 “D Necc, \add wah,\add* d Necc wenni kenniw issfewwjen. Min \add teɛnid\add* cek, aqa cek tᵉtteggʷeded zeg weryaz \add ifennan\add*, zi mmis n bnadem nni \add iǧan am\add* arbiɛ, \x ◘ \xo 51:12 \xt Izhd. 118:6; Ica. 51:7\x*
\v 13 tᵉttettud SIDI wenni cek iggin, wenni ibezzɛen ajenna d wenni issarsen dsusa n temmurt, aqa cek tᵉtteggʷeded řebda, ass ikmeř, zi ssibbet n wesɛar n wenni iḥeṣṣaren umi issewjad ixef nnes maḥend ad yareddeǧ? Mani iǧa \add xenni\add* wesɛar n wenni iḥeṣṣaren? \x ◘ \xo 51:13 \xt Ayub 9:8; Izhd. 104:2; Ica. 40:22; 42:5; 44:24\x*
\v 14 Wenni icarrfen s ssnaseř am ittefriɣ ad ittwafekk daweḥda. War ittmetti deg weḥfur \add n imeḥbas\add*, war zzayes ineqqeṣ weɣrum.
\v 15 \add Maɣar\add* Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni issehwařen řebḥar ař ɣa hajan řemwaj nnes, SIDI n řɛeskarat d Isem nnes.
\v 16 Tteggeɣ ac awařen inu deg uqemmum nnec u ssdurruyeɣ cek di tiři n ufus inu, maḥend ad ẓẓuɣ ajenna, ad ssarseɣ dsusa n temmurt u ad iniɣ i Ṣihyun: ‘Cek d řgens inu!’”
\b
\m 
\v 17 \bd “Faq, faq,\bd* kkar-dd a Urcalim! Zeg ufus n SIDI teswid zi řkas n wesɛar nnes ameqqran. Teccid řexmira zi řkas nni issdewwaxen, \add wah,\add* tẓemmed \add tt\add*. \x ◘ \xo 51:17 \xt Izhd. 60:5; Ica. 52:1\x*
\v 18 War tt ittgewwid uřa d ijjen zi marra iḥenjiren nni dd-turuw, u zi marra iḥenjiren nni tessyem, war tt yeṭṭif uřa d ijj zeg ufus.
\v 19 Tnayen \add n tmesřayin\add*-a řeqfent cem, \add maca\add* wi xam i ɣa iḥinnen? \add Xzar,\add* axarreb d weřbez d řaẓ d ssif! Mammec cem i ɣa ssfewwjeɣ? \x ◘ \xo 51:19 \xt Ica. 47:9\x*
\v 20 Wḍan iḥenjiren nnem, ɣacan, zzřen ɣar marra tiɣemmar n ibriden am tɣayḍin n wezɣar di tracca. Nitni jjiwnen s wesɛar n SIDI, s usiggʷed n AREBBI nnem.” \x ◘ \xo 51:20 \xt Igjd. 2:11, 12\x*
\b
\m 
\v 21 “S uya seř aya, \add a cem\add* řmiskina, d tamescart, \add maca\add* war iǧi s binu!
\v 22 Ammu i iqqar Sidi nnem, SIDI, AREBBI nnem, wenni iccaten ddeɛwet x řgens nnes: ‘Xzar, Necc ad kkseɣ řkas issdewwaxen zeg ufus nnem, war tsessed ɛad ktar zi řexmira n řkas n wesɛar inu.
\v 23 Necc ad t ggeɣ deg ufus n yinni dayem iɣezzan, inni innan i řeɛmar nnem: Saḍar ixef nnem \add ɣar temmurt\add*, neccin ad xam neẓwa! Ammu i teggid aɛrur nnem am mammec teǧid d tammurt, \add uca\add* tuɣa cek d abrid di ṭṭweɛ n yinni xam iẓwan.’”
\b
\b
\c 52
\m 
\v 1 \bd “Faq, faq\bd*, arḍ s jjehd \add a,\add* Ṣihyun, arḍ s werruḍ nnem iccuwwaren, \add a\add* Urcalim, tandint tamqeddast! Zi ssa tsawent war ɣarem t-i-dd-ittidif ɛad wenni war ittwaxetnen d umexmuj.
\v 2 Zerz xam taɛejjact, kkar, qqim cem, \add a\add* Urcalim! Arxu ssnaseř zeg yiri nnem, \add a\add* tameḥbust, \add a\add* yeǧis n Ṣihyun!
\v 3 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Temmenzem s baṭeř, ad tᵉttwassfekkem \add ɛawed\add* břa tmenyat!’
\v 4 Maɣar ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Zic ihwa řgens inu ɣar Miṣra maḥend ad dinni iqqim \add am řbarrani\add*, uca Accur iḥṣar i-t x walu!’” \x ◘ \xo 52:4 \xt Amz. 46:6\x*
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Uca řexxu, min ɣari ɛad xafi ad tt ggeɣ danita, iqqar SIDI, maɣar awyen řgens inu břa ssibbet uca inni xas ittṣellṭen ssɣuyyun, iqqar SIDI, ass marra ttɛeyyben deg Yisem inu. \x ◘ \xo 52:5 \xt Ḥiz. 36:20, 23; Rum. 2:24\x*
\v 6 S uya ad issen řgens inu Isem inu, s uya, aqa \bd Necc Necc\bd*, wenni iqqaren \bd deg wass nni\bd*: Necc aqa ayi da!”
\b
\m 
\v 7 “Mecḥař cnan x idurar iṣuraf n umbeccar nni ittbarrḥen s řehna, n umbeccar n \add řexbar\add* aṣebḥan nni ittbarrḥen s usenjem, wenni iqqaren i Ṣihyun: ‘AREBBI nnem d Ajeǧid!’ \x ◘ \xo 52:7 \xt Nḥm. 2:1; Rum. 10:15\x*
\v 8 \add Sřem i\add* tmijja n iɛessasen nnem! Nitni ttsgeɛɛaden tmijja \add nsen\add*, ttesřiwřiwen munen, maɣar udem deg udem \add akides\add* ad twařan mammec i dd ɣa isseɛqeb SIDI Ṣihyun.
\v 9 Sɣuyyent s řefraḥet, sřiwřewent tmunent, \add a\add* řxirbat n Urcalim, maɣar SIDI issfewwej řgens nnes, ifekk Urcalim.
\v 10 Iɛarra SIDI aɣiř nnes amqeddes zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra řegnus u marra timawwin n temmurt ad ẓarent asenjem n AREBBI nneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 52:10 \xt Izhd. 98:2; Lk. 3:6\x*
\b
\m 
\v 11 \bd “Ruḥem, ruḥem\bd*, ffɣem-dd ssenni, war ttḥadam walu n min ixemjen, ffɣem ssenni zi řwesṭ nnes, sizedgem ixef nwem, \add a kenniw\add* inni yarebbun řeqcuɛ n SIDI! \x ◘ \xo 52:11 \xt 2 Kur. 6:17; Asa. 18:4\x*
\v 12 Maɣar kenniw war tᵉtteffɣem s tezřa, war tarekkwařem, maɣar SIDI ad yuyur zzat nwem u AREBBI n Israil ad yiři d aɣezdis nwem aneggar.”
\b
\c 53
\s1 Aswaḍeɛ n Umsexxar n SIDI (Řexbar Aṣebḥan Wiss Xemsa)
\m 
\v 1 “Xzar, Amsexxar inu ad yegg s řeɛqeř, ad ittwassɛuǧa u ad ittwassuɛřa, \add wah,\add* ad ittwassɛuǧa ař ṭṭarf.
\v 2 Am zzayek nnxeřɛen aṭṭas - ammu s waṭṭas ixsar udem nnes, war iǧi \add ɛad\add* am n ijj n bnadem, u addud nnes, war iǧi \add ɛad\add* am n tarwa n bnadem - \x ◘ \xo 53:2 \xt Ica. 53:3\x*
\v 3 ammu i ɣa issengez Netta aṭṭas n řegnus, \add wah, ɛad\add* ijeǧiden ad sseɣden, maɣar min war d asen barrḥen, ad t ẓaren, u min ɛemmarṣ war sřin, ad t fehmen.” \x ◘ \xo 53:3 \xt Rum. 15:21\x*
\b
\b
\m 
\v 4 “Man wen yumnen di řexbar nneɣ u wi i umi d ittwasscen uɣiř n SIDI? \x ◘ \xo 53:4 \xt Yḥ. 12:38; Rum. 10:16\x*
\m 
\v 5 \add Maɣar\add* am tseṭṭa imɣar Netta zzat i wudem nnes, am weẓwar zi temmurt yuẓɣen. Netta tuɣa war ɣares addud niɣ acewwar \add xmi\add* t nẓar, war ɣares bu waẓri n řxeẓrat ařami dayes i ɣa nemmeẓri.
\m 
\v 6 Tuɣa ittwasseḥqar, immenḍar zeg iwdan, aryaz n řeḥriq, issen řeḥřac, am yijjen i umi řeḥḥfen aɣembub, \add ammu i\add* tuɣa ittwasseḥqar u neccin war t nḥessib walu. \x ◘ \xo 53:6 \xt Izhd. 22:7, 8; Izhd. 69:2-4; Ica. 49:7; 52:14; Mk. 9:12\x*
\m 
\v 7 S tidett, iksi xas řeḥřac nneɣ uca yarbu řeḥriq nneɣ, \add maca\add* neccin nḥesb i-t am yijjen teřqef i-t lmuṣiba, am yijjen iɣḍeř i-t u iḥṣar i-t AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 53:7 \xt Mt. 8:17\x*
\m 
\v 8 \add Maca\add* netta ittwassnuqqeb x iɛeddiyen nneɣ, x řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ řebzen t. Temmars xas tecti nni d aneɣ dd-issakkwaḍen řehna, u s iyezzimen nnes idweř aneɣ d agenfi. \x ◘ \xo 53:8 \xt Rum. 4:25; 5:1; 1 Kur. 15:3; Afa. 2:14; 1 Bṭ. 2:24\x*
\m 
\v 9 Marra neccin tuɣa nweddar am wuǧi, nedweř kuř ijj ɣar webrid nnes, \add maca\add* SIDI yarra ad xas tewḍa řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ marra. \x ◘ \xo 53:9 \xt Mt. 10:1, 5, 6\x*
\m 
\v 10 Deǧen t, uca ijja \add i-ten\add* ad t ssbehdřen. War yarzim aqemmum nnes. Am izmar nedhen t ɣar tɣarṣt, am texsi tegnu qibač i wenni tt iǧasen, ammu war yarzim Netta aqemmum nnes. \x ◘ \xo 53:10 \xt Mt. 26:63; 27:12, 14; Mk. 14:61; 15:5; Řex. 8:32; 1 Bṭ. 1:19-20\x*
\m 
\v 11 Immeksi-dd zi řeḥṣaret u zi řeḥkam. Man wen zi jjiř nnes tuɣa ixemm dayes, zeɛma ittwaqess zi temmurt n yinni iddaren, aqa xas ticti zi ssibbet n uɛeddi n řgens inu! \x ◘ \xo 53:11 \xt Dan. 9:26\x*
\m 
\v 12 Immewc as wenḍeř ɣar iɛeffanen, \add maca\add* ɣar ttujar tuɣa-t di řmewt nnes iqesḥen, waxxa netta ɛemmarṣ war iggi lɛunf u ɛemmarṣ war tuɣi řɣecc deg uqemmum nnes. \x ◘ \xo 53:12 \xt Mt. 27:57-61; 1 Bṭ. 2:22; 1 Yḥ. 3:5\x*
\m 
\v 13 \add Maca\add* tuɣa iǧa i arḍa n SIDI maḥend ad t iřbez, isseḥřec \add i-t\add*. Řami řeɛmar nnes igga ixef nnes d taɣarṣt n umarwas \add i ddnub nneɣ\add*, ad iẓar Netta zzariɛet, ad isszuggar Netta ussan nnes uca arḍa n SIDI ad iqfeř s ufus nnes. \x ◘ \xo 53:13 \xt Yḥ. 3:16\x*
\v 14 Di ssibbet n umarret n řeɛmar nnes ad t iẓar uca ad ijjiwen. S tussna nnes ad isegged Umsexxar inu, Amsegged, aṭṭas n yewdan, maɣar ad yarbu řmuɛṣiyyet nsen. \x ◘ \xo 53:14 \xt 1 Yḥ. 5:20\x*
\m 
\v 15 S uya ad as wceɣ tasɣart jar imeqqranen uca ak-d aytbab n ṣṣulṭa ad ibḍa takeccaḍt, minzi isebbeř tudart nnes i řmewt uca ittwaḥseb zeg inni ittɛeddan uca yarbu ddnub n waṭṭas uca ittar di ṭṭweɛ n yinni ittɛeddan.” \f ◼ \fr 53:15 \fk tudart\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 53:15 \xt Mk. 15:28; Lk. 22:37; 23:34; Kul. 2:15\x*
\b
\b
\c 54
\s1 Řefraḥet n temɣart i war dd-ittirwen n Siḥyun
\m 
\v 1 “Sriwřew, \add cem\add* tenni war ittirwen ɛemmarṣ! Duqqez s usřiwřew, sɣuyy s řefraḥet, \add a cem\add* tenni war issinen řewjeɛ n tarwa, maɣar tarwa n tenni di semḥen d aṭṭas x iḥenjiren n tenni ɣar iǧa weryaz, iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 54:1 \xt Gal. 4:27\x*
\v 2 Egg ttasiɛ i iqiḍan nnem u ejj ad bezzɛen arwaqat n tzeddiɣin nnem aṭṭas, war \add ten\add* menneɛ. Szuggar timurar nnem uca ziyyar řewtad!
\v 3 Maɣar cem ad tiriwed ɣar yefus u ɣar uzeřmaḍ uca zzariɛet nnem ad tᵉṭṭef řegnus d tasɣart uca nitni ad sszedɣen tineddam yareddǧen.”
\b
\m 
\v 4 “War tteggʷed ca, maɣar war tseḍḥid u war ttwassbarrqed ca, maɣar war tᵉttwafeḍḥed. Ad tᵉttud řefḍiḥet n temẓi nnem, war tᵉtteɛqiřed x řeḥcumiyyet n iseggʷusa nnem am tajjač.
\v 5 Maɣar aryaz nnem d wenni cem iggin, ‘SIDI n řɛeskarat’ d Isem nnes, uca Amqeddas n Israil d Amefdi nnem. Ad as řaɣan ‘AREBBI n marra tammurt’.
\v 6 Maɣar SIDI iřaɣa xam am i yict n temɣart i di ismeḥ \add weryaz nnes\add*, i dayes acḍan deg buḥbeř nnes, u \add am\add* temɣart n iseggʷusa n temẓi, waxxa tuɣa-tt temmenḍar, iqqar AREBBI nnem.
\v 7 \add Mɣir\add* tazeḥziḥt semḥeɣ dayem, \add maca\add* s arreḥmet tameqqrant ad cem ssmuneɣ \add ɣari\add*.
\v 8 Umi ggiɣ aduqqez n weɣḍab inu ad isfi, aqa ssnuffareɣ zzayem aɣembub inu i yict tzeḥziḥt \add waha\add*, \add maca\add* s tmexsiwt icuwwaren n řebda ad ayi tezziǧzed, iqqar SIDI, Amefdi nnem.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Maɣar wa ad yiři i Necc \add am\add* wussan n Nuḥ umi jjuǧeɣ aqa aman n Nuḥ ɛemmarṣ war ssfiyen tammurt. Ammu i jjuǧeɣ \add řexxu\add*, aqa ɛemmarṣ war tteggeɣ ad xam idduqqez weɣḍab inu u war cem ttɛiqibeɣ \add ɛad\add*. \x ◘ \xo 54:9 \xt Amz. 9:11\x*
\v 10 Maɣar idurar ad dewřen ɣar uɣezdis u tiwririn ad nnhezzent, \add maca\add* tamexsiwt inu icewwaren ɛemmarṣ ad xam tḥeyyed uca Řɛahd n řehna inu war ittenhezzi ɛemmarṣ, iqqar SIDI, wenni umi tezziǧzed.”
\b
\m 
\v 11 “\add A, cem\add* tenni ittwaḥṣaren, tenni iqeṭṭeb usemmiḍ, tenni nhřa afewwej! Xzar, Necc ad quwwareɣ iẓra nnem \add iɣřan\add* s \add ict n tma\add* tabarcant uca ad ggeɣ dsas nnem x tyaqutin n ṣaffir.
\v 12 Necc ad ggeɣ řekwaza nnem i tfuct zeg ukristal, uřa d tiwwura nnem n řeɛqaq izeggwaɣen d marra řeḥyuḍ nnem i d am innḍen zeg iẓra iɣřan. \x ◘ \xo 54:12 \xt Asa. 22:19-21\x*
\v 13 Marra iḥenjiren nnem ad iřin d imeḥḍaren n SIDI uca řehna n iḥenjiren nnem ad yiři d ameqqran. \x ◘ \xo 54:13 \xt Yḥ. 6:45\x*
\v 14 Cem ad tiřid tarekkned s tsegda. Ad tiřid tᵉttaggʷejed x řeḥṣaret, maɣar war \add din\add* min zi ɣa teggʷeded, uřa x unexřiɛ, minzi war dd ɣarem ittikkwiḍ ca.
\v 15 Xzar, ad ssmunen, \add maca aya\add* war iǧi zzayi. Wi xam i ɣa issmunen, ad zzayem iwḍa.
\v 16 Xzar, Necc xeřqeɣ-dd amziř wenni ittsuḍen tirjin n tmessi u issuffuɣ-dd ict n řqecɛet i řxedmet nnes. \add Ammu\add* i dd-xeřqeɣ ɛawed amteḥḥay maḥend ad yareddeǧ.
\v 17 Kuř řesnaḥ nni ittwaggen ḍidd nnem, war ittiweḍ, uca kuř iřes nni xam i dd ɣa igeɛɛden di ddeɛwet, ad t tḥekmed cem. Ta d tasɣart n imsexxaren n SIDI uca tasegda nsen teffeɣ-dd zzayi, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”
\b
\b
\c 55
\s1 Asem-dd ɣar waman
\m 
\v 1 “A, marra inni iffuden, \bd asem-dd\bd* ɣar waman, wenni war ɣar ǧint tenɛacin, \bd asem-dd\bd*, sɣem, ccem, \add wah,\add* \bd asem-dd\bd* uca sɣem binu d uɣi, břa tinɛacin u břa ttaman. \x ◘ \xo 55:1 \xt Yḥ. 7:37,38; Asa. 22:17, 20\x*
\v 2 Mayemmi twezznem nnuqart i min war iǧin d aɣrum u \add mayemmi\add* tjehdem i min war ijjiwnen? Sřem-dd ɣari mliḥ, ccem min icnan uca ejj řeɛmar nwem ad iɣebba tadunt.
\v 3 Wcem amezzuɣ uca \bd asem-dd\bd* ɣari, sřem, \add xenni\add* ad iddar řeɛmar nwem, \add maɣar\add* Necc ad akidwem ggeɣ ijj n Řɛahd i řebda, timegga n tmexsiwt n řaman icewwaren n Dawud. \x ◘ \xo 55:3 \xt Řex. 13:34\x*
\b
\m 
\v 4 Xzar, ggiɣ t d acehhad i ccuɛub, d řḥakem, d bab n řumur i ccuɛub.
\v 5 Xzar, ad třaɣid ijj n řgens i war tessined, u řgens i war cek issinen ad ɣarek dd-yas di ṭṭweɛ n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, u di ṭṭweɛ n Umqeddas n Israil, minzi Netta issɛuǧa cek.”
\b
\m 
\v 6 “Arzum x SIDI řami Netta ittejja ixef nnes ad ittwaf, řaɣam as řami dd-yudes Netta.
\v 7 Ejj aɛeffan ad ismeḥ deg webrid nnes uca aryaz n řɣecc deg ixarriṣen nnes. Ejj i-t ad dd-idweř ɣar SIDI, \add xenni\add* Netta ad as izziǧez, u ɣar AREBBI nneɣ, maɣar Netta iɣeffar aṭṭas n twařawin.
\b
\m 
\v 8 Maɣar ixariṣṣen inu war ǧin am yixariṣṣen nwem u ibriden inu war ǧin am yibriden nwem, iqqar SIDI.
\v 9 Maɣar am mammec uɛřan ijenwan x temmurt, ammu i yuɛřan ibriden inu x ibriden nwem u ixarriṣen inu x ixarriṣen nwem.
\v 10 Maɣar am mammec i dd-ihekkwa wenẓar d wedfeř zeg ujenna u war ɣares dd-iddikkwiř ca, maca issuffa tammurt d amezwaru uca ittarra i-tt ad tewc řɣiǧet, ad tawi aɣemmuy uca \add awarni as\add* ittic zzariɛet i wenni iẓarrɛen d weɣrum i wenni ittetten,
\v 11 ammu i ɣa yiři uřa d awař i dd-itteffɣen zeg uqemmum inu. War dd ɣari iddikkwiř ixwa, maca ad yegg min xseɣ u ad yaweḍ \add marra\add* min ɣar t ssekkeɣ.”
\b
\m 
\v 12 “Maɣar ad teffɣem s řefraḥet uca ad kenniw ssqebbḍen di řehna. Idurar d tewririn ad dduqqzen s usřiwřew zzat i wudem nwem u marra ticejjura n yeyyar ad wtent camxa s ifassen. \x ◘ \xo 55:12 \xt 1 Im. 16:33\x*
\v 13 Deg wemcan n usennan ad teɣmi \add tcejjart n\add* umerzi, deg wemcan n tzeggʷart ad teɣmi tcejjart n tariḥant. Aya ad yiři i SIDI, i \add ccan n\add* Yisem \add nnes\add*, i řeɛřamet n řebda i war imeḥḥin ɛemmarṣ.” \f ◼ \fr 55:13 \fk amerzi\ft - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*
\b
\b
\c 56
\s1 Lwuɛud i wenni yarezzun tasegda uca ad tuben
\m 
\v 1 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ḥḍam řḥeqq uca ggem tasegda, minzi asenjem inu yudes-dd, ad dd-yas deɣya, uca tasegda inu \add tiweḍ-dd\add* ḥima ad tᵉttwassargeb.
\v 2 Sseɛd n weryaz nni itteggen ammu uřa d mmis n bnadem nni imennɛen di man aya, wenni iḥeṭṭan ass n ssebt ḥima war ittwassɛiǧit, d wenni iḥeṭṭan afus nnes ařami war ittegg zi marra min war iḥřin.
\v 3 War ttejji abarrani wenni iqqnen ɣar SIDI ad yini: ‘SIDI iɛzeř ayi qaɛ x řgens nnes!’, uca war ttejji wenni umi ttwaddzen imeǧařen ad yini: ‘Xzar, necc d tacejjart yuẓɣen!’ \f ◼ \fr 56:3 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*
\v 4 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI x \add imsexxaren\add* inni umi ttwaddzen imeǧařen, inni iḥeṭṭan ussan inu n ssebt u ttixḍaren min iǧan i arḍa inu u ttᵉṭṭfen di Řɛahd inu:
\v 5 Necc ad asen ggeɣ amcan di Taddart inu u jar řeḥyuḍ inu uca ad asen wceɣ isem ḥsen x \add yisem\add* n iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin. Kuř ijjen zzaysen ad as wceɣ isem n řebda nni ɛemmarṣ war imeḥḥin.
\b
\m 
\v 6 Ibarraniyyen nni i ɣa iqqnen ɣar SIDI ḥima ad as sexxaren u ḥima ad xsen Isem n SIDI, ḥima ad iřin d imsexxaren nnes - marra inni iḥeṭṭan ass n ssebt ḥima war ittwassɛiǧit, uřa d inni imennɛen di Řɛahd inu -
\v 7 ad ten awyeɣ \add ɛawed\add* ɣar wedrar inu iqeddsen u ad ten ssefraḥeɣ di Taddart inu n tẓaǧit. Tiɣarṣa nsen n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣa nsen nneɣni ad iřint i arḍa inu x uɛalṭar inu, maɣar Taddart inu ad as řaɣan Taddart n tẓaǧit i marra řegnus.’” \x ◘ \xo 56:7 \xt Mt. 21:13; Mk. 11:17; Lk. 19:46\x*
\b
\m 
\v 8 “Sidi inu, SIDI, wenni d issmunan inni x yuẓẓřen n Israil, iqqar: ‘Necc ad ɣares dd-ssmuneɣ ktar x yinni dd-ittwassmunen ɣares \add ɛad\add*.’”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Marra řewḥuc n řexřa, asem-dd i macca, \add wah,\add* marra řmař n wezɣar! \f ◼ \fr 56:9 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\v 10 Iɛessasen nnes ddarɣřen marra, war ssinen walu. Marra nitni d iṭan ibekmen, war zemmaren ad zun, ṭṭsen, zzřen, ttexsen anudem.
\v 11 Iṭan-a arjfen ař ṭṭarf, war ssinen tayawant. Nitni d imeksawen war ifehhmen, kuř ijjen \add zzaysen\add* iḍeffar abrid nnes, kuř ijj yarezzu tizi nnes, ɛad wenni d aneggar zzaysen.
\v 12 \add Qqaren\add*: ‘Asettiw-dd, ad dd-awyeɣ binu, ad nescar s ccrab. Am wass-a ammu i ɣa yiři uřa d tiwecca, \add ad yiři ɛad\add* d ameqqran d icnan \add xas\add*!’”
\b
\b
\c 57
\m 
\v 1 “Ittwahellek umsegged uca war din uřa d ijj wi t ittkessin ɣar wuř. Iryazen daysen tamexsiwt icewwaren mmeksin, břa ma iḥeṭṭa uřa d ijj aqa amsegged immeksi qbeř i dd ɣa yas \add ass n\add* lmuṣiba. \x ◘ \xo 57:1 \xt Izhd. 12:2; Mixa 7:2\x*
\v 2 Netta ad dd-yadef di řehna, ad arreyḥen nitni di qamat nsen \add deg imeḍřan\add*, \add kuř ijj\add* wenni yuyuren abrid nnes iseggmen.”
\b
\m 
\v 3 “Qarrbem-dd da, \add a kenniw\add* iḥenjiren n tbezgiwt, tarwa n yinni izennan u n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř!
\v 4 Wi zi testehezzam ammu, wi x tcarragem aqemmum u wi ɣar tjebbdem iřes ɣar barra? Ma war teǧim d iḥenjiren n uɛeddi, tarwa n řɣecc? \f ◼ \fr 57:4 \fk tarwa\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzariɛet’.\f*
\v 5 \add Kenniw\add* inni itthajen ɣar tcejjura n l’aṣnam, sadu kuř tacejjart tazizawt, \add kenniw\add* inni iɣarrṣen i iḥenjiren imeẓyanen di teɣzurin, swadday di tezziyin n řejruf. \f ◼ \fr 57:5 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*
\v 6 Tasɣart nnem ɣar iẓra iyuydan n teɣzurin. Aqa din tasɣart i d am dd-yekkaren. Uřa i nitni tzeǧɛed asen tawhibt n useyyeb, twehhbed tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*. Ma Necc ad qqimeɣ sqareɣ x man aya?”
\b
\m 
\v 7 “X wedrar yuɛřan d ittwassgeɛɛden tessud qama nnem. Uřa dinni tgeɛɛded ḥima ad twehhbed taɣarṣt.
\v 8 Awarni tewwart d řeḍruf nnes \add ɣar iɣezdisen nnes\add* teggid řeɛřamet nnem n řidaret, \add ‘mzuza nnem’\add*, maɣar cem tenɛezřed xafi d taɛaryant u tgeɛɛded dinni sennej. Tɛedřed i yixef nnem qama d tmiriwt uca tɛahded ixef nnem ak-d ca zzaysen. Tettexsed tassut nsen, teẓrid taryast \add nsen\add*.
\v 9 Ak-d zzect truḥed ɣar ujeǧid uca tarnid aṭṭas di řeɛṭur ittfuḥen nnem. Tessekked imsexxaren nnem ɣar řaggʷaj uca tesswaḍɛed ixef nnem ař řaxart.
\v 10 Zi ssibbet n waṭṭas n imsagaren nnem tuḥřed, \add maca\add* ɛemmarṣ war tennid: ‘War din iqqim řayas!’ Tufid jjehd n jdid i tudart. X uya war teḥřiced.
\v 11 Man wen zi tessḥissfed u teggʷeded aqa cem tessxarrqed xafi u war d ayi tidared, war d ayi teggid ɣar wuř nnem? Ma war tuɣi Necc sseɣdeɣ zeg wecḥař uya, \add ařami\add* cem war zzayi teggʷided ca \add ɛad\add*?” \x ◘ \xo 57:11 \xt Ica. 42:14\x*
\b
\m 
\v 12 “Necc ad ɛawdeɣ x tsegda nnem d tmegga nnem: war cem neffɛen ca.
\v 13 Xmi ɣa třaɣid, ejj xenni agraw nnem \add i ɣarem tessmuned\add* ad cem ifekk. Asemmiḍ ad ten yawi marra, ijj n usuḍi ad ten iksi, \add maca\add* wenni ɣari yarekkwařen, ad iwart tammurt d wedrar inu iqeddsen d tasɣart.” \x ◘ \xo 57:13 \xt Izhd. 34:9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 “Ad yini: ‘Sgeɛɛdem, sgeɛɛdem \add abrid\add*, ksem min issenqraḍen zeg webrid n řgens inu!’
\v 15 Maɣar ammu i iqqar wenni yuɛřan u wenni ittwassgeɛɛden, wenni izeddɣen di řebda, wenni umi qqaren aqa Amqeddas \add i iǧa\add*: ‘Necc zeddɣeɣ di řuɛřa u deg weqdas u ɣar wenni umi ittwarẓ buḥbeř u ɣar umwaḍeɛ n buḥbeř, maḥend ad arreɣ buḥbeř n imwaḍɛen d wuř n inni ittwarẓin ɣar Tudart!’
\v 16 Maɣar Necc war ttemcubbuceɣ i řebda u war tteggeɣ ad idduqqez weɣḍab inu břa qeṭṭu, minzi \add xenni\add* iři ad yarxu \add kuř\add* buḥbeř zi zzat n wudem inu, řeɛmur nni ggiɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 57:16 \xt Izhd. 103:9; Ɛbr. 12;9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 17 “Necc ffugmeɣ x řmuɛṣiyyet n meẓri nnes deg warbeḥ uca wtiɣ \add řgens\add*. Necc nnuffareɣ uca \add xenni\add* idduqqez weɣḍab inu. \add Maca\add* řgens yuyur, idweř ɣar webrid n wuř nnes.”
\b
\m 
\v 18 “Necc ẓriɣ ibriden nnes, ad t ssgenfiɣ, ad t ssqebbḍeɣ, ad as ssfewwjeɣ uca ad as wceɣ ifewwajen, i netta u i yinni iceḍnen nnes.
\v 19 Necc ad dd-xeřqeɣ řɣiǧet n iyencicen nsen. ‘Řehna, řehna i yinni iggʷejen u i yinni yudsen’, iqqar SIDI.
\v 20 Maca iɛeffanen ggin am řebḥar innhewřen i war izemmaren ad yarsa, uca aman nnes iwyen-dd abaryuḍ d ubeǧaɛ.
\v 21 Iɛeffanen war ɣar iǧi řehna!, iqqar AREBBI inu.” \x ◘ \xo 57:21 \xt Ica. 48:22\x*
\b
\b
\c 58
\m 
\v 1 “Řaɣa s jjehd, war ttceṭṭar, ejj tmijja nnec ad tgeɛɛed am uyicc n icarri uca barreḥ i řgens inu iɛeddiyen nsen u i taddart n Yaɛqub ddnub nsen!
\v 2 Nitni arezzun xafi ass x wass uca iɛjeb asen tussna n ibriden inu, amecnaw \add ǧan d\add* řgens nni itteggen tasegda u war ittejji řḥeqq n AREBBI nnes. Nitni ttaren zzayi řeḥkamat iseggden, iɛjeb asen ad dd-qarrben ɣar AREBBI,
\v 3 \add maca nitni qqaren\add*: ‘Mayemmi nẓumm, uca Cek war t teẓrid? \add Mayemmi\add* nessecḍan buḥbeř nneɣ \add am\add* Cek war d as tḥekkared?’ Xzar, deg wass n uẓummi nwem, tarrim meẓri uca tzeyyarem aṭṭas marra ixeddamen nwem.
\v 4 Xzar, aẓummi nwem yiwi kenniw ɣar umcubbec d umenɣi, ɣar tiyyita s řpuniyyet s řeqsaḥet. War ttẓummem am tᵉtteggem ass-a, maḥend ad tᵉttwaseř tmijja nwem di řuɛřa!
\v 5 Ma wa d aẓummi nni ixḍareɣ Necc: ijj n wass nni di ɣa iɛeddeb bnadem řeɛmar nnes, wenni x i ɣa imeyyeř bnadem azeǧif nnes am uɣanim, u ad issars taxancet n wecḍan d yiɣɣeḍ am qama nnes? Ma teqqared i uya aẓummi, ma aya d ass i dd-yusin x řxaḍar i SIDI?”\x ◘ \xo 58:5 \xt Zak. 7:5\x*
\b
\m 
\v 6 “Ma war iǧi wa d aẓummi nni ixḍareɣ: afekki n iceddiyyen n řɣar, azeɛwaḍ n tesɣunin n zzayřet, anufseř i yinni ittwaḥṣaren, aqa ad tekksem qaɛ zzayřet?
\v 7 Ma war iǧi \add wa d aẓummi nni ixḍareɣ\add*, aqa ad tebḍid aɣrum nnec ak-d wenni iǧuzen uca ad tessidfed řmusakin nni ittwadarrcen ɣar taddart? Mařa cek teẓrid aɛaryan, ad t tessyarḍed u war tessnufared ixef nnec zeg wenni iǧan zeg weysum nnec? \x ◘ \xo 58:7 \xt Ḥiz. 18:7, 16; Mt. 25:35I\x*
\v 8 Xenni tafawt nnec ad dd-tenqar am tuffut n řḥař uca asgenfi nnec ad dd-yaweḍ deɣya, tasegda nnec ad ac tizwar uca aɛuǧi n SIDI ad yiři d aɣezdis nnec aneggaru.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Xenni ad třaɣid uca SIDI ad xak dd-yarr. Ad tesɣuyed ɣar twiza, \add uca xenni\add* ad yini Netta: ‘Xzar, aqa ayi da!’ Mařa \add nican\add* tekksed zzayret zi řwesṭ nnec, uřa d aceyyar s uḍaḍ d wawař aɛeffan,
\v 10 uca ad tarzmed řeɛmar nnec i wenni iǧuẓen u ad tessjjiwned řeɛmar iceḍnen! \add Xenni\add* ad dd-tenqar tfawt nnec di taǧest uca tubbarcent nnec ad tiři am ṭṭya n uziř.
\v 11 SIDI ad cek ittgewwad řebda u Netta ad issjjiwen řeɛmar nnec di jjwayeh yuẓɣen uca ad issejhed iɣsan nnec. Ad tdewřed am weḥwic ittwassun u am řɛunṣar ittazzřen n waman i war ttɣarran aman nnes ɛemmarṣ.
\v 12 Inni zzayek \add dd-iffɣen\add* ad ɛawden asbeddi i řxirbat n wecḥař uya, ad ɛedřen dsusa n jjiřat iɛdun uca ad ac qqaren: ‘Wenni iɛeddřen tareẓẓitin, d wenni ittarran izubaq ad daysen uyuren!’”
\b
\m 
\v 13 “Mařa \add xenni\add* tqeřbed aḍar nnec x \add wass n\add* ssebt, x taggit min d ac itteɛjiben deg wass inu iqeddsen, uca ad třaɣid i \add wass n\add* ssebt: ‘Ṭṭibet!’, i min iǧan iqeddsen i SIDI: ‘Aɛuǧi!’, uca ad tweqqared \add ass n ssebt\add* am war tḍeffareḍ ibriden nnec, war tᵉtteggid min d ac itteɛjiben u war tessiwiřid \add ɣar\add* tizi \add nnec\add*,
\v 14 xenni ad tafed řefraḥet nnec di SIDI u Necc ad cek jjeɣ ad tnedhed tiwa i řegɛudi n temmurt. Ad cek ssecceɣ zi tesɣart n babac Yaɛqub, minzi aqemmum n SIDI issiweř.”
\b
\b
\c 59
\s1 Aɣiř n SIDI AREBBI war iǧi d aqudad ařami war izemmar ad ifekk
\m 
\v 1 “Xzar, afus n SIDI war iǧi d aquḍaḍ ḥima ad issenjem, amezzuɣ nnes war idduhcar aqa Netta war ittesři, \x ◘ \xo 59:1 \xt Řxř. 11:23; Ica. 50:2\x*
\v 2 maca řmuɛṣiyyet nwem d min ittemsebḍan jar awem d AREBBI nwem, uca ddnub nwem řeḥḥfen zzaywem aɣembub nnes, aqa Netta war \add i d awem\add* ittesři.
\v 3 Maɣar ttwassxemmjen ifassen nwem s idammen, iḍewḍan nwem s řmuɛṣiyyet, iyencicen nwem ssxarriqen, iřes nwem inṭeq s min war iḥrin.
\v 4 Uřa d ijj issmuna s tsegda uca uřa d ijj ittwacarreɛ s řḥeqq. Marra nitni ttɛemmden x min iǧan baṭeř uca qqaren ixarriqen. Aqa kessin s ddeyset n tuɛeffna u ttarwen-dd řmuɛṣiyyet. \x ◘ \xo 59:4 \xt Ayub 15:35; Izhd. 7:15\x*
\v 5 Ḥebḍen x tmeǧařin n třefsa u zeṭṭen axmař n qundɛa. Wenni iccen zi tmeǧařin nsen, ad immet, u xmi ittareẓẓa ijj icten, tᵉtteffeɣ-dd zzayes ict n tfiɣart.
\v 6 Ixmaren nsen war dd-usin i werruḍ uca war zemmaren ad arḍen ixef nsen s min ggin \add ifassen nsen\add*. Min ggin aqa d řexdayem n řmuɛṣiyyet uřa d řxedmet n řexcunet n ifassen nsen. \x ◘ \xo 59:6 \xt Ayub 8:14, 15\x*
\v 7 Iḍaren nsen ttazzřen ɣar řɣar u nitni ttqeǧiqen maḥend ad ssizzřen idammen imezdagen. Ixarriṣen nsen d ixarriṣen \add ccuren\add* ak-d řmuɛṣiyyet, areddeǧ d ukehheḍ aqa aten x ibriden nsen iwaṭan. \x ◘ \xo 59:7 \xt Awřn. 1:16; Rum. 3:15\x*
\v 8 Abrid n řehna war t ssinen u řatarat nsen war xasent walu n řḥeqq. Nitni ssfarraɣen izubaq nsen i yixef nsen, marra inni daysen igguren, war ssinen řehna.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “X uya ittɣima řḥeqq iggʷej xaneɣ u tasegda war dd aneɣ dd-tᵉttikkwiḍ. Neccin nettraja tafawt, \add maca\add* xzar, aqa din ṭṭřam, nraja tissiqt n tfawt, \add maca\add* nuyur di taǧest.
\v 10 Nettfafa am yiḍarɣařen ak-d řḥiḍ u nᵉttemhafa \add ssa ɣar da\add*, axmi war ɣarneɣ ǧint tiṭṭawin. Nweṭṭa di ṭṭḥa n uziř axmi di tbambast x yinni iddaren axmi x imettan.
\v 11 Neccin nzehhar marra am ddubat u nettgergur am ttgergurent tedbirin, nettraja řḥeqq, \add maca\add* war dd-yusi, \add nettraja\add* asenjem, \add maca\add* iggʷej xaneɣ.
\v 12 Maɣar iɛeddiyen nneɣ aṭṭas qibač Cek u ddnub nneɣ cehhden xaneɣ, minzi iɛeddiyen nneɣ aqa aten ɣarneɣ u řmuɛṣiyyat nneɣ aqa nessen i-tent:
\v 13 aɛeddi d uxarreq x SIDI, uca aḥeyyed zi AREBBI nneɣ, řhard x ddeǧ d uɣewweɣ, aḥaweř d usuffeɣ n ixarriqen zeg wuř.
\v 14 Ittwexxar řḥeqq ɣar ḍeffar, uca tᵉttɣima tsegda ɣar řaggʷaj, maɣar tidett tennedref deg wazzay uca min iseggmen war izemmar ad dd-yadef.
\v 15 Tbeṭṭeř tidett u wenni iḥeyyden x tuɛeffna idweř d takeccaḍt. Aya iẓra i-t SIDI uca tuɣa-t d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin nnes aqa war din iǧi řḥeqq.
\v 16 Iẓra aqa war din uřa d ijjen u Netta tuɣa ittebhet řami uřa d ijj iksi s řmeɛruf i uceffaɛ. \add Xenni\add* yiwi uɣiř nnes d asenjem i Netta uca tasegda nnes tuɣa d aɛemmed nnes. \x ◘ \xo 59:16 \xt Ica. 63:5\x*
\v 17 Issyarḍ Ixef nnes tasegda am warruḍ n wuzzař uca issars lkask n usenjem x uzeǧif nnes. Netta yarḍ arruḍ n wexřaf uca iřeḥḥef s tusmi \add iqeddsen\add* am iřeḥḥef s useřham. \x ◘ \xo 59:17 \xt Afa. 6:17; 1 Ts. 5:8\x*
\v 18 Am mammec sdahǧent tmegga \add nsen\add*, ammu i ɣa ixřef i iɣrimen nnes s wesɛar, i řɛedyan nnes min d asen dd-yusin. Tigzirin ad tent iwc řexřef nsent i isdaḥǧen.”
\b
\m 
\v 19 “\add Xenni\add* ad ggʷeden zeg Yisem n SIDI zi manis tɣeǧi tfuct, uca aɛuǧi nnes zi manis dd-tneqqar tfuct. Maɣar ad dd-yas am yeɣzar iḥṣaren, asemmiḍ n SIDI ad t iɛarn.
\v 20 Ad dd-yas Umefdi zi Ṣihyun, i yinni i ɣa ituben zeg iɛeddiyen \add nsen\add* zi Yaɛqub, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 59:20 \xt Ica. 10:21, 22; Rum. 11:26\x*
\b
\m 
\v 21 “Wa d Řɛahd inu akidsen, iqqar SIDI. Arruḥ inu, wenni xak \add iǧan\add*, d wawařen inu nni ggiɣ deg uqemmum nnec, war xak ttḥeyyiden ca zeg uqemmum nnec, war iǧi zeg uqemmum n tarwa nnec uřa zeg uqemmun n tarwa n tarwa nnec, zi řexxu ař i řebda, iqqar SIDI.”
\b
\b
\c 60
\s1 Aɛuǧi n Ṣihyun deg wussan ineggura
\m 
\v 1 “Kkar, egg tfawt maɣar tafawt nnem tusa-dd u aɛuǧi n SIDI yareqq tiwa nnem.
\v 2 Maɣar xzar, taǧest ad tdeř tammurt u aseynu ibbumbes \add ad ideř\add* ccuɛub, \add maca\add* tiwa nnem ad igeɛɛed SIDI u aɛuǧi nnes ad dd-iḍhar tiwa nnem.
\v 3 Řegnus ad ɣarem dd-asen u ijeǧiden ɣar tissiqt n řefjar nnem.”
\b
\m 
\v 4 “Sgeɛɛed tiṭṭawin nnem, xzar da d diha, xzar, marra nitni munen, ttasen-dd ɣarem. Iḥenjiren nnem ad dd-asen zi řaggʷaj, yessim ttwaksint i-dd x tmeṣṣaḍin.
\v 5 Xenni ad t tẓared u ad tsiqsiqed uca uř nnem ad inhezz s uweqqar u ad innurzem aṭṭas, maɣar agřa n řebḥar ad idweř ɣarem, afeyyec n řegnus ad ɣarem dd-yas. \x ◘ \xo 60:5 \xt Izhd. 34:6; Asa. 21:26\x*
\v 6 Ijj n ubarru n iřeɣman ad cem ideř, iřeɣman imeẓyanen zi Midyan d Ɛiyfa. Marra ad dd-asen zi Caba. Ad awyen ureɣ d jjawi, uca ad beccaren s wawařen n ccan i SIDI.
\v 7 Marra uǧi n Qidar ad ɣarem nnjarwen. Icarriyyen n Nabayut ad iřin i tsexxart nnem. Ad ten ssgeɛɛden s arḍa x uɛalṭar inu u Necc ad ssɛuǧeɣ Taddart n uɛuǧi inu s tidett.”
\b
\m 
\v 8 “Man ina inni dd-iṭṭawen ɣar dinni am yiseynuten, am tedbirin ɣar řekwaza nsent?
\v 9 \add Wah,\add* tigzirin ad ayi řajant, uca iɣarruba n Tarcic ad iřin d imezwura maḥend ad awyen iḥenjiren nnem zi řaggʷaj, ak-d nnuqart nsen d wureɣ nsen, i Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI nnem, i Umqeddas n Israil, minzi Netta issɛuǧa cem.
\v 10 Ibarraniyyen ad bnan řeḥyuḍ nnem uca ijeǧiden ad am sexxaren, maɣar deg uduqqez n weɣḍab inu wtiɣ cem, \add maca\add* di arḍa inu tezziǧed ayi. \x ◘ \xo 60:10 \xt Ica. 49:23\x*
\v 11 Tiwwura nnem ad qqiment řebda arzment. Ass d ǧiřet war ttbelliɛent maḥend ad ɣarem ssidfen agřa n řegnus uca ad \add din\add* ssqebbḍen uřa d ijeǧiden nsen nni dd-iwyen.
\v 12 Maɣar řgens d tgeldit nni war ttexsen ad am sexxaren, ad hellken, uca řegnus \add nni\add* ad ttwaredǧen qaɛ.”
\b
\m 
\v 13 “Acuwwar n Lubnan ad ɣarem dd-yas, tacejjart n umerzi, tacejjart n ddulb d tcejjart n tengelt munent, ḥima ad zewwqen amcan n Zzawect inu Iqeddsen, uca amcan n iḍaren inu ad t ssɛuǧeɣ. \f ◼ \fr 60:13 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’). \fk amerzi\ft - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*
\v 14 Iḥenjiren n yinni tuɣa cem iḥeṣṣaren ad ɣarem dd-asen s uwaḍeɛ, ad aḍaren ɣar iḍaren nnem marra inni zzayem istehzan, uca ad am řaɣan: ‘Tandint n SIDI, Ṣihyun n Umqeddas n Israil’.”
\b
\m 
\v 15 “I umi, aqa cem tuɣa texřid d tᵉttwacarhed ařami uřa d ijj war d xam issijj, ad cem ggeɣ d řɛezz ittduman d \add řɛunṣar n\add* řefraḥet zi jjiř ař jjiř. \x ◘ \xo 60:15 \xt Ica. 49:19; 54:1, 6, 7\x*
\v 16 Ad tᵉṭṭḍed aɣi n řegnus u ad tᵉṭṭḍed ɣar iffan n ijeǧiden. Ad tessned aqa Necc d SIDI, Amsenjam nnem d Amefdi nnem, Amzemmar n Yaɛqub.” \x ◘ \xo 60:16 \xt Ica. 43:3\x*
\b
\m 
\v 17 “Deg wemcan n nnḥas ad awyeɣ ureɣ, deg wemcan n wuzzař nnuqart, deg wemcan n ukeccuḍ nnḥas, deg wemcan n yeẓra uzzař. Necc ad ggeɣ řehna d iweqqafen nnem uřa d tasegda d imzeyyaren nnem.
\v 18 War ssiwřen ɛad x lɛunf di temmurt nnem, uřa x wareddeǧ d uxarreb di jjwayeh nnem. Řeḥyuḍ nnem ad asen inin: ‘Asenjem!’, u i tewwura nnem: ‘Taṣebbiḥt!’.
\b
\m 
\v 19 War tᵉttiři ɛad tfuct d tafawt nnem deg uziř u taziri war d am tᵉttic ɛad tissiqt nnes, \add maca\add* SIDI ad am yiři d tafawt n řebda, uca AREBBI nnem ad yiři d řehzuṭ nnem icnan qaɛ.
\v 20 Tafuct nnem war tɣeǧi ɛad u taziri nnem war tneqqeṣ, maɣar SIDI ad yiři d tafawt nnem n řebda uca ussan n wecḍan nnem ad qḍan.
\v 21 Řgens nnem aqa aten marra d imseggaden, nitni ad ṭṭfen tammurt d řwart i řebda: taɣeddut i ẓẓuɣ, řxedmet n ifassen inu, aqa-ten i řɛezz \add inu\add*! \x ◘ \xo 60:21 \xt Ica. 29:23; 45:11; Mt. 15:13\x*
\v 22 Ameẓyan qaɛ ad idweř d ařef u amuqřiř qaɛ ad idweř d řgens ijhed, Necc, SIDI, ad t-i-dd-nedheɣ deɣya xmi dd ɣa yaweḍ řḥař.”
\b
\b
\c 61
\s1 Aseggʷas n usřiwřew i SIDI
\m 
\v 1 “Arruḥ n Sidi, SIDI, xafi minzi idhen ayi SIDI inu maḥend ad awyeɣ řexbar aṣebḥan i imwaḍɛen. Netta issekk ayi-dd, maḥend ad cefneɣ inni umi ittwarẓ uř nsen, maḥend ad barrḥeɣ s třelli i imeḥbas d unufseř zi řeḥbes i yinni icarfen, \x ◘ \xo 61:1 \xt Lk. 4:17, 18, 19, 20\x*
\v 2 maḥend ad barrḥeɣ aseggʷas n arḍa i SIDI d wass n wexřaf n AREBBI nneɣ, maḥend ad ssfewwjeɣ marra inni iceḍnen, \x ◘ \xo 61:2 \xt Ica. 63:4\x*
\v 3 maḥend ad ggeɣ i yinni iceḍnen di Ṣihyun aqa ad asen wcen řehzuṭ deg wemcan n yiɣɣeḍ, zzect n řefraḥet deg wemcan n wecḍan, arruḍ n usemɣar deg wemcan n buḥbeř ittwarẓen, ḥima ad asen řaɣan ‘Ticejjura n yigg n tsegda!’, tinni ittwaẓẓun zi SIDI, i řɛezz \add nnes\add*!”
\b
\m 
\v 4 “Ad ssbedden řxirbat n wecḥař uya, ad ɛedřen řebniyyat ihedmen n \add jjiřat\add* i d \add aneɣ\add* izwaren, uca ad ssbedden ɛawed tineddam ixarrben nni tuɣa ihedmen zi jjiř ař jjiř \add nneɣni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 61:4 \xt Ica. 58:12\x*
\v 5 Ibarraniyyen ad iřin wejden ḥima ad arewsen uǧi nwem, uca iɣriben ad iřin d ifeǧaḥen nwem d ayt n tzayart nwem.
\v 6 \add Maca\add* ad kenniw řaɣan ‘Ikehhanen n SIDI!’ uca ad awem inin ‘Imsexxaren n AREBBI nneɣ!’. Ad teccem agřa n řegnus uca ad tfeyycem s uɛuǧi nsen.\x ◘ \xo 61:6 \xt 1 Bṭ. 2:5, 9; Asa. 1:6; 5:10\x*
\v 7 Deg wemcan n useḍḥi nwem, \add ad din iřint\add* tnayen n tseqqar, u \add deg wemcan n\add* řefḍiḥet, ad sřiwřewen nitni x tesɣart nsen. S uya ad ṭṭfen tnayen n tseqqar di temmurt nsen, řefraḥet ittduman ad ɣarsen tiři.
\v 8 Maɣar Necc, SIDI, ttexseɣ řḥeqq, carrheɣ tukkarḍa s lɛunf. Necc ad asen wceɣ řmunet di řaman, ad kidsen qqneɣ ijj n Řɛahd ittduman.
\v 9 Zzariɛet nsen ad tedweř tᵉttwassen jar řegnus uca tarwa nsen di řwesṭ n řegnus. Marra wi ten i ɣa iẓaren, ad qenɛen aqa ina d zzariɛet i ibarek SIDI.”
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Farḥeɣ aṭṭas di SIDI, řeɛmar inu ifarḥ di AREBBI inu minzi Netta issyarḍ ayi arruḍ n usenjem, u s useřham n tsegda i d ayi iřeḥḥef, am muřay i iqqnen areẓẓet n ukehhan u am tesřit nni isswejden ixef nnes s řehzuṭ nnes.
\v 11 Maɣar am temmurt tᵉttejja aɣemmuy nnes ad dd-iffeɣ u am weḥwic issɣemmay min dayes izarrɛen, ammu i dd isseɣmay Sidi inu, SIDI, tasegda d ccan zzat \add i tiṭṭawin\add* n marra řegnus.”
\b
\b
\c 62
\s1 Cḍaret n SIDI i yeǧis n Siḥyun
\m 
\v 1 “Di ṭṭweɛ n Ṣihyun war zemmareɣ ad sseɣdeɣ, di ṭṭweɛ n Urcalim war ttesqiriɣ, ař dd ɣa tenqar tsegda nnes am tissiqt u asenjem nnes am wesfeḍ yareqqen.
\v 2 Ad ẓaren řegnus tasegda nnem u marra ijeǧiden \add ad ẓaren\add* aɛuǧi nnem. Ad am řaɣan s yijj n yisem n jdid nni d am i ɣa igga uqemmum n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 62:2 \xt Ica. 65:15\x*
\v 3 Ad tiřid d ttaj icewwaren deg ufus n SIDI uřa d areẓẓet igellden deg ufus n AREBBI nnem.
\v 4 War d am qqaren ɛad ‘Tenni di semḥen!’ u war d as qqaren ɛad i temmurt nnem ‘Tammurt ixřan!’, maca ad am řaɣan ‘Řxaḍar inu!’, u tammurt nnem ‘Tanemřact!’, maɣar tusid-dd x řxaḍar n SIDI u tammurt nnem ad tᵉttwamřec.
\v 5 Maɣar am uɛezri imřec taɛzarect, ammu i kidem ɣa meřcen iḥenjiren nnem, uca am muřay ifarreḥ i tesřit, \add ammu\add* i d am ɣa ifarḥ AREBBI nnem.”
\b
\m 
\v 6 “\add A\add* Urcalim, ssbeddeɣ iɛessasen x řeḥyuḍ nnem nni war ssɣidin řebda, deg wass d ǧiřet. \add A\add* kenniw inni iɛeqqřen x SIDI, war ttareyyḥem!
\v 7 War ttareyyḥem di ṭṭweɛ nnes, ař dd issbedd Urcalim uca igga i-tt d aṣebbeḥ x temmurt.
\v 8 SIDI ijjuǧ ɣar ufus nnes afusi u ɣar uɣiř nnes ijehden: ‘Ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad wceɣ imendi nnem d macca i řɛedyan nnem, u ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad ssesweɣ ibarraniyyen binu nnem n jdid i x teksid tamara!
\v 9 Maɣar wi t ɣa issmunen, ad zzayes ccen u ad ssemɣaren SIDI, u wi ɣa iřeqḍen aḍiř, ad zzayes swen di řemraḥat n Zzawect inu Iqeddsen.’”
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Ɛdum, ɛdum zi tewwura uca swejdem i řgens abrid. Sgeɛɛdem, sgeɛɛdem abrid iwaṭan, kksem iẓra, sgeɛɛdem taɛeǧant i řegnus! \x ◘ \xo 62:10 \xt Ica. 40:3; 57:14\x*
\v 11 Xzar, SIDI igga ad sřen ař ṭṭarf n temmurt. Inim i yeǧis n Ṣihyun: ‘Xzar, asenjem nnem yusa-dd, xzar, řmunet nnes ɣares uca řexřaṣ nnes ɣar zzates.’
\v 12 Ad asen qqaren: ‘Řgens amqeddas, inni ittwafekken n SIDI!’, uca ad am qqaren: ‘Tenni x tuɣa arezzun!’ d ‘Tandint i war ittwajjen!’.” \f ◼ \fr 62:12 \fk inni ittwafekken\ft - niɣ ‘inni ittwafdin’. Xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*
\b
\b
\c 63
\s1 Řḥukm x Idum, řeɛdu amezwaru n Israyil
\m 
\v 1 “Min iɛna wenni dd-yusin zi Idum, zi Buṣra, deg warruḍ s uzzeggwaɣ yuǧřen, iɛuǧen deg warruḍ nnes, wenni igguren di jjehd nnes ameqqran?”
\m “D Necc, wenni issawařen di tsegda, d wenni izemmaren ad issenjem!”
\b
\m 
\v 2 “Mayemmi arruḍ nnec d azeggwaɣ u \add mayemmi\add* arruḍ nnec am werruḍ n wenni iɛeffsen x tsirt n uḍiř?” \x ◘ \xo 63:2 \xt Asa. 19:13\x*
\b
\m 
\v 3 “Necc weḥḥdi d wenni iɛefsen tasirt n binu u war din tuɣi uřa d ijj akidi zi řegnus. Ɛefseɣ xasen deg weɣḍab inu, řebzeɣ ten deg wesɛar inu. Idammen nsen ruccen x warruḍ inu, uca ssarṣuḍen marra arruḍ inu.
\v 4 Maɣar ass n wexřaf aqa-t ɣari deg wuř, u yusa-dd useggʷas i yinni ittwafekken s ufus inu.” \f ◼ \fr 63:4 \fk inni ittwafekken\ft - niɣ ‘inni ittwafdin’. Xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 63:4 \xt Ica. 61:2 \x*
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Necc xzareɣ \add ammu d wammu\add*, maca war \add din\add* tuɣi uřa d ijj i d ayi iwcin afus. Necc tuɣa ttbehteɣ, minzi uřa d ijjen war kidi ibedd. \add Ufiɣ\add* mɣir aɣiř inu i d ayi issnejmen uca asɛar inu tuɣa d aɛemmed inu. \x ◘ \xo 63:5 \xt Ica. 59:16\x*
\v 6 Necc ɛefseɣ x řegnus deg weɣḍab inu, Necc ssᵉscareɣ ten deg wesɛar inu uca ggiɣ idammen nsen ttazzřen ɣar temmurt.”
\b
\s1 Asemɣar d tkessit s řmeɛruf zzat i Arebbi
\m 
\v 7 “Necc xseɣ ad idareɣ timegga n tmexsiwt n SIDI, timegga iṣebḥen n SIDI, marra min i d aneɣ igga SIDI, uřa d řxir ameqqran i isscen i taddart n Israil ɛlaḥsab arreḥmet nnes d řemɣaret n tmexsiwt nnes icewwaren.
\v 8 Netta inna: ‘Nitni d řgens inu, iḥenjiren nni war issxarriqen!” Uca Netta idweř d Amsenjem i nitni.
\v 9 Di marra řeḥṣaret nsen tuɣa uřa d Netta ittwaḥṣar, uca lmalak n wudem nnes issenjem i-ten. Di tayri nnes d arḍa nnes ifekk i-ten. Netta issgeɛɛed i-ten uca yarbu ten di marra ussan n wecḥař uya.” \x ◘ \xo 63:9 \xt Aɛwd. 7:7, 8, 9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Nitni \add maca\add* ɣewwɣen uca ssceḍnen Arruḥ Iqeddsen nnes. \add Xas uca\add* idweř asen d řeɛdu i nitni, immneɣ akidsen. \x ◘ \xo 63:10 \xt Řxř. 14:11; Izhd. 78:57; 95:9-11\x*
\v 11 \add Waxxa amenni\add* iɛqeř x wussan n zzmanat n wecḥař uya, x Musa d řgens nnes. Mani iǧa wenni d asen dd-issgeɛɛden zi řebḥar ak-d imeksawen n wuǧi nnes? Mani iǧa wenni iggin Arruḥ nnes Iqeddsen di řwesṭ nsen, \f ◼ \fr 63:11 \fk imeksawen\ft - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*
\v 12 wenni iggin afus nnes ittseqsiqen aṭṭas ad yuyur ak-d Musa, wenni ibḍan aman zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen ḥima ad dd-yawi i Yixef nnes Isem i řebda, \f ◼ \fr 63:12 \fk zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzat i wudmawen nsen’.\f*
\v 13 wenni ten inedhen deg \add waman\add* innhewřen? Am uyis di řexřa war nnqarḍen ca, \x ◘ \xo 63:13 \xt Izhd. 105:37\x*
\v 14 am řmař nni dd-ihekkwan di teɣzurt, \add ammu\add* i issareyyeḥ i-ten Arruḥ n SIDI, ammu tnedhed řgens nnec maḥend ad dd-tawyed i Yixef nnec ijj n Isem ittseqsiqen aṭṭas.”
\b
\m 
\v 15 “Sijj zeg ujenna, u wařa zi Tzeddiɣt \add nnec\add* \add teccur s\add* tamqeddast nnec d tessiqt nnec! Mani teǧa tusmi nnec \add iqeddsen\add* u \add mani ǧant\add* tmegga nnec ijehden? Tessiggʷejed xafi řehnunect nnec d arreḥmet nnec. \x ◘ \xo 63:15 \xt Aɛwd. 26:15\x*
\v 16 Aqa Cek d Babatneɣ, maɣar Ibrahim war d aneɣ issin uca uřa d Israil war d aneɣ issin. Cek, \add a\add* SIDI, d Babatneɣ, Amefdi nneɣ, Isem nnec aqa-t zi řebda.
\v 17 \add A\add* SIDI, mayemmi i d aneɣ tejjid nᵉtteffeɣ zeg ibriden nnec, mayemmi tesseqseḥed uř nneɣ ařami war Cek neggʷed? Dweř-dd di ṭṭweɛ n imsexxaren nnec, \add di ṭṭweɛ n\add* tqebbař n tesɣart nnec.
\v 18 Řgens nnec iṭṭef i-tt d řwart mɣir cwayt n řweqt. Iɣrimen nneɣ ɛefsen x Zzawect nnec Iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 63:18 \xt Izhd. 74:7\x*
\v 19 Aqa nedweř am yinni i war x tḥekmed zi zzmanat n wecḥař uya u i x war ittwařaɣa Isem nnec. Mři tcarrged ijenwan, ḥima ad dd-tehwid, ad arjijen idurar zzat i wudem nnec.”
\b
\b
\c 64
\m 
\v 1 “\add Mři dd-tehwid,\add* am timessi tessareɣ tizgi u am tmessi tesstartar aman, maḥend ad ittwasscen Isem nnec i iɣrimen nnec, ḥima ad arjijen zzatek řegnus,
\v 2 umi teggid timesřayin issaggʷaden i war tent nriji ɛemmarṣ. Mři dd-tehwid \add ařami\add* arjijen idurar zzat i wudem nnec.”
\b
\m 
\v 3 “Zeg wecḥař uya ɛemmarṣ war \add t\add* sřin, řa d amezzuɣ war \add t\add* isři, uřa d tiṭṭ war \add t\add* teẓri, aqa ijj n arebbi nneɣni nhřa Cek, wenni itteggen ca di ṭṭweɛ n yinni xas ittrajan. \x ◘ \xo 64:3 \xt Izhd. 31:19, 20; 1 Kur. 2:9\x*
\v 4 Wenni ifarrḥen zi tsegda uca ad zzayes yegg, ad t teřqid Cek, inni xak itteɛqiřen deg ibriden nnec. Xzar, teffugmed, \add minzi\add* neccin nexḍa. Negga i-t \add ɛad\add* řebda, ma \add xenni\add* ad nejmen?
\v 5 Neccin marra am umexmuj, marra řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ am warruḍ ixeǧḍen deg idammen, neccin marra am tfart nissřaw, uca řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ tkessi aneɣ am usemmiḍ. \x ◘ \xo 64:5 \xt Izhd. 90:5, 6\x*
\v 6 Uřa d ijj war ittřiɣi Isem nnec, \add uřa d ijj\add* ittekkar ḥima ad dayek iṭṭef, maɣar Cek tessnuffared aɣembub nnec xaneɣ uca tejjid aneɣ ad nɣarq deg ufus n řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ.
\v 7 \add Maca\add* řexxu, \add a\add* SIDI, Cek d Babatneɣ, neccin d třaxt u Cek d bu-třaxt nneɣ, neccin marra d řxedmet n ifassen nnec.
\v 8 \add A\add* SIDI, war teggid ad idduqqez weɣḍab nnec ammu aṭṭas u war ttidar i řebda řmuɛṣiyyet. Aqa da, xzar, neccin marra d řgens nnec. \x ◘ \xo 64:8 \xt Izhd. 79:8\x*
\v 9 Tineddam nnec timqeddasin dewřent d řexřa, Ṣihyun tedweř d tanezruft, Urcalim d amcan ittwareddǧen.
\v 10 Taddart nneɣ teccur s temqeddast d tissiqt, mani řejdud nneɣ ssemɣaren Cek, tᵉttwacmeḍ s tmessi u marra min xaneɣ iɛizzen, idweř d řxirbet.
\v 11 Ma tzemmared ad tmenɛed Ixef nnec di qaɛ aya, \add a\add* SIDI, ma tzemmared ad tesseɣded u ad aneɣ teḥṣared ammu aṭṭas?”
\b
\b
\c 65
\s1 Řḥukm d usenjem i řgens n Arebbi x wedrar n Siḥyun
\m 
\v 1 “Tuɣa ttbaneɣ asen-dd i yinni war xafi sseqsin, zemmaren ad ayi afen inni war xafi yarezzun. Necc nniɣ i řgens i war iřiɣin s Yisem inu: ‘Aqa ayi da, xzar, aqa ayi da!’
\v 2 Ass marra sswiẓẓaḍeɣ ifassen inu ɣar řgens iɣewwɣen, wenni yuyuren deg ijj n webrid war iḥřin, x řeḥsab ixarriṣen nnes,
\v 3 řgens nni d ayi iseɛɛaren řebda deg wudem inu, am qeddmen tiɣarṣa deh iḥwicen u bexxaren \add tiwhibin\add* x llajur.
\v 4 Nitni ttɣiman deg imeḍřan, u ttnusan deg ifran am ttᵉtten aysum n iřfan u ɣarsen ijj n nnɛi n arrwa di marmitat nsen. \x ◘ \xo 65:4 \xt Ica. 66:17\x*
\v 5 Nitni qqaren: ‘Qqim mani teǧid, war d ayi dd-tades, maɣar necc d amqeddes zzayek!’ Aqa aten \add am\add* ddexxan deg wenzaren inu, \add am\add* tmessi yareqqen ass ikmeř.
\v 6 Xzar, aya yura zzat i wudem inu, war ssɣidiɣ, maca ad xeřfeɣ, \add wah,\add* ad xeřfeɣ \add aya\add* deg weḥsin nsen: \f ◼ \fr 65:6 \fk aḥsin\ft - niɣ ‘abeḥrur’.\f*
\v 7 řmuɛṣiyyat nwem d řmuɛṣiyyat n ibabaten nwem, inni wehhben řebxur x idurar u inni d ayi isseḥqaren x tewririn. Necc simant inu ad asen xeǧṣeɣ řmunet nsen i sdahǧen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”
\b
\m 
\v 8 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Am mammec umi ufin aẓemmi n uḍiř deg uzekkun uca qqaren: War t jarreḥ, maɣar dayes lbaraka!, ammu i ɣa ggeɣ di ṭṭweɛ n imsexxaren inu, ḥima war ten qeṭṭiɣ marra.
\v 9 Necc ad dd-jjeɣ zzariɛet zi Yaɛqub u ad ssuffɣeɣ awrit n idurar inu zi Yahuda. Inni zzayi ittwafarzen ad tt ṭṭfen d tasɣart uca imsexxaren inu ad dinni zedɣen.
\v 10 Řewḍa n Carun ad yiři d takessawt n wuǧi, u taɣzurt n Axur d amcan n arraḥet i ifunasen, i řgens inu wenni xafi yarezzun.”
\b
\m 
\v 11 “Kenniw maca inni isemḥen di SIDI, inni ittun adrar inu iqeddsen, inni isswejden ṭṭabřa i Jad u inni iccuren \add aɣarraf s\add* binu ixeǧḍen i Mini,
\v 12 Necc ad kenniw ḥesbeɣ i ssif. Kenniw ad taḍarem marra maḥend ad ttwaɣarṣem, umi Necc i d awem řaɣiɣ, \add maca\add* kenniw war \add xafi\add* dd-tarrim, \add umi\add* Necc ɣarwem ssiwřeɣ, \add maca\add* kenniw war \add ɣari\add* tesřim, maca teggim min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin inu, u tixḍarem min war d ayi dd-yusin x řxaḍar.”
\b
\m 
\v 13 “S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Xzar, imsexxaren inu ad ccen, \add maca\add* kenniw ad tǧaẓem. Xzar, imsexxaren inu ad swen, \add maca\add* kenniw ad teffadem. Xzar, imsexxaren inu ad farḥen, \add maca\add* kenniw ad tseḍḥam.
\v 14 Xzar, imsexxaren inu ad sřiwřewen s řefraḥet n wuř, \add maca\add* kenniw ad tesɣuyem zi řeḥriq n wuř, ad tweɛɛḍem zi arẓiyyet n buḥbeř.
\v 15 Ad tejjem isem nwem am nneɛřet i yinni zzayi ittwafarzen, uca Sidi inu, SIDI, ad kenniw ineɣ, \add maca\add* imsexxaren nnes ad xasen iřaɣa s ijj n yisem nneɣni,
\v 16 ařami wenni ixsen ad ibarek ixef nnes di temmurt, ad ibarek ixef nnes di AREBBI n tidett, u wenni ixsen ad ijjuǧ di temmurt, ad ijjuǧ ɣar AREBBI n tidett, maɣar řeḥṣarat n zic ad ttwattunt u ad ttwassnuffarent zzat i tiṭṭawin inu.’”
\b
\m 
\v 17 “Maɣar xzar, Necc ad ggeɣ ijenwan n jdid d temmurt n jdid. War tteɛqiřen ɛad x tmesřayin iɛdun, war dd-ttisent \add ɛad\add* i uřa d ijj ɣar řbař.
\v 18 Farḥem xenni u farrjem i řebda x min i dd ɣa xeřqeɣ, maɣar xzar, Necc ad dd-xeřqeɣ Urcalim d řefraḥet u řgens nnes d afarrej.
\v 19 Necc ad sřiwřeweɣ x Urcalim, ad farḥeɣ zi řgens inu. Ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad dayes sřen i řḥess n imeṭṭawen niɣ n uɣuyyi.
\v 20 Aḥḍiḍ i ɣa iddaren ca n wussan \add waha\add*, war ittiři ɛad, uřa d awessar nni war ittkemmiřen ussan nnes. Maɣar aḥuḍri ad immet xmi ɣares ɣa yiři mya n iseggʷusa, u amednub ad ittwanɛeř xmi ɣares ɣa yiři mya n iseggʷusa.
\v 21 Nitni ad bnan tudrin ad daysent zedɣen, ad ẓẓun tizayarin deg imarjaɛen, ad ccen řɣiǧet nsen.
\v 22 Nitni war bennin \add maḥend\add* wenneɣni ad \add dayes\add* izdeɣ, war tteẓẓun \add maḥend\add* wenneɣni ad \add zzayes\add* yecc, maɣar ussan n řgens inu ad iřin am wussan n tcejjart, u inni zzayi ittwafarzen ad awyen ariqqi zi řxedmet n ifassen nsen. \f ◼ \fr 65:22 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*
\v 23 Nitni war xeddmen ɛad baṭeř, war ttirwen iḥenjiren i uceřwaw s řɣefřet, maɣar nitni d zzariɛet n yinni ittwabarken zi SIDI, uřa d tarrawt nsen akidsen.
\v 24 Qbeř ma ad řaɣan, ad \add xasen\add* dd-arreɣ, xwansu ɛad ssawařen, ad \add asen\add* sřeɣ.
\v 25 Uccen d izmar ad arewsen munen, ayrad ad icc řum am ufunas, uca afar ad yiři d macca i ufiɣar. War tteggen tuɛeffna u war ssekkaren řeqjaret x marra adrar inu iqeddsen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 65:25 \xt Ica. 11:6, 7, 8, 9; Mt. 18:3\x*
\b
\b
\c 66
\s1 SIDI d Řqaḍi ad iḥkem zi Zzawect Iqeddsen
\m 
\v 1 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ajenna d řɛarc inu u tammurt d tanebdat i iḍaren inu. Mani \add i ɣa tiři\add* xenni taddart nni texsem ad ayi tebnam u mani \add i ɣa yiři\add* wemcan n arraḥet inu? \x ◘ \xo 66:1 \xt 1 Ij. 8:27; 2 Im. 6:18; Řex. 7:48,49; 17:24\x*
\v 2 Marra aya igga i-t ufus inu d marra aya tuɣa iǧa ɛad, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, \add maca\add* Necc ad nḍareɣ tiṭṭawin inu x umezřuḍ, x wenni ittwarẓan buḥbeř nnes u x wenni ittarjijin zzat i wawař inu.’”
\b
\m 
\v 3 “Wenni iɣarṣen i ufunas, inɣa \add uřa d\add* aryaz, u wenni yiwyen ijjen zeg wuǧi d ddbiḥet, yarẓa \add ɛawed\add* iri i yiṭan, u wenni iqeddmen tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*, \add iqeddem\add* \add uřa d\add* idammen n yiřef, u wenni issbexxaren jjawi, ibarek \add uřa d\add* aɛbed n řexyařat. Nitni ixḍaren ibriden \add i yixef nsen\add* uca řeɛmar nsen iɛjeb as nnɛawat nsen n l’aṣnam.
\v 4 Ammu i ɣa areccḥeɣ uřa d Necc tiyyita nsen i nitni uca ad xasen awyeɣ min zi tteggʷeden, maɣar nitni war dd-arrin umi Necc d asen řaɣiɣ, \add maɣar\add* nitni war sřin umi ɣarsen ssiwřeɣ, \add maca\add* nitni ggin min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin inu uca ixḍaren min war dd-yusin x řxaḍar inu.” \x ◘ \xo 66:4 \xt Awřn. 1:24; Ica. 65:12; Irm. 7:13\x*
\b
\m 
\v 5 “Sřem i wawař n SIDI, \add a kenniw\add* inni ittarjijin zzat i wawař nnes: ‘Aytmatwem, inni kenniw icarrhen, inni kenniw inḍaren di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem inu uca qqaren: Iři ad ittwassɛuǧa SIDI, scen aneɣ řefraḥet nwem!, ad seḍḥan. \x ◘ \xo 66:5 \xt Ica. 5:19\x*
\v 6 Ad dd-iffeɣ ddriz imɣar zi tendint, tmijja zi Zzawect Tameqqrant, tmijja n SIDI, wenni i ɣa ixeǧṣen řɛedyan nnes řmunet nsen i isdaheǧen.’” \x ◘ \xo 66:6 \xt Asa.16:1, 17. \x*
\b
\s1 Axřaq i isstebhten n tarwa n Siḥyun
\m 
\v 7 “Qbeř i ɣa iṭṭef řeḥriq n tarwa \add i temɣart Ṣihyun\add*, aqa turuw-dd, qbeř i tt ɣa menɛen řewjeɛ n tarut, tegga \add aḥenjir\add* d awtem ad injem. \x ◘ \xo 66:7 \xt Asa. 12:1-6\x*
\v 8 Wi isřan aya? Man wen i iẓrin aya? Ma ad dd-texřeq ict n temmurt deg ijj n wass \add waha\add*? Ma ad dd-ixřeq ijj n řgens deg ict n tecti \add waha\add*? Maca usin as-dd i Ṣihyun řewjeɛ n tarut ɛad cwayt \add waha\add*, aqa turuw-dd iḥenjiren nnes.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 “Ma ad as arzmeɣ aɛeddis nhřa ma jjiɣ \add tt\add* ad taru?, iqqar SIDI. Ma Necc wenni issarawen \add timɣarin\add*, ad \add asent\add* bellɛeɣ \add taɛeddist\add*?iqqar AREBBI nnem.”
\b
\m 
\v 10 “Farḥem ak-d Urcalim uca sřiwřiwem as, \add a\add* marra kenniw inni tt ittexsen. Farḥem zzayes s usřiwřew, marra \add kenniw\add* inni tuɣa xas iceḍnen,
\v 11 ḥima ad tᵉṭṭḍem, ad tejjiwnem zeg ibbac nnes iccuren s ufewwej, ḥima ad teswem s tyawant u ad tarrem meẓri zi min iǧan d aṣebḥan qaɛ n uɛuǧi nnes!”
\b
\m 
\v 12 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad as ssizzřeɣ řehna am yeɣzar u aɛuǧi n řegnus am teɣzart iḥemřen, ḥima kenniw ad \add zzayes\add* tᵉṭṭḍen. Ad kenniw arbun x tmeṣṣaḍin u ad xawem ssḥinnben x ifadden. \x ◘ \xo 66:12 \xt Ica. 49:22; 60:4\x*
\v 13 Am ijj n weryaz nni tessřehha as yemmas, ammu kenniw i ɣa sseřhuɣ, di Urcalim ad kenniw ssfewwjen.
\v 14 Ad tẓarem aya, ad ifarḥ wuř nwem, u iɣsan nwem ad ttwaneɛcen am arbiɛ aziza. Ammu i ɣa ittwassen ufus n SIDI ɣar imsexxaren nnes, \add maca\add* Netta ad isxeḍ x řɛedyan nnes.’”
\b
\m 
\v 15 “Minzi, xzar, ad dd-yas SIDI di tmessi, ikarruten nnes \add ad ggen\add* am tḥaryaḍt, ḥima ad yejj aɣḍab nnes ad yarsa s ijj n uduqqez n wesɛar nnes u tafqeḥt nnes s iḥudaq n tmessi.
\v 16 Maɣar SIDI ad iḥkem marra ddat s tmessi d ssif uca inni ɣa ittwanɣen zi SIDI ad iřin deg waṭṭas.
\v 17 \add Marra\add* inni issqeddsen u issizdigen ixef nsen deg iḥwicen awarni i yijjen, inni ittetten aysum n iřfan uřa d nnɛi \add n řmař\add* d iɣardayen, aqa marra nitni ad ttwaqḍan!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 66:17 \xt Ica. 65:3, 4; Ḥiz. 8:11, 12\x*
\b
\m 
\v 18 “Necc \add ad xeǧṣeɣ\add* timegga nsen d ixarriṣen nsen, uca ad imsar ad ssmuneɣ marra řegnus d iřsawen u nitni ad dd-asen ad ẓaren aɛuǧi inu.
\v 19 Necc ad ggeɣ ict n řeɛřamet jar asen uca ad ssekkeɣ inni zzaysen innejmen ɣar řegnus, ɣar Tarcic, Fuṭ d Lud, imjebbaden n řqews, ɣar Tubal d Yawan, ɣar tegzirin iggʷejen, tinni war isřin řexbar xafi u war iẓrin aɛuǧi inu. Nitni ad barrḥen aɛuǧi inu i řegnus,
\v 20 ad awyen aytmatwem zi marra řegnus d tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* i SIDI: x yeysan d ikarruten, di řekrasi ittwarebbun, x isardan d iřeɣman n ict n tgeɛrurt, ɣar wedrar inu amqeddes, ɣar Urcalim, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI inu, am mammec ttawyen ayt n Israil tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* di tqedduḥt tezdig ɣar Taddart n SIDI.
\v 21 Uřa zzaysen ad farzeɣ \add ca maḥend ad iřin\add* d ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen, iqqar SIDI.
\v 22 Maɣar am yijenwan n jdid d temmurt n jdid nni i ɣa ggeɣ ad bedden zzat i wudem inu, iqqar SIDI, ammu i ɣa \add teqqim\add* tbedd uřa d zzariɛet nwem d isem nwem \add zzat i wudem inu\add*. \x ◘ \xo 66:22 \xt Ica. 65:17; 2 Bṭ. 3:13; Asa. 21:1\x*
\v 23 Ad imsar zi qaɛ abeddi n uyur ař qaɛ abeddi nneɣni u zeg wass n ssebt ař ass n ssebt nneɣni ad dd-asen marra iwdan maḥend ad bendqen zzat i wudem inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 66:23 \fk marra iwdan\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘marra ddat’.\f*
\v 24 Nitni ad ffɣen, ad ẓařen řxecbat n yeryazen nni xafi iɛeddan, maɣar akecca nsen ɛemmarṣ war ittmetti uřa d timessi nsen ɛemmarṣ war tᵉttxessi. Ad iřin d nnɛi i marra iwdan d řmař.” 
